    'https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19:meeting_MDUyZTNiYTMtMTMxNi00YWUyLWI0MjktZjNiZjI1NWU5MGMy@thread.v2/0?context={"Tid":"0188564a-93de-489c-bf54-1927d4a9ed28","Oid":"bdae9fd3-d481-4c5e-aeea-7272e37b7d07"}',
    '{"id":"01KCHT10AD3QSS4S71ZZBNETX5","title":"iCorps + New North Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Campaign Performance and Lead Management**\n\nThe team confirmed strong progress on the **AI Readiness assessment ABM campaign**, with **22 points delivered in December** and **59 points of management tasks remaining** for the month (08:31).  \n- **Ruby Pontbriand** highlighted the campaign’s focus on a smaller, prioritized pool of contacts, sending up to the **third email to 60 people** so far, emphasizing timely follow-ups rather than mass outreach.  \n- **Nathalie Mintjens** reported the campaign targets about **873 contacts total**, with the system sending personalized drip emails rather than bulk blasts, improving engagement tracking.  \n- Ruby requested access to the campaign dashboard to better visualize contact stages and improve sales coordination; Nathalie agreed to share login details for enhanced transparency (12:04).  \n- They discussed a recent lead from the nurture campaign who requested a sales meeting via the free IT checkup form, illustrating the campaign’s ability to generate qualified sales opportunities beyond content downloads (14:42).  \n- Ruby flagged the need to better differentiate lead types in the CRM, suggesting clearer labels like “meeting requested” to distinguish hand-raisers from content downloaders, improving sales follow-up prioritization (19:20).  \n- Samuel and Ruby debated lifecycle stage definitions: Ruby noted sales prefers to treat LinkedIn leads differently, reserving MQL status for leads showing reciprocal interest post-contact, while Samuel advocated for keeping these as MQLs to maintain marketing alignment (22:26).  \n- Ruby proposed a marketing operations review early in the new year to clarify lead lifecycle stages and definitions, aiming to align marketing and sales perspectives for lead qualification and reporting (26:17).  \n- Ruby emphasized that despite different lead types, all leads still require follow-up, but sales should focus more on leads explicitly requesting meetings, ensuring efficient use of Kristen’s time (29:54).  \n- Ruby shared a success story of a client converted after years of content nurture, proving the value of sustained engagement and multi-touch lead development (32:20).\n\n## **Lead Lifecycle and CRM Process Improvements**\n\nClarifying lead categories and follow-up workflows is critical for smooth sales-marketing handoff and accurate reporting (23:17).  \n- Ruby suggested adding a “meeting requested” status in the CRM to trigger notifications similar to website form fills, alerting sales teams promptly and unifying lead handling processes (34:03).  \n- Nathalie agreed to explore developer options for mimicking website form notification workflows for LinkedIn form fills, improving visibility and response times (35:53).  \n- Samuel offered to share example workflows from their system to aid development and alignment on notification routing (37:00).  \n- Ruby plans to cancel and reset recurring meetings in January, creating a streamlined weekly process involving **Samuel, Nathalie, Ruby, and Colin** to maintain ongoing coordination (45:55).  \n- Invoice processing was briefly confirmed, with December invoices covering that month’s services and no pending follow-ups, ensuring financial clarity (46:16).\n\n## **SEO Strategy and Website Maintenance**\n\nThe SEO strategy focuses on targeting **low difficulty, high-volume keywords** selected through **Ahrefs** to improve rankings and drive relevant traffic to localized pages (38:30).  \n- Nathalie will send Jeff a detailed keyword list per page with monthly search volumes and difficulty scores, explaining the rationale to satisfy his thorough review needs (41:49).  \n- Ruby confirmed this transparency will help Jeff track SEO progress effectively and validate keyword targeting decisions (42:12).  \n- They agreed that keyword-driven pages will appear in relevant regional searches, avoiding mismatches like Boston results showing for Philadelphia queries (39:38).  \n- Ruby raised concern over broken links leading to **404 errors**, suggesting this become part of ongoing website upkeep and management tasks to preserve site health (42:41).  \n- Nathalie noted blog posts are likely the main source of outdated links due to landing page updates, and plans to coordinate with web team to scan and fix these errors to maintain user experience and SEO integrity (43:38).\n\n## **Scheduling and Team Coordination**\n\nThe team agreed to pause meetings during the holiday weeks, resuming the regular cadence on **Wednesday, January 7th**, to ensure productivity without overloading team members during vacation periods (44:40).  \n- Nathalie will send scheduling links for any interim communications, but the main working rhythm will pause to accommodate planned absences (44:45).  \n- Ruby confirmed updating the meeting invite list to include key personnel and streamline participation for the new year’s workflow (45:20).","outline":null,"keywords":["AI Readiness","Marketing Qualified Leads","Lead Management","SEO Keyword Strategy","LinkedIn Campaign","Meeting Scheduling"],"overview":"- **AI Readiness Campaign Progress:** 22 points delivered in December; 59 tasks left for completion.  \n- **Targeted Email Strategy:** Focus on 873 contacts with personalized drip emails improving engagement and follow-up.  \n- **Lead Type Differentiation:** Suggestions made for clearer CRM labels like “meeting requested” for better sales prioritization.  \n- **Lead Lifecycle Review Proposal:** Marketing operations review suggested for early January to align definitions of lead qualification.  \n- **SEO Strategy Focus:** Targeting low difficulty, high-volume keywords to improve search rankings and relevant traffic.  \n- **Meeting Schedule Adjustments:** Meetings paused during holidays, resuming January 7th to balance workload and team absences.","action_items":"\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nProvide Ruby Pontbriand with login credentials for the AI readiness campaign dashboard to increase transparency (12:09)\nExplore options with developers to implement notification workflows mimicking website form fills for LinkedIn meeting requests (35:53)\nSend Jeff a detailed recap email on SEO keyword targeting, including monthly search volume, difficulty, and rationale (41:49)\nPerform a website audit to identify and fix 404 errors, focusing on blog post links, coordinating with web support team (43:39)\nCoordinate scheduling by sending out a scheduling link for next week and confirm no meetings during Nathalie’s absence (44:10)\n\n**Ruby Pontbriand**\nCancel the existing recurring meeting series and create a fresh weekly series starting January 7th including Sam, Nathalie, Ruby, and Colin (45:43)\nReview and modify the contact list view (e.g., adding columns) to better distinguish between lead campaigns like Free IT Checkup vs. Smart IT Budget guide for improved qualification clarity (15:47)\n\n**Samuel Bagnall**\nShare the workflow example used for discovery meeting booked notifications to help design the LinkedIn meeting request notification (37:06)\nSubmit the December invoice for reimbursement processing (46:40)\n"},"duration":47.63999938964844,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"id":1,"name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"id":2,"name":"Ruby Pontbriand"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Natalie, how''s it going?","index":0,"end_time":3.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2.16,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Hello.","index":1,"end_time":5.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":4.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Good.","index":2,"end_time":5.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.44,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":3,"end_time":7.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":5.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Good.","index":4,"end_time":7.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":7.4,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"How''s your weekend?","index":5,"end_time":15.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":14.4,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Really busy, actually.","index":6,"end_time":20.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":19.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, yeah?","index":7,"end_time":21.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":20.72,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Is that a good thing?","index":8,"end_time":22.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":21.64,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":9,"end_time":23.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":23.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":10,"end_time":24.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":24.16,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I feel like it was very slow for a while, which we talked about, but this week it just picked up for some reason.","index":11,"end_time":30.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":24.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":12,"end_time":32.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":32.15,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":13,"end_time":33.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":33.03,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Or were you gonna ask?","index":14,"end_time":35.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.15,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Oh, I was gonna ask if you have big Christmas plans.","index":15,"end_time":41.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":36.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, not.","index":16,"end_time":42.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":41.99,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Not too.","index":17,"end_time":43.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":42.75,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Just staying around here.","index":18,"end_time":44.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.43,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Michael''s snowboarding the weekend after Christmas, so that''ll be fun.","index":19,"end_time":48.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":45.11,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And then.","index":20,"end_time":50.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":50.31,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":21,"end_time":52.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":51.99,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"New Year''s Eve I have a wedding.","index":22,"end_time":54.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.47,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Should be fine, but.","index":23,"end_time":56.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":55.19,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":24,"end_time":56.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.27,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So what about you?","index":25,"end_time":59.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":56.59,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Someone planned their wedding on New Year''s.","index":26,"end_time":61.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":59.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"New Year''s Eve.","index":27,"end_time":63.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":28,"end_time":63.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":63.04,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It''s.","index":29,"end_time":64.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I mean, you know, it''s.","index":30,"end_time":66.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.6,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It''s kind of fun because I never have plans on New Year''s Eve, so I''m excited.","index":31,"end_time":69.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":66.52,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s my wife''s cousin, so it''ll be fun.","index":32,"end_time":74.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.04,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And it''s nearby, so it''s nothing crazy.","index":33,"end_time":75.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":74.32,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I have to travel, so that''s kind of cool, actually.","index":34,"end_time":79.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":75.96,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I think.","index":35,"end_time":80.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":79.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I feel like we''re always looking for plans on New Year''s.","index":36,"end_time":83.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":80.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"A wedding is, like, a fun thing to go to.","index":37,"end_time":86.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":84.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":38,"end_time":87.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I mean, I. I never had plans because.","index":39,"end_time":89.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.36,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":40,"end_time":90.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":89.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So there''s just so much going on, so I just.","index":41,"end_time":92.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":90.6,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I''m like, yeah, it''s fine.","index":42,"end_time":93.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":92.32,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"But, yeah, so it''d be cool.","index":43,"end_time":94.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":93.48,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Like, just go to a wedding, have some fun.","index":44,"end_time":100.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":94.8,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":45,"end_time":100.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":100.4,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Nice.","index":46,"end_time":102.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":101.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I.","index":47,"end_time":104.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":103.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Well, my mom is here visiting from Hong Kong for, like, a month, so.","index":48,"end_time":111.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":104.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Is she staying with you?","index":49,"end_time":113.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":111.87,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, she''s staying with me and my older sister.","index":50,"end_time":116.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":113.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it''s a full house over here.","index":51,"end_time":119.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":117.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":52,"end_time":120.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":119.55,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":53,"end_time":121.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":120.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe that''s why it feels so busy, like the work hasn''t changed.","index":54,"end_time":124.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":121.47,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But I''m also, like, hosting people.","index":55,"end_time":126.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":124.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":56,"end_time":127.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":127.07,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":57,"end_time":128.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":127.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Have they.","index":58,"end_time":129.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":128.67,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Have they been.","index":59,"end_time":129.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129.23,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And they''ve been before, right?","index":60,"end_time":130.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":129.79,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"To Chicago.","index":61,"end_time":131.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":130.91,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":62,"end_time":132.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":131.87,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":63,"end_time":132.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":132.43,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":64,"end_time":133.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":132.79,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I figured.","index":65,"end_time":134.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":133.71,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And then we had our holiday party on Saturday, which was fun.","index":66,"end_time":144.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":140.76,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Ruby did get up and sing with the band.","index":67,"end_time":147.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":145.24,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"She can tell you about that a little more, but, yeah, it was.","index":68,"end_time":151.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":149.08,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It was very funny.","index":69,"end_time":153,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":151.88,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Wait.","index":70,"end_time":155.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":154.44,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I.","index":71,"end_time":157.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":156.12,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"She didn''t expect it either, but the guy, the lead singer, was like, ruby can harmonize, and he''s like, get up here.","index":72,"end_time":163.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":158.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And then she got up here and sang.","index":73,"end_time":164.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":163.04,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Oh, my.","index":74,"end_time":165.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":165.07,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":75,"end_time":165.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":165.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I was about to ask whether that was voluntary or they called.","index":76,"end_time":169.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":165.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":77,"end_time":169.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":169.47,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I mean, I don''t know.","index":78,"end_time":170.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":170.19,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Maybe if she mentioned that she could sing a little bit, and then he.","index":79,"end_time":174.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":170.99,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Like, before.","index":80,"end_time":175.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.15,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Because she was kind of their point of contact, like, when they got there, like, hey, guess anything, let me know.","index":81,"end_time":180.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":176.19,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":82,"end_time":181.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":181.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Kind of thing.","index":83,"end_time":182.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":181.71,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And she was talking to him, so maybe she mentioned it and then he just called her up.","index":84,"end_time":187.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":183.95,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"But no, it was not planned.","index":85,"end_time":188.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":187.67,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"She did not expect it.","index":86,"end_time":190.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":188.83,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"This is funny.","index":87,"end_time":193.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":192.36,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, that was pretty cool.","index":88,"end_time":197.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":193.72,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"How did the rest of the party go?","index":89,"end_time":199.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":198.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It was good.","index":90,"end_time":200.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":200.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":91,"end_time":202.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":202.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Moved to a bigger room, which was, I think, really good.","index":92,"end_time":205.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":202.6,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And the band, so we had, like, a DJ in past years, which have been.","index":93,"end_time":210.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":206.279,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I don''t know, it''s kind of okay.","index":94,"end_time":213.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.48,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"But the band was really good.","index":95,"end_time":214.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":213.32,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Definitely worth the bigger room and all that.","index":96,"end_time":218.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":215.4,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Nice.","index":97,"end_time":221.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":220.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":98,"end_time":222.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":222.45,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I mean, the view isn''t as good from the bigger room because it''s over, like, Boston harbor, so you can see the city.","index":99,"end_time":227.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":222.89,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"But I didn''t mind it.","index":100,"end_time":231.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.85,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It was fine because, I mean, it''s so much more room to, like, move around and we''re More seating and stuff like that.","index":101,"end_time":238.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":231.81,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I thought it was all around, just better.","index":102,"end_time":241.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.37,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"How many employees are at I Corps?","index":103,"end_time":246.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":243.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think there''s like, 73 as of right now.","index":104,"end_time":250.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":247.02,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":105,"end_time":251.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":250.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":106,"end_time":251.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":251.5,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So.","index":107,"end_time":252.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":251.98,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"And not everybody came.","index":108,"end_time":253.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":252.3,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"We had some no shows on the night of, too.","index":109,"end_time":255.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":253.58,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I''m trying to think how many people were there?","index":110,"end_time":259.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":257.74,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Maybe like 80 with plus ones.","index":111,"end_time":261.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":259.14,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Oh, no, hold on.","index":112,"end_time":262.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":261.46,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"That''s not right.","index":113,"end_time":262.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":262.06,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, maybe 80 with plus ones.","index":114,"end_time":265.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":262.78,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"85.","index":115,"end_time":266.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":265.5,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":116,"end_time":267.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":266.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":117,"end_time":268.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.58,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":118,"end_time":272.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":272.23,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Hello.","index":119,"end_time":277.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":277.51,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":120,"end_time":278.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":277.95,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Hi.","index":121,"end_time":279.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":278.79,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":122,"end_time":280.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":279.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"How''s it going?","index":123,"end_time":281.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":280.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Good.","index":124,"end_time":282.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":281.75,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Good.","index":125,"end_time":283.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":283.43,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I heard that you''re a singing star.","index":126,"end_time":286.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":284.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, God.","index":127,"end_time":288.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":287.51,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Words out.","index":128,"end_time":289.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":288.79,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I sing.","index":129,"end_time":292.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":291.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":130,"end_time":294.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":294.35,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think I''ve always done well.","index":131,"end_time":297.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":294.55,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I know.","index":132,"end_time":298.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":297.75,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I knew that.","index":133,"end_time":298.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":298.31,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I was just talking about the holiday party of.","index":134,"end_time":300.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":298.71,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, the holiday party.","index":135,"end_time":301.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":300.43,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s been, like, wild.","index":136,"end_time":302.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":301.35,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"That was fun.","index":137,"end_time":303.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":302.67,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Pulled me up on stage and I was like, really?","index":138,"end_time":305.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":303.27,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Are you sure?","index":139,"end_time":306.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":305.59,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And of course, in the moment, I didn''t think, like.","index":140,"end_time":309.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":307.55,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I didn''t think through, like, the full scope of, like, what that would mean because, like, the whole audience is all these people I work with, but.","index":141,"end_time":320.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":311.39,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Oh.","index":142,"end_time":321.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":321.24,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So, yeah, it was fine.","index":143,"end_time":323.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":321.96,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It was fun.","index":144,"end_time":325.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":325.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I actually really enjoyed it.","index":145,"end_time":326.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":325.76,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It was great.","index":146,"end_time":327.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":326.84,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":147,"end_time":327.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":327.36,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Wait, what did you sing?","index":148,"end_time":329.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":328.04,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I only sung, like.","index":149,"end_time":331.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":330.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I only sung, like, a verse and a half of Wagon Wheel, like, at the end of the song by Old Chrome Messenger.","index":150,"end_time":339,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":331.24,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think there or no wagon.","index":151,"end_time":341.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":339,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, Wagon Wheel.","index":152,"end_time":343.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":342.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You know the song, right?","index":153,"end_time":343.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.04,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":154,"end_time":344.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.04,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So Darius Rucker did a.","index":155,"end_time":346.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.48,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Did a cover of it, too.","index":156,"end_time":347.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":346.76,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":157,"end_time":348.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":347.96,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Rock me, mama Like a wagon wheel Rock me, mom Anyway you feel.","index":158,"end_time":354.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":349.23,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Hey.","index":159,"end_time":355.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":354.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":160,"end_time":356.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":355.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That sounds fun, though.","index":161,"end_time":361.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":360.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":162,"end_time":361.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.63,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I.","index":163,"end_time":362.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":361.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Did anyone take a video?","index":164,"end_time":363.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":165,"end_time":366.03,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":365.07,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"As of right now, it seems like no.","index":166,"end_time":369.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":367.07,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, we asked yesterday and nobody did, but it''s fine.","index":167,"end_time":372.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":369.31,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think there''s pictures, though.","index":168,"end_time":373.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":372.43,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":169,"end_time":374.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":374.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I know the photographer.","index":170,"end_time":377.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":376.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"She showed me a picture when we were there.","index":171,"end_time":380.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":377.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So it is documented because Jeff was joking and being like, oh, there''s no video.","index":172,"end_time":386.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":380.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It didn''t happen.","index":173,"end_time":387.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":386.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, oh, my God.","index":174,"end_time":388.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":387.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Hey, thanks.","index":175,"end_time":392.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":390.28,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It sounds like you had fun.","index":176,"end_time":396.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":395.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":177,"end_time":397.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":397.48,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"All right.","index":178,"end_time":401.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":400.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"How are you doing?","index":179,"end_time":404.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":403.33,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How''s your.","index":180,"end_time":404.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":404.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How was.","index":181,"end_time":405.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":404.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How''s.","index":182,"end_time":407.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":406.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How''s life?","index":183,"end_time":407.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":407.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How''s.","index":184,"end_time":408.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":407.73,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Getting all ready for Christmas?","index":185,"end_time":409.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":408.45,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Or, like, what are your holiday plans?","index":186,"end_time":411.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":409.77,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I was just telling Sam, my mom and older sister are here visiting from Hong Kong, and they''ll be here for, like, a month.","index":187,"end_time":420.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":411.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it''s a full house.","index":188,"end_time":421.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yay.","index":189,"end_time":422.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":421.97,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I''m really busy trying to host, like, balancing work and then, like, trying to entertain them at the same time.","index":190,"end_time":428.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":422.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":191,"end_time":428.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":428.62,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s a lot.","index":192,"end_time":429.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":428.94,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s a lot.","index":193,"end_time":430.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":429.82,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":194,"end_time":430.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":430.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But it''ll.","index":195,"end_time":434.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":433.26,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''ll be fun.","index":196,"end_time":434.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":434.02,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll get to show them.","index":197,"end_time":437.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":436.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"They''ve been here a few times, but I still get to show them a bit of the city.","index":198,"end_time":441.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":437.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I booked Chicago Bulls tickets for us to go watch as a surprise.","index":199,"end_time":447.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":442.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So, yeah, it''ll be fun.","index":200,"end_time":450.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":448.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":201,"end_time":452.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":451.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":202,"end_time":453.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":453.59,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right, so looking at our points, we have 22 delivered so far in December.","index":203,"end_time":461.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":455.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we did the webpage and then got the AI Readiness assessment ABM launched.","index":204,"end_time":467.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":462.15,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then for the rest of the month, we just have your management tasks here, which equal a total of 59 points.","index":205,"end_time":474.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":467.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then looking at ABM.","index":206,"end_time":480.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":478.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I just wanted to show you how the AI readiness campaign is going so far for email.","index":207,"end_time":487.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":480.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So so far, we''ve reached the third email for some contacts.","index":208,"end_time":491.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":487.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So this is the number of emails that have been sent in total.","index":209,"end_time":494.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":491.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So how the campaign is set up is.","index":210,"end_time":498.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":496.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s.","index":211,"end_time":498.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":498.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s prioritizing, following up with people who have already received the first email over sending the first email to people, if that makes sense.","index":212,"end_time":509.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":498.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":213,"end_time":510.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":509.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So once they.","index":214,"end_time":511.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Smaller pool.","index":215,"end_time":512.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":511.34,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Smaller pool focused on.","index":216,"end_time":516.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":513.9,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Not, like, on them responding or opening or something.","index":217,"end_time":522.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":517.98,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Instead of a larger set of just, like, spray and pray.","index":218,"end_time":527.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":522.14,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":219,"end_time":529.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":528.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And also like a smaller pool.","index":220,"end_time":531.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":529.14,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And, like, once they receive the first email, making sure we''re not waiting too long before they receive the second.","index":221,"end_time":536.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":222,"end_time":537.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":537.34,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":223,"end_time":538.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":537.78,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":224,"end_time":538.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":538.39,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So, yeah, this is how it''s going around the third email so far for 60 people.","index":225,"end_time":544.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":539.67,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then more people keep getting entered into this first email over here.","index":226,"end_time":548.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":544.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then looking at our MQL so far for December, this is just a breakdown of where they''ve come from.","index":227,"end_time":557.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":550.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So LinkedIn is doing well.","index":228,"end_time":559.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":557.91,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Specifically, people downloading the smart IT budget guide followed by content and then SEO.","index":229,"end_time":566.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":559.83,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And it looks like we did get a.","index":230,"end_time":568.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":567.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Another ChatGPT referral this month as well.","index":231,"end_time":571.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":568.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, I have a question.","index":232,"end_time":577.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":572,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"On the, the contacts themselves that are in these sequences, can you remind me, like, where they live or like, I don''t know, just trying to visualize, like.","index":233,"end_time":594.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":577.52,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay, You''ve got these 176 contacts to start with, and then it drilled down to 123 and then down to 60.","index":234,"end_time":604.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":594.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Is that right?","index":235,"end_time":605.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":604.81,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"No, no.","index":236,"end_time":608.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":607.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So these are the.","index":237,"end_time":609.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This is the number of people that have received email.","index":238,"end_time":612.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":609.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"1.","index":239,"end_time":612.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":612.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I see.","index":240,"end_time":614.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":613.69,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Actually receipts.","index":241,"end_time":615.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":614.49,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yes.","index":242,"end_time":616.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":615.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Not sends or sent.","index":243,"end_time":619.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":616.19,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, sent.","index":244,"end_time":620.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":619.51,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we, I think in our campaign we have a total of about a thousand people, but, like, we''re not sending a mass email.","index":245,"end_time":629.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like, it just goes out at once.","index":246,"end_time":630.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":629.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"These are like one to one individual emails that happen like on a drip sequence.","index":247,"end_time":635.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":631.27,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, yeah.","index":248,"end_time":637.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":636.31,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"All right, that.","index":249,"end_time":638.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":637.51,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That makes sense.","index":250,"end_time":638.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":638.11,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I knew that part.","index":251,"end_time":639.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":638.67,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think I was just more thinking of like a little bit.","index":252,"end_time":643,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":639.35,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Kind of like on Kristen''s side of like, is there like a list of all these people that we could look at and see where they''re at in the like.","index":253,"end_time":656.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":643,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because I know they don''t hit HubSpot until they reach that score.","index":254,"end_time":660.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":656.2,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I didn''t know if.","index":255,"end_time":666.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":665.44,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":256,"end_time":669.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":669.29,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s probably over complicating it.","index":257,"end_time":672.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":671.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I just thought maybe like in between sends, like she could reach out on LinkedIn or something.","index":258,"end_time":678.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":673.21,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":259,"end_time":680.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":680.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think if we go on smart lead itself.","index":260,"end_time":683.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":680.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, these dashboards are cool.","index":261,"end_time":697.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":695.62,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yes.","index":262,"end_time":699.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":698.58,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"This is showing just by day how many were sent, opened, and then clicked.","index":263,"end_time":704.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":699.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":264,"end_time":705.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":705.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":265,"end_time":707.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":707.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we.","index":266,"end_time":707.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":707.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":267,"end_time":708.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":707.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"In this campaign we have 873 people.","index":268,"end_time":711.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":708.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":269,"end_time":715.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":715.06,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So if we.","index":270,"end_time":716.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":715.7,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We can go and see each individual contact and then which stage they''re on.","index":271,"end_time":720.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":716.34,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh.","index":272,"end_time":721.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":721.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s super helpful.","index":273,"end_time":725.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":724.37,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Is this something that we could have view access to?","index":274,"end_time":728.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":725.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll give you the login details.","index":275,"end_time":734.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":729.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right, that''d be great because I think more.","index":276,"end_time":741.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":739.33,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I think the more we could, like, see and like, you know, see behind the curtain a little bit.","index":277,"end_time":747.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":743.41,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":278,"end_time":748.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":747.77,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Maybe the better for either Kristen to understand.","index":279,"end_time":751.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":749.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I know this is helpful for me even just like having the dashboard for the performance would be cool for me to just pop in front of like, Mike and Jeff.","index":280,"end_time":760.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":751.61,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s like a quick update.","index":281,"end_time":762.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":761.37,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"This is pretty cool.","index":282,"end_time":763.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":762.89,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, sure.","index":283,"end_time":765.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":764.57,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll send this over to you.","index":284,"end_time":766.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":765.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then you can also see past campaigns too, that we ran over here.","index":285,"end_time":771.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":767.61,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":286,"end_time":772.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":771.85,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":287,"end_time":775.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":774.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It also might be cool because, like, if she sees a name and a company that like pops for her in that.","index":288,"end_time":782.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":775.38,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"In that list or whatever, if it does end up in highly engaged, like, she''d be even that more ready to jump on it.","index":289,"end_time":793.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":782.98,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":290,"end_time":794.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":794.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And she can also go back and see exactly what emails they received.","index":291,"end_time":799.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":794.98,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Mm.","index":292,"end_time":800.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":799.75,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s really.","index":293,"end_time":801.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":800.31,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s.","index":294,"end_time":801.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.43,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think.","index":295,"end_time":802.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.87,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":296,"end_time":802.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.23,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"This is like the part that''s been missing.","index":297,"end_time":803.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":802.63,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s like, what did it look like before they got to HubSpot?","index":298,"end_time":808.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":803.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You know, what were.","index":299,"end_time":809.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":808.47,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"What did that conversation look like?","index":300,"end_time":810.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":809.35,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And the past has just been like, okay, we know the content, we know the sequence, but we don''t know exactly, like, where they.","index":301,"end_time":820.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":810.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How many they got before they landed in HubSpot, or like, what the exact stuff was.","index":302,"end_time":827.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":822.63,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So, yeah, this is great.","index":303,"end_time":828.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":827.43,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":304,"end_time":830.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":829.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":305,"end_time":832.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":832.01,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then one other thing.","index":306,"end_time":836.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":834.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":307,"end_time":837.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we got this lead the other day that I wanted to point out.","index":308,"end_time":843.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":837.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So this is a lead that came.","index":309,"end_time":845.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":843.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"If you remember, in LinkedIn, we have the Smart IT budget guide campaign, and that is what''s getting most of the downloads right now.","index":310,"end_time":853.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":845.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But we also have the nurture campaign that''s running where we''re retargeting people in our highly engaged lead list and trying to get them to book a meeting.","index":311,"end_time":864.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":854.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So this person actually came from that nurture campaign where they submitted the form to get the free IT checkup, which is really our sales discovery call.","index":312,"end_time":875.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":865.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But it looks like Kristin followed up with the Smart IT Budget guide.","index":313,"end_time":881.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":877.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, I see.","index":314,"end_time":882.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":882,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":315,"end_time":883.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":883.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So just a note.","index":316,"end_time":886.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":885.21,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I don''t know if.","index":317,"end_time":887.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":886.93,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I don''t know if this is enough information for her to be able to tell where they came from.","index":318,"end_time":895.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":890.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, it might be, but it might.","index":319,"end_time":898.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":896.73,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"She might not even know to look there.","index":320,"end_time":901.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":898.65,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because I know, I personally, like last week when I was trying to put together some pieces, I ended up putting those properties in on the left hand side so I could see at a glance, like, what thing they came from.","index":321,"end_time":917.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":901.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So she might not know to look there.","index":322,"end_time":923.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":921.76,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"She also might not know the difference between the Free IT checkup and the Smart IT Budget guide.","index":323,"end_time":928.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":923.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So that''s a great point.","index":324,"end_time":931.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":929.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I also think that we could probably modify the view that she''s working from and the contacts list, like the highly engaged leads list, the way we have it set up with the columns.","index":325,"end_time":945.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":931.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I.","index":326,"end_time":947.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":947.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Think she like, you know, kind of goes through.","index":327,"end_time":949.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":947.56,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s kind of like, you know, a pick list, and she''s able to see side by side, maybe at a glance.","index":328,"end_time":957,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":949.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"If she could see like, oh, easily, like, this is Smart IT Budget Guide, and this one was definitely IT checkup.","index":329,"end_time":964.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":957,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think it''s in there based on, like, that first conversion thing.","index":330,"end_time":969.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":964.77,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We just maybe need to pull that property into the columns or something.","index":331,"end_time":974.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":970.09,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":332,"end_time":975.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":975.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Because it doesn''t show up as a separate campaign.","index":333,"end_time":978.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":976.57,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":334,"end_time":979.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":978.73,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"The only place I can see the difference is.","index":335,"end_time":987.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":984.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, this first conversion.","index":336,"end_time":988.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":987.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":337,"end_time":990.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":990.18,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because I am still struggling a little bit with that.","index":338,"end_time":997.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":994.9,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Know that abm column, like the abm property.","index":339,"end_time":1002.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":998.66,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"List?","index":340,"end_time":1007.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1007.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yes.","index":341,"end_time":1009.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1009.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"This one.","index":342,"end_time":1014.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1013.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yes, that''s the one.","index":343,"end_time":1022.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1020.59,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So ideally, if we look up that Vanada Venkata, what does it say for her campaign?","index":344,"end_time":1037.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1025.79,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s just blank.","index":345,"end_time":1039.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1038.83,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":346,"end_time":1041.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1041,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But it would hypothetically be like retargeted.","index":347,"end_time":1047.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1041.8,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":348,"end_time":1050.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1049.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Highly engaged or like.","index":349,"end_time":1051.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1050.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because basically she.","index":350,"end_time":1056.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1055.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So if I understand this right, she was part of the.","index":351,"end_time":1058.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1056.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"She was part of an ABM sequence at some point in the past.","index":352,"end_time":1064.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1060.04,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And, like, made it through but, like, did become highly engaged.","index":353,"end_time":1074.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1068.77,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yes.","index":354,"end_time":1076.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":355,"end_time":1077.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1077.17,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So did become highly engaged for some reason and we just never heard back from her.","index":356,"end_time":1085.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1077.89,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":357,"end_time":1086.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1086.21,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So we''re still serving her with ads on LinkedIn and she actually did convert and say, yeah, I want to it checkup.","index":358,"end_time":1096.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1087.41,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Which is basically saying, yeah, I want to book a meeting.","index":359,"end_time":1099.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1097.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, we definitely need to mark that better because that''s definitely different than a, hey, I''m going to download your piece of helpful content, you know, because that''s not really like a hand raise.","index":360,"end_time":1112.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1101.42,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I want to talk.","index":361,"end_time":1113.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1112.46,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s like a different, different one.","index":362,"end_time":1116.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1113.14,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So, yeah, definitely open to your ideas for how you think we can better account for that in the system so that whoever is monitoring these and following up knows like, oh, hey, this is.","index":363,"end_time":1134.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1116.94,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"A.","index":364,"end_time":1134.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1134.33,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"It''s a different kind of approach, I think of a lead.","index":365,"end_time":1139.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1136.57,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":366,"end_time":1140.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1139.85,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"What about like a meeting.","index":367,"end_time":1144.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1143.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Meeting requested option here?","index":368,"end_time":1149.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1147.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So it''s like they haven''t booked yet, but they''ve requested one.","index":369,"end_time":1155.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1152.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we need to follow up and get that booked.","index":370,"end_time":1158.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1155.3,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That could work.","index":371,"end_time":1161.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1160.82,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think this might play into.","index":372,"end_time":1174.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1172.59,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"All right, that could work.","index":373,"end_time":1183.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1182.35,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"However.","index":374,"end_time":1184.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1183.79,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I do.","index":375,"end_time":1189.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1188.75,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So one thing I want to mention is that because it ties into this, is that Kirk, I guess he had a conversation with Mike and Cook and they wanted to let me know that LinkedIn leads should not be considered MQLs until or unless there is a reciprocal motion after Kristin connects with them.","index":376,"end_time":1223.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1199.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Just passing this on.","index":377,"end_time":1227.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1226.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So I haven''t written back yet because I know we''ve gone around in circles a lot on what we call these things, whether it''s mql, SQL, whatever, whatever, whatever.","index":378,"end_time":1241.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1229.16,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"The kind of lead, it is a good lead, a bad lead.","index":379,"end_time":1244.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1241.96,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"The ones that sales wants.","index":380,"end_time":1246.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1245,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"The ones that sales doesn''t want to.","index":381,"end_time":1249.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1246.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How to, you know, track them throughout the, the, the, the cycle stages.","index":382,"end_time":1256.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1249.73,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think we keep coming up against this challenge of the life cycle stage holding, assuming value of the lead, as opposed to where a lifecycle stage, typically in marketing speak, is just a stage.","index":383,"end_time":1281.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1259.09,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s just a marker of where they''re at.","index":384,"end_time":1284.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1281.42,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Whereas I think historically I Corps has often used the life cycle stage to suggest how good of a lead it is.","index":385,"end_time":1295.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1285.9,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Where.","index":386,"end_time":1297.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1297.26,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s why we came up with the.","index":387,"end_time":1299.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1298.14,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Lead detail and lead status properties to further indicate that like type or value piece of like what type of a lead is this?","index":388,"end_time":1318.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1304.31,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"What type of a thing?","index":389,"end_time":1320.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1318.07,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So like this.","index":390,"end_time":1323.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1322.79,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So anyway, I''m just struggling with this because I think this is also tied into that because this is, this is not just a lead who downloaded a piece of content.","index":391,"end_time":1338.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1324.79,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"This is a lead who filled out a Contact Us form for all intents and purposes.","index":392,"end_time":1345.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1339.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":393,"end_time":1346.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1346.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Which in the normal world, if somebody were to fill out Contact Us on our website, they come in as an MQL and then after sales talks to them, they decide whether they''re sales qualified or not.","index":394,"end_time":1365.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1347.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":395,"end_time":1366.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1365.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So now I think the question is the ones a step below that.","index":396,"end_time":1377.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1369.21,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":397,"end_time":1377.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1377.25,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"These, the LinkedIn ABM leads or leads that are not explicitly raising their hand of yes, I''m ready to have a meeting, but they are saying yes, I want your content.","index":398,"end_time":1390.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1377.61,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think Mike and Cook want us to call them something different.","index":399,"end_time":1396.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1392.32,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":400,"end_time":1397.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Until Kristen can touch base with them or something.","index":401,"end_time":1404.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1399.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I don''t know if they want to do that because they don''t realize they already have like a, like we already have a first follow up, second follow up.","index":402,"end_time":1412.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1404.96,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like we already have a way to track whether she''s interacted or not.","index":403,"end_time":1416.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1412.96,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So.","index":404,"end_time":1419.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1419,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":405,"end_time":1421.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1420.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s where my.","index":406,"end_time":1422.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1421.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":407,"end_time":1422.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1422.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"What do you think, Sam?","index":408,"end_time":1423.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1422.72,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":409,"end_time":1424.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1423.8,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I mean I, to me it''s an mql.","index":410,"end_time":1432.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1427.32,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":411,"end_time":1432.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1432.2,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, so I bet.","index":412,"end_time":1435.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1433.88,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So they don''t know about the first follow up and second follow up and stuff like that.","index":413,"end_time":1438.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1435.97,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Like, I mean, I can''t imagine that they.","index":414,"end_time":1440.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1438.93,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"No, I mean I, I can''t imagine.","index":415,"end_time":1443.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1442.37,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That you''ve probably explained it before, but they might not remember.","index":416,"end_time":1446.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1443.93,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":417,"end_time":1447.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1446.69,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yes.","index":418,"end_time":1448.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1447.57,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I would say to them the only lingo or lead lingo that they''ve.","index":419,"end_time":1456.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1448.37,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That they, that that ever comes up is just the stage, the lifecycle stage.","index":420,"end_time":1460.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1456.69,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s either a lead, an MQL or an SQL or an opportunity or customer.","index":421,"end_time":1463.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1460.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Anything else in HubSpot, all those other stages, I don''t think they really grasp them.","index":422,"end_time":1472.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1463.89,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But it.","index":423,"end_time":1473.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1472.98,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because they don''t really have to, I think.","index":424,"end_time":1477.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1474.66,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":425,"end_time":1478.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1477.86,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"So I mean do they want to create another life cycle stage, like another step?","index":426,"end_time":1482.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1478.5,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I don''t know because I.","index":427,"end_time":1484.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1483.22,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"That''s the other thing that we''ve talked about in the past is for a while and you''ll See in the notes, Natalie, like, when we first started with you guys, there was talk about doing a sales accepted lead and a sales qualified lead.","index":428,"end_time":1500.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1484.74,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So the additional life cycle stage would be sales accepted, which would mean.","index":429,"end_time":1506.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1501.28,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"They like it.","index":430,"end_time":1516.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1515.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But it''s not perfect.","index":431,"end_time":1521.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1518.72,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":432,"end_time":1522.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1522.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I also don''t know what value that gives us either because, like, the goal is to get a deal.","index":433,"end_time":1528.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1522.65,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, I don''t.","index":434,"end_time":1529.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1528.89,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But they also want to be able to track like, the quality of the leads.","index":435,"end_time":1533.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1530.57,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":436,"end_time":1533.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1533.41,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, how well is marketing bringing in leads and what do they look like and are they good or not?","index":437,"end_time":1539.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1533.61,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But that''s, I think, why we had the lead detail, because it would tell you if it''s.","index":438,"end_time":1544.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1539.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Sure, it''s an MQO, but some MQLs are unqualified because they''re out of the country, and some MQLs are unqualified because they went dark, and some SQLs get unqualified because they went dark.","index":439,"end_time":1562.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1545.13,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So I don''t know.","index":440,"end_time":1568.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1564.32,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I''m stuck.","index":441,"end_time":1569.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1568.32,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think maybe we should have like a marketing operations, like powwow.","index":442,"end_time":1576.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1569.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":443,"end_time":1577.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1577.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Regroup, debrief thing, like moving into the new year, like reassess the ops plan, clarify these properties, what the values mean.","index":444,"end_time":1590.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1577.61,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, and just make sure, like, everything is rolling up to this common goal of.","index":445,"end_time":1596.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1590.97,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We cohesively want good leads that make it all the way through.","index":446,"end_time":1612.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1601.3,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":447,"end_time":1614.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1613.62,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But we also want to be able to show how many crappy leads we had and how many good leads we had.","index":448,"end_time":1623.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1614.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then further, we want to show how many leads didn''t make it out of SQL or didn''t make it out of MQL and why.","index":449,"end_time":1634.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1624.39,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think we have a lot of that.","index":450,"end_time":1636.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1635.27,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I really do.","index":451,"end_time":1637.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1636.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But we just keep kind of like circling around on it.","index":452,"end_time":1643.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1638.15,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think it''s because of, like, It''s just different perspectives.","index":453,"end_time":1651.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1643.35,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":454,"end_time":1651.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1651.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, I have a marketing perspective on this and Kirk has very much a sales perspective on this.","index":455,"end_time":1657.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1651.88,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think Mike and Cook also very much have a sales perspective as well because their number one is closing this business.","index":456,"end_time":1664.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1657.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Let''s close it.","index":457,"end_time":1665.279,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1664.56,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Close it.","index":458,"end_time":1665.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.279,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Close it.","index":459,"end_time":1666.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1665.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Whereas sometimes my perspective ends up being cool.","index":460,"end_time":1672.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1668,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"My job is to bring you good leads so that you can close them.","index":461,"end_time":1677.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1672.8,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I. I can only.","index":462,"end_time":1680.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1679.39,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We can only do so much until a certain point, at which point it becomes.","index":463,"end_time":1688.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1682.51,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s in sales court, you know?","index":464,"end_time":1692.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1689.31,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":465,"end_time":1692.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1692.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And I don''t care what we call stuff, I don''t care what we label it as.","index":466,"end_time":1697.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1694.03,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"As long as it makes sense and it helps us with reporting and reaching our goals.","index":467,"end_time":1702.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1697.63,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, we could call it a strawberry lead.","index":468,"end_time":1705.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1702.11,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t care.","index":469,"end_time":1706.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1705.75,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":470,"end_time":1707.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1707.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"It''s just a naming system.","index":471,"end_time":1708.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1707.75,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You know, it has to.","index":472,"end_time":1710.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1708.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think that''s where marketing qualified lead for them communicates value.","index":473,"end_time":1716.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1710.71,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"They think a marketing qualified lead is better than a regular lead.","index":474,"end_time":1724.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1717.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So somebody filling out a form to download an IT guide they don''t think is as good as somebody filling out a forum saying that they want to actually book a meeting.","index":475,"end_time":1740.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1726.63,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I get that.","index":476,"end_time":1742.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1741.22,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That does make sense.","index":477,"end_time":1743.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1742.1,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But it''s still a lead that was qualified through marketing tactics, through segmentation and research.","index":478,"end_time":1754.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1744.18,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And like we did all of this, like work with the Personas and the, you know, the number of employees.","index":479,"end_time":1763.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1754.98,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, it''s not just a random lead.","index":480,"end_time":1766.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1763.4,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It is, you know what I mean?","index":481,"end_time":1768.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1766.2,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Probably too early in the morning to talk about this.","index":482,"end_time":1772.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1770.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":483,"end_time":1775.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1775.32,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think, I think also what they''re saying is then there''s a difference between who''s worse following up with.","index":484,"end_time":1782.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1776.52,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":485,"end_time":1783.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1782.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because if, like, if it''s someone that just downloaded a piece of content, they don''t want that to be an mql.","index":486,"end_time":1789.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1783.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Does that mean Kristen doesn''t follow up with them then?","index":487,"end_time":1792.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1789.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think she''s.","index":488,"end_time":1795.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1794.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think she does.","index":489,"end_time":1796.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1795.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think it''s.","index":490,"end_time":1798.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1797.55,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It maybe just changes the.","index":491,"end_time":1800.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1798.35,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Maybe it just changes the approach to her follow up to where she.","index":492,"end_time":1806.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1801.39,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because like, Kristen''s really good at being persistent.","index":493,"end_time":1810.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1807.9,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, she''s very on top of things.","index":494,"end_time":1812.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1810.38,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"She''s very like, she''s a go getter.","index":495,"end_time":1813.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1812.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t know what the word is there, but.","index":496,"end_time":1815.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1813.86,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"She''s on top of it.","index":497,"end_time":1822.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1821.5,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like she, she''s the kind of person where like if you get her on the phone, like you, you''re coming out of that call with a meeting or you''re coming out of that call like with a plan.","index":498,"end_time":1834.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1825.18,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So I think that''s maybe where they''re looking at, like they want her to spend her time on the most.","index":499,"end_time":1845.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1838.39,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"On the biggest fruit.","index":500,"end_time":1849.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1848.79,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I guess, if that makes sense.","index":501,"end_time":1851.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1849.99,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":502,"end_time":1852.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1851.75,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, that makes sense.","index":503,"end_time":1853.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1852.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think that makes sense.","index":504,"end_time":1856.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1855.11,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"As long as it means we''re not disregarding the other ones just because.","index":505,"end_time":1862.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1856.19,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Explicitly asking for a sales call.","index":506,"end_time":1865.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1863.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":507,"end_time":1866.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1865.92,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":508,"end_time":1868.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1867.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":509,"end_time":1870.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1869.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, I think having a marketing operations meeting is a good idea.","index":510,"end_time":1874.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1870.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe in the new year, just like sitting down.","index":511,"end_time":1878.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1874.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And we do have that marketing operations plan.","index":512,"end_time":1880.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1878.08,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":513,"end_time":1881.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1881.28,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That we have for you that kind of outlines each stage explicitly.","index":514,"end_time":1885.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1881.84,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we can just revisit that.","index":515,"end_time":1886.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1885.12,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":516,"end_time":1887.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1886.96,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think we definitely need to revisit just to make sure it''s up to snuff with everything we''ve learned from the year.","index":517,"end_time":1893.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1887.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":518,"end_time":1894.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1893.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And get folks on the same page.","index":519,"end_time":1897.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1896.24,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then for this one, if there.","index":520,"end_time":1905.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1901.2,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"For now, I would say we''re not changing the lifecycle stage at all for this.","index":521,"end_time":1914.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1910.32,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"This is still an mql.","index":522,"end_time":1916.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1914.88,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"This is an MQL in its purest.","index":523,"end_time":1918.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1916.2,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But on the surface, it''s not sending the same signals as a form fill on the website does, which is what we.","index":524,"end_time":1928.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1920.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And they all take like, super seriously.","index":525,"end_time":1932.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1929.34,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, oh my God, we got a lead.","index":526,"end_time":1933.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1932.74,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s gold.","index":527,"end_time":1934.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1933.7,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Somebody like, right back immediately.","index":528,"end_time":1936.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1934.54,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So.","index":529,"end_time":1938.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1937.82,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":530,"end_time":1940.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1940.54,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And this is an anomaly because it''s part of that retargeting.","index":531,"end_time":1943.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1940.94,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But this also shows that retargeting works.","index":532,"end_time":1945.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1943.38,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":533,"end_time":1946.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1946.37,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We also got an amazing client a couple weeks back that came in through content and they''re like, they, they''re in the deal stage now and they''re awesome.","index":534,"end_time":1961.969,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1947.33,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But they''ve actually been in HubSpot and been getting stuff from us for years.","index":535,"end_time":1972.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1962.69,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Years?","index":536,"end_time":1975.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1975.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, like nine years.","index":537,"end_time":1977.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1976.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And we just closed them.","index":538,"end_time":1980.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1978.78,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Wow.","index":539,"end_time":1982.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1981.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And there was a, you know, conversation of like, oh, wow, like, where did this lead come from?","index":540,"end_time":1986.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1982.54,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, was this from abm?","index":541,"end_time":1987.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1986.38,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Was this from whatever?","index":542,"end_time":1988.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1987.7,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I didn''t have an answer right in that moment when we were talking about it on the sales call.","index":543,"end_time":1992.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1989.1,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But I looked further into it.","index":544,"end_time":1993.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1992.5,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I was like, oh, man.","index":545,"end_time":1995.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1994.22,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":546,"end_time":1996.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1995.5,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like, they''ve been in here for a really long time.","index":547,"end_time":1998.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1996.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So we have been staying top of mind for them.","index":548,"end_time":2002.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1999.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We had like, and the time was right and we popped.","index":549,"end_time":2005.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2002.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"When we popped, they landed on the contact.","index":550,"end_time":2007.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2005.8,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"They actually landed on services and Solutions.","index":551,"end_time":2010.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2008.04,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That was their first converting site and then boom, meeting and then deal.","index":552,"end_time":2016.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2010.16,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":553,"end_time":2018.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2017.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So that''s cool.","index":554,"end_time":2019.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2018.84,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":555,"end_time":2020.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2020.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, that''s exactly what we, we have to do is just stay in front of people.","index":556,"end_time":2024.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2020.68,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":557,"end_time":2025.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2025.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And taking time is just right.","index":558,"end_time":2026.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2025.21,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":559,"end_time":2029.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2028.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I.","index":560,"end_time":2033.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2032.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Let me see about this one.","index":561,"end_time":2037.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2036.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So you said that adding in meeting requested would be good for now at least.","index":562,"end_time":2042.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2037.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"At least.","index":563,"end_time":2043.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2043.05,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":564,"end_time":2044.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2044.17,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"But it real, it will.","index":565,"end_time":2046.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2045.45,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I''m just nervous about that because it''s going to totally, like, it''ll change like the routing.","index":566,"end_time":2054.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2046.85,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":567,"end_time":2055.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2055.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Not really because like, Sam, you know how when we get a form fill on the website, we all get an email.","index":568,"end_time":2063.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2056.18,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":569,"end_time":2064.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2064.1,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Kirk takes a look and then the chosen people follow up and it''s kind of like a everybody knows about it kind of a thing.","index":570,"end_time":2076.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2064.9,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":571,"end_time":2077.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2077.33,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Adding a meeting requested property or dropdown into that thing, As long as we could tie that into the flow for actual Contact Us forms also.","index":572,"end_time":2104.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2084.21,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":573,"end_time":2106.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2105.85,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like, it should limit the notification.","index":574,"end_time":2108.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2106.33,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":575,"end_time":2108.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2108.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Just so it''s like.","index":576,"end_time":2109.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2108.41,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Because maybe that would bring it together in a better way even for reporting.","index":577,"end_time":2115.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2111.45,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So we could say like, all right, show me every mql.","index":578,"end_time":2120.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2115.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s Ever had a custom lead status of meeting requested and then ideally those form fills or first conversions or whatever would be either a Contact Us form or this free it Check any other thing where we have them where the call to action is like, hey, I want to book a meeting.","index":579,"end_time":2145.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2120.29,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"So if they fill up the form, it would just be meeting requested automatically.","index":580,"end_time":2149.019,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2146.1,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Right.","index":581,"end_time":2149.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2149.019,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Is interesting.","index":582,"end_time":2149.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2149.18,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":583,"end_time":2150.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2149.94,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":584,"end_time":2150.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2150.42,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":585,"end_time":2151.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2150.82,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":586,"end_time":2154.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2153.78,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll check if our developers.","index":587,"end_time":2156.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2154.9,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Maybe there''s a way, like if someone fills up in that form on LinkedIn, we can mimic the same kind of notifications that you get with a website form.","index":588,"end_time":2166.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2156.34,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, let me see.","index":589,"end_time":2169.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2168.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s probably a workflow.","index":590,"end_time":2171.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2170.24,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You do like a communication workflow.","index":591,"end_time":2173.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2171.52,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"There are examples of them.","index":592,"end_time":2185.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2183.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":593,"end_time":2188.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2187.7,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That we use for.","index":594,"end_time":2189.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2188.42,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"When somebody books a meeting.","index":595,"end_time":2195.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2194.02,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You''ll.","index":596,"end_time":2200.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2200.26,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You''ll.","index":597,"end_time":2201.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2200.7,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":598,"end_time":2201.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2201.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Run it by them if they need help or if you need to see an example or whatever.","index":599,"end_time":2205.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2201.46,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I mean, you guys have access to all of our stuff, so.","index":600,"end_time":2207.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2205.38,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it''s like discovery meeting booked is the workflow and it just shows like, I wouldn''t clone that specifically, but just to get an idea of.","index":601,"end_time":2218.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2208.1,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like.","index":602,"end_time":2219.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2218.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Who it gets sent to, it basically just needs to get sent to everyone on the sales leads group.","index":603,"end_time":2225.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2220.91,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I can send it really quick in the chat.","index":604,"end_time":2228.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2226.51,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Okay.","index":605,"end_time":2230.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2230.03,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Thank you, Sam.","index":606,"end_time":2235.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2234.59,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yep.","index":607,"end_time":2236.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2235.63,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":608,"end_time":2242.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2240.52,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Sorry for the long vent session, but.","index":609,"end_time":2246.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2242.28,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"No, that''s all good to know.","index":610,"end_time":2248.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2246.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":611,"end_time":2250.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2250.04,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And it would be helpful.","index":612,"end_time":2251.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2250.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, we should be on the same page as Kirk, so.","index":613,"end_time":2255.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2251.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, happy to meet with everyone and try to get all aligned on it.","index":614,"end_time":2261.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2255.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"What do we think?","index":615,"end_time":2266.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2265.89,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Is this a after Christmas thing?","index":616,"end_time":2269.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2266.33,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":617,"end_time":2271.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2269.57,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Definitely.","index":618,"end_time":2273.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2273.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, everything''s after Christmas now.","index":619,"end_time":2275.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2273.69,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I love it.","index":620,"end_time":2276.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2275.61,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":621,"end_time":2278.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2277.97,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then for SEO.","index":622,"end_time":2282.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2280.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, thank you for sending those pages to Jeff again.","index":623,"end_time":2285.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2282.77,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Did my response to him make sense about the SEO keywords when he asked about like doing using the IP address tool to route people to the correct page?","index":624,"end_time":2298.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2286.29,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So the tool he gave you, the geo target, targetly, is the one he.","index":625,"end_time":2304.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2299.9,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"You''re talking about.","index":626,"end_time":2304.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2304.06,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Yes.","index":627,"end_time":2305.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2305.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":628,"end_time":2307.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2306.86,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I think it made sense.","index":629,"end_time":2310.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2309.18,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it made sense and.","index":630,"end_time":2313.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2310.7,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"I think he''s good with it.","index":631,"end_time":2314.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2313.62,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I think.","index":632,"end_time":2315.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2314.74,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Find the email again.","index":633,"end_time":2320.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2319.48,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Where is it?","index":634,"end_time":2321.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2320.36,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"They did bring it up in our meetings yesterday and I basically was like, hey, there, the pages are done.","index":635,"end_time":2331.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2323.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We did all the edits.","index":636,"end_time":2332.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2331.48,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Jeff had some questions about geotargeting and we are discussing it.","index":637,"end_time":2338.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2333.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then he had asked me, okay, even if we don''t do that specific like IP routing stuff, what hap.","index":638,"end_time":2349.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2341.16,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"How is a person who''s in, I don''t know, somewhere getting to our page, getting to that page and I said, they''re typing in managed it near me in Google.","index":639,"end_time":2365.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2349.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That''s the correct answer, right?","index":640,"end_time":2368.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2366.88,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":641,"end_time":2368.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2368.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Or any of the other keywords that we''ve identified that drive to this page because they''re on the page.","index":642,"end_time":2377.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2370,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":643,"end_time":2378.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2378.53,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And those pages would show up because of the keyword they put in.","index":644,"end_time":2384.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2380.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Like Philadelphia wouldn''t show up for Boston, for example.","index":645,"end_time":2388.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2385.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Right.","index":646,"end_time":2390.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2389.73,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Do we have a list of.","index":647,"end_time":2392.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2390.53,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I know, I know we do.","index":648,"end_time":2394.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2393.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Somewhere.","index":649,"end_time":2394.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2394.17,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Like the list of all the keywords that we identified.","index":650,"end_time":2397.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2395.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":651,"end_time":2401.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2401.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"For each page.","index":652,"end_time":2402.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2401.42,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":653,"end_time":2403.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2402.62,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I can send that over.","index":654,"end_time":2404.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2403.34,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"All right, that''d be cool.","index":655,"end_time":2405.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2404.78,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I''ll show that to Jeff and be like, hey, these are the ones.","index":656,"end_time":2408.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2405.82,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then he''s going to want to know, well, why these ones?","index":657,"end_time":2411.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2408.94,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And then the explanation there is you guys use.","index":658,"end_time":2415.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2412.3,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"What is the tool semrush.","index":659,"end_time":2421.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2419.26,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s not.","index":660,"end_time":2422.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2421.5,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"You guys don''t use semrush.","index":661,"end_time":2423.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2422.06,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Right.","index":662,"end_time":2423.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2423.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"You use something different.","index":663,"end_time":2424.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2423.5,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Ahrefs.","index":664,"end_time":2426.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2426.39,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":665,"end_time":2427.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2426.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So you''ve run them all through ahrefs and you''ve run them for, like, difficult difficulty ranking volume, something like that.","index":666,"end_time":2438.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2427.67,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, we.","index":667,"end_time":2440.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2439.43,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So we look at the number of monthly searches for the keyword and the difficulty to rank and then decide which ones we think we could rank well for.","index":668,"end_time":2451.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2440.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So low difficulty, high monthly search volume.","index":669,"end_time":2454.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2451.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":670,"end_time":2457.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2454.72,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That all makes sense to me.","index":671,"end_time":2458.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2457.44,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I know you''ve explained it multiple times, but.","index":672,"end_time":2460.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2458.52,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"If at some point between now and next week, you want to throw together a quick recap email of like, this SEO targeting for.","index":673,"end_time":2473.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2464.64,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"In relation to these pages, and, you know, here''s the list of keywords, and this is how we use ahrefs to get here.","index":674,"end_time":2485.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2473.2,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":675,"end_time":2486.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2486.07,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":676,"end_time":2487.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2487.35,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think he just wants to see behind the curtain of the process to ensure that we''re checking all the boxes.","index":677,"end_time":2493.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2488.07,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I know we are, but he wants to know also.","index":678,"end_time":2498.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2493.75,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, and sometimes when I tell him, it doesn''t.","index":679,"end_time":2502.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2499.51,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Doesn''t work.","index":680,"end_time":2507.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2506.83,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":681,"end_time":2510.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2509.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Jeff is very thorough.","index":682,"end_time":2511.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2510.15,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I''ll send over the keywords we''re using for each page, the monthly search volume here and the difficulty, and then also what those mean and why we selected those keywords.","index":683,"end_time":2524.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2511.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And that further we can then go back in and track as.","index":684,"end_time":2530.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2527.08,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"As they perform.","index":685,"end_time":2532.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2531.4,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, that was everything I had.","index":686,"end_time":2533.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2532.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Anything else you wanted to discuss?","index":687,"end_time":2535.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2534.2,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"No, I think that''s it.","index":688,"end_time":2538.6,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2537.4,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"All right.","index":689,"end_time":2541.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2541.24,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, actually, no.","index":690,"end_time":2542.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2541.72,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":691,"end_time":2543.119,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2542.76,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"One more thing.","index":692,"end_time":2543.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2543.119,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That 404, just like, page health wise, is there a way we can make sure that we don''t have stuff out there that''s got bad links?","index":693,"end_time":2560.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2543.76,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, that leads to a 404.","index":694,"end_time":2565.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2561.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":695,"end_time":2566.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2565.49,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I mean, that might be like a project, but I do think.","index":696,"end_time":2572.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2566.01,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"And I think Jeff would probably agree that''s something that we should.","index":697,"end_time":2575.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2572.13,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"That needs to be part of maybe some of these management tasks or like the just ongoing website upkeep stuff.","index":698,"end_time":2585.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2575.57,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":699,"end_time":2587.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2586.95,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ve made a note of that.","index":700,"end_time":2591.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2590.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it''s going to.","index":701,"end_time":2596.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2594.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We''re going to need to especially go through past blog posts because we updated copy on the landing pages.","index":702,"end_time":2605.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2598.71,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So, like, even when we''re linking something there, it should be to a current page.","index":703,"end_time":2609.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2605.99,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Blog posts though, like, aren''t updated, so those might be leading to old URLs.","index":704,"end_time":2617.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2610.44,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, I see what you mean.","index":705,"end_time":2619.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2618.12,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":706,"end_time":2620.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2619.72,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":707,"end_time":2622.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2621.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"But I think we can do.","index":708,"end_time":2623.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2622.28,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Probably do a scan of the whole, like, blog site and see if there are any that are leading to 404s.","index":709,"end_time":2631.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2623.64,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll check with our web people.","index":710,"end_time":2633.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2631.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":711,"end_time":2635.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2634.52,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":712,"end_time":2639.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2639.41,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Cool.","index":713,"end_time":2643.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2643.41,"speaker_name":"Samuel Bagnall"},{"text":"Oh, and then just for next week, I''ll be out next week on the 24th.","index":714,"end_time":2649.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2645.49,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":715,"end_time":2650.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2650.21,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Wednesday.","index":716,"end_time":2651.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2651.09,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So if you''d like, I''m still happy to meet.","index":717,"end_time":2653.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2651.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"We can do maybe Tuesday next week or Friday.","index":718,"end_time":2657.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2653.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Up to you.","index":719,"end_time":2659.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2658.69,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"And then I''m out for the week after that as well.","index":720,"end_time":2662.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2659.81,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So just so that we don''t miss two weeks in a row, I can send you the scheduling link for next week and see if you still want to meet.","index":721,"end_time":2671.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2663.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''m cool with.","index":722,"end_time":2682.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2680.77,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Let''s just meet on the 7th.","index":723,"end_time":2685.652,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2683.17,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"7Th of January.","index":724,"end_time":2687.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2685.928,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s just make it easy.","index":725,"end_time":2689.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2688.37,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Okay.","index":726,"end_time":2691.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2690.68,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Take the time off.","index":727,"end_time":2692.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2691.32,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"We all have time off.","index":728,"end_time":2693.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2692.44,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s.","index":729,"end_time":2694.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2693.88,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"It''s fine.","index":730,"end_time":2696.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2695.24,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"Everything we talked about today, I know everyone will be working on between now and when we meet again, so I don''t.","index":731,"end_time":2705.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2696.6,"speaker_name":"Ruby Pontbriand"},{"text":"I don''t think we nee