 and balance point overage (24:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Finalize internal agreement to reset negative points balance and establish monthly scoped plans to control overage (24:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide monthly spreadsheets detailing scope and points usage for transparency and planning (24:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist team with strategy for optimizing LinkedIn audience size and campaign efficiency (26:31)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
