,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"She''s.","index":458,"end_time":1053.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1052.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"She''s the only one wearing red.","index":459,"end_time":1054.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1053.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re good.","index":460,"end_time":1055.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1054.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know what I mean?","index":461,"end_time":1056.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1055.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, that was.","index":462,"end_time":1056.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1056.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That was.","index":463,"end_time":1056.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1056.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think that was fine.","index":464,"end_time":1057.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1057,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Unless you want to change it to the.","index":465,"end_time":1059.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1057.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The yellow band around the cup to the red instead.","index":466,"end_time":1063.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1059.72,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I wouldn''t say no to that, but I think it''s fine the way it is.","index":467,"end_time":1067.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1063.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The next one.","index":468,"end_time":1071.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1070.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":469,"end_time":1072.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1071.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I know we have these kind of more vertical ones, and some of them look really great, and I''m wondering if we can do like a vertical and a horizontal version.","index":470,"end_time":1081.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1072.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":471,"end_time":1082.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.88,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Of them.","index":472,"end_time":1083.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1082.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that would be great.","index":473,"end_time":1085.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1084.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, maybe.","index":474,"end_time":1088.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1086.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":475,"end_time":1088.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1088.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I said, maybe just a touch lighter.","index":476,"end_time":1090.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1088.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like when you go to the next one, it''s the same people, but they are there.","index":477,"end_time":1096.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1090.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":478,"end_time":1096.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1096.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s quite a bit lighter.","index":479,"end_time":1098.03,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1096.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":480,"end_time":1099.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1098.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":481,"end_time":1100.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1099.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I wouldn''t.","index":482,"end_time":1100.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1100.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I wouldn''t say no to this one being horizontal as well.","index":483,"end_time":1102.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1100.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then to your point, pick a red.","index":484,"end_time":1104.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1102.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, it could be the band behind him, the cup, the book.","index":485,"end_time":1107.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1104.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like just one of these elements.","index":486,"end_time":1108.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1107.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Red would be fine.","index":487,"end_time":1109.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1108.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah, I think she was fine.","index":488,"end_time":1114.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1110.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":489,"end_time":1116.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1115.86,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So I wanted to ask about the GUI for our.","index":490,"end_time":1119.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1116.5,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, Yeah.","index":491,"end_time":1120.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1119.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":492,"end_time":1121.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1120.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I checked my files and I don''t have.","index":493,"end_time":1122.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1121.26,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Don''t you.","index":494,"end_time":1124.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1123.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You don''t have any Google images.","index":495,"end_time":1125.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1124.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, let me send you.","index":496,"end_time":1127.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1125.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me send you a couple and you guys can play.","index":497,"end_time":1130.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1127.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I.","index":498,"end_time":1131.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1130.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, these are the same ones that you can grab from, like, The.","index":499,"end_time":1134.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1131.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The sales guide.","index":500,"end_time":1135.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1134.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like the IPM sales guide.","index":501,"end_time":1136.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1135.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''ll be exactly the same.","index":502,"end_time":1138.1,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1136.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s what I was alluding to.","index":503,"end_time":1140.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1139.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, if you want me to send some product shots, I can do that.","index":504,"end_time":1143.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1140.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have an entire file of nothing but.","index":505,"end_time":1146.34,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1143.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":506,"end_time":1147.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1146.82,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, okay.","index":507,"end_time":1148.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1147.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, Let me do that.","index":508,"end_time":1149.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1148.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ll make a note and send you some.","index":509,"end_time":1151.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1149.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Some product shots.","index":510,"end_time":1152.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1151.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":511,"end_time":1153.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1152.74,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":512,"end_time":1154.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1154.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":513,"end_time":1157.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1156.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":514,"end_time":1157.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1157.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This gentleman I thought was fine, but again, horizontal.","index":515,"end_time":1160.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1157.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If we could as.","index":516,"end_time":1161.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1160.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, So I didn''t mind these people, except the man bun has got to go.","index":517,"end_time":1169.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1165.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ll never hear the end of it.","index":518,"end_time":1170.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1169.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And the.","index":519,"end_time":1173.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1170.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The red on the.","index":520,"end_time":1175.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1174.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What do you call it?","index":521,"end_time":1178.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1177.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The bottle.","index":522,"end_time":1179.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1178.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t mind the bottle being red, but it feels really orangey to me and I need it to be a bit more Rico red.","index":523,"end_time":1186.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1180.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":524,"end_time":1187.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1186.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If that can''t be done, just make it a clear bottle.","index":525,"end_time":1189.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1187.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And maybe her glasses on.","index":526,"end_time":1191.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1189.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The lady on the left wearing the yellow jacket could maybe be red or something like that.","index":527,"end_time":1196.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1191.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, like something subtle because it does kind of pull my eye a little bit.","index":528,"end_time":1201.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1196.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That.","index":529,"end_time":1201.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1201.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That.","index":530,"end_time":1201.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1201.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But it could just be the.","index":531,"end_time":1203.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1201.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That It''s a, you know, it''s just a different kind of red.","index":532,"end_time":1206.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1204.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":533,"end_time":1209.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1209.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"See, like I said, all red.","index":534,"end_time":1213.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1211.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All the.","index":535,"end_time":1213.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1213.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":536,"end_time":1220.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1219.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just, you know how it goes.","index":537,"end_time":1221.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1220.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just that little subtle hint of it is fine.","index":538,"end_time":1224.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1221.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":539,"end_time":1225.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1224.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then.","index":540,"end_time":1225.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1225.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think this one was okay.","index":541,"end_time":1229.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1227.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t mind it again, I think I said if we could do a horizontal version of it so her shoulder''s not cut off.","index":542,"end_time":1234.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1229.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, you know, we can.","index":543,"end_time":1235.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1234.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just find.","index":544,"end_time":1236.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1235.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I can play a bit more with ones that are horizontal.","index":545,"end_time":1238.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1236.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah.","index":546,"end_time":1240.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1239.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t mind the verticals, though, so don''t let me stop you with.","index":547,"end_time":1244.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1241.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"With something vertical.","index":548,"end_time":1246.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1245.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I will use a horizontal one more because this kind of thing we use, you know, in our PowerPoints.","index":549,"end_time":1251.74,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1246.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And if I were to try to use this, it would be.","index":550,"end_time":1253.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1251.74,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It could be a little bit difficult, but not the end of the world.","index":551,"end_time":1257.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1254.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s see the next lady.","index":552,"end_time":1260.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1258.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I thought that.","index":553,"end_time":1260.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1260.3,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think this lady was fine.","index":554,"end_time":1262.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1260.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":555,"end_time":1263.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1263.3,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Ah, yes.","index":556,"end_time":1266.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1265.7,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I like this.","index":557,"end_time":1268.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1266.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I like the idea of this image like a mail room and that kind of thing, but it was.","index":558,"end_time":1273.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1268.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It was coming across a little primary school for me because of all the different colored boxes.","index":559,"end_time":1279.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1273.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":560,"end_time":1279.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1279.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I''m wondering if maybe we can pull back a little bit on all the color.","index":561,"end_time":1285.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1280.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think a couple of the boxes being red would be fine to like, bring in that little bit of red, but the fact that everything else is like, you know, yellow and blue.","index":562,"end_time":1294.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1286.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I was getting primary school, but I did like the whole mail room, you know.","index":563,"end_time":1300.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1294.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thought process here.","index":564,"end_time":1301.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1300.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I did not show you.","index":565,"end_time":1304.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1302.39,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I know you sent over these as well.","index":566,"end_time":1307.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1304.87,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"When I was trying to find example images for this, I wanted to see would it ever come in like this, more bulk mail items?","index":567,"end_time":1318.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1309.83,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I mean, it could, but when I look at these bulk mail items, I think fulfillment.","index":568,"end_time":1324.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1320.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that''s something else again in our world, you know.","index":569,"end_time":1327.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1324.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But this mail room here, the bottom left with the blue top, that I think is maybe a bit closer to kind of what I was thinking.","index":570,"end_time":1337.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1328.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I do like the people.","index":571,"end_time":1338.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1337.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I also think this is probably like a courier because of those rolling grates on the left hand side.","index":572,"end_time":1346.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1339.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That kind of thing is usually what you see at a courier.","index":573,"end_time":1349.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1346.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Don''t ask.","index":574,"end_time":1350.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1349.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I used to work at a courier many, many moons ago.","index":575,"end_time":1353.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1350.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I, I, I kid you not.","index":576,"end_time":1355.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1353.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Those were the, those were the things we used to move, you know, mail around Canada, frankly.","index":577,"end_time":1364.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1355.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":578,"end_time":1368.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1364.18,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, I think you''re on the right track.","index":579,"end_time":1370.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1368.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just a little bit of fine tuning.","index":580,"end_time":1372.74,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1370.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":581,"end_time":1375.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1373.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":582,"end_time":1377.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1376.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And this guy thought, oh, lots of red.","index":583,"end_time":1378.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1377.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Pick one, you know.","index":584,"end_time":1380.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1378.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":585,"end_time":1386.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1381.23,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think this one was fine.","index":586,"end_time":1387.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1386.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It just felt when I was looking at it and it just could be, but I felt the ladies, their skin and their face, they looked like a little too perfect.","index":587,"end_time":1396.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1388.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":588,"end_time":1397.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1396.589,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just we can add some texture.","index":589,"end_time":1400.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.95,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":590,"end_time":1401.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1400.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just a little something, something.","index":591,"end_time":1403.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1401.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I mean, I wish my skin looked that good, but I don''t think it ever looked that good.","index":592,"end_time":1407.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1403.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, if we can just kind of make, give it a bit of texture, that would be good.","index":593,"end_time":1412.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1407.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And just make sure the red of the notebook is the, you know, the RICO red because it looks a little dull to me.","index":594,"end_time":1418.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1412.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":595,"end_time":1424.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1424.05,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":596,"end_time":1425.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1424.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And was that it?","index":597,"end_time":1425.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1425.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Was that the last one?","index":598,"end_time":1426.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1425.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yep, I think that was the last one.","index":599,"end_time":1428.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1427.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":600,"end_time":1430.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1428.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":601,"end_time":1431.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1430.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":602,"end_time":1431.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1431.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, I think we''re on the right track.","index":603,"end_time":1432.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1431.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just these things take a bit of time of going back and forth, these images to get them like, kind of like just spot on.","index":604,"end_time":1439.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1432.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think you''re in the right realm with all of these.","index":605,"end_time":1442.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1439.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then the three that I sent you will lean into that mailing like that top one with the, the computer.","index":606,"end_time":1451.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1442.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think that would be splendid to have.","index":607,"end_time":1454.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1451.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Rico.","index":608,"end_time":1456.79,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1456.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Predictive insight does a lot of, a lot of like, like I said in my note, like insurance forms, insurance statements, financial statements, bills, you know, like those, those, those kinds of things that like a, you know, like a hospital might do in bulk or an insurance company might do in bulk or some kind of financial company will do in bulk.","index":609,"end_time":1481.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1456.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s what that one on the bottom left is alluding to.","index":610,"end_time":1486.34,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1482.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t like that the computer has that whatever that financial thing on it because it''s leaning a little bit too hard into like that financial realm.","index":611,"end_time":1497.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1487.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But with those two on the left, I would love to have the.","index":612,"end_time":1501.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1497.68,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The product shot, like the RPD product shot on them.","index":613,"end_time":1505.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1501.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then on the right, what I was kind of getting to here is that they probably have a large, you know, a large plant somewhere where they''re printing off all of these, you know, statements, bills, that kind of thing.","index":614,"end_time":1523.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1505.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I like that it was pulled back far enough that you get the idea that it''s a.","index":615,"end_time":1527.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1523.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s a shop floor, but you can''t really see whose equipment it is.","index":616,"end_time":1532.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1527.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yay.","index":617,"end_time":1533.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1532.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because that''s always, you know, something hard to do.","index":618,"end_time":1535.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1533.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We don''t want to obviously highlight, you know, a competitor''s equipment, but this to me is just alludes to a shop floor.","index":619,"end_time":1541.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1535.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s nothing super colorful on those rollers.","index":620,"end_time":1544.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1542.05,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that would be the case with a, you know, with a company that would use rpd because nothing is really terribly flashy about a statement or a bill.","index":621,"end_time":1553.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1544.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we can find something kind of similar.","index":622,"end_time":1556.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1555.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think this would be good.","index":623,"end_time":1558.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1557.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then maybe, you know, we take one of these yellow elements as an example, maybe those girders across the top and make them red instead, just to instill that tiny bit of Ricoh red into them.","index":624,"end_time":1569.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1559.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But yeah, if we can find something that looks like a shop floor that''s pulled back far enough that you can''t really see what kind of press or what kind of finishing they''re using or any of that stuff to keep us legal, I would be over the moon.","index":625,"end_time":1584.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1569.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That might be harder to find, to be honest with you.","index":626,"end_time":1587.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1584.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":627,"end_time":1588.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1588.16,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it''s pretty similar.","index":628,"end_time":1590.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1588.8,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Was it the optimizer ones that we did maybe on a shop floor as well?","index":629,"end_time":1596.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1590.4,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I think.","index":630,"end_time":1597.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1596.76,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, you''re right.","index":631,"end_time":1598.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1597.84,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You guys did the.","index":632,"end_time":1599.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1598.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The ones where it was like stacks of stuff coming off of like a, you know, off of a.","index":633,"end_time":1604.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1599.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"A conveyor belt.","index":634,"end_time":1606.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1604.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, kind of like that, except it wouldn''t be stacked.","index":635,"end_time":1609.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1607.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So stuff.","index":636,"end_time":1610.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1609.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The reason I like those ones for Optimizer is because that''s what Optimizer does.","index":637,"end_time":1614.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1610.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It.","index":638,"end_time":1614.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1614.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It pulls together like items in a print job, prints them all off first or prints them all off together.","index":639,"end_time":1622.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1614.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And it.","index":640,"end_time":1623.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1622.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It shaves down on cost and waste.","index":641,"end_time":1625.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1623.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s why I love those ones.","index":642,"end_time":1627.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1626,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We use them all over the place because it, it, it image wise, it really pulls together what that product is doing, which is why I''m Leaning kind of heavy into this whole statements and bills conversation with rpd because that''s generally where it plays the best.","index":643,"end_time":1645.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1627.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"With IPM as an example.","index":644,"end_time":1648.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1647.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So Info Print Manager, that''s distributed print.","index":645,"end_time":1652.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1648.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we''re looking more at a company that may have 15 different locations across the U.S. let''s say, and they need to be able to print across all of those locations, whatever it is that they''re printing.","index":646,"end_time":1665.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1652.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s what distributed print is.","index":647,"end_time":1668.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1666.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So whereas RPD will generally maybe have one, maybe two locations if they''re a really big company.","index":648,"end_time":1675.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1669.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Distributed print is more, let''s think more government based where you could have like a department of something that''s across, like a federal department of something that could be across the entire country that people are talking back and forth and it''s like, here''s, here''s this important piece of documentation I need to send to some guy in Nebraska while I''m in, you.","index":649,"end_time":1695.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1676.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Know, Chicago kind of thing.","index":650,"end_time":1698.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1695.53,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s where the differences lie.","index":651,"end_time":1700.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1698.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''m trying to kind of lean into those image wise.","index":652,"end_time":1704.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1700.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I know they can, it can get really gray really quickly.","index":653,"end_time":1708.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1704.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I try to be, you know, really specific about the imagery for these two because it, they can go back and forth.","index":654,"end_time":1715.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1708.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that does happen occasionally with our customers where they''re like, oh, you know, process director isn''t working for us.","index":655,"end_time":1721.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1715.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let''s try ipm.","index":656,"end_time":1722.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1721.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, that works better for our particular, you know, like how our company is set up.","index":657,"end_time":1728.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1722.28,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we do sometimes have people flip flop between the two but for marketing purposes of course, I''m trying to keep it, you know, like that line down the middle of the two of them.","index":658,"end_time":1738.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1728.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So yeah, yeah, perfect.","index":659,"end_time":1741.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1738.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So we''ll.","index":660,"end_time":1742.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1741.97,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":661,"end_time":1744.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1744.09,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Everything you wanted to know about commercial print, Natalie, but didn''t know.","index":662,"end_time":1747.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1744.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know to come to you always.","index":663,"end_time":1751.769,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1750.17,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Oh, it''s, it''s not sexy.","index":664,"end_time":1754.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1752.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It really isn''t.","index":665,"end_time":1755.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1754.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"This is not, this is not an Apple iPhone.","index":666,"end_time":1759.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1756.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Much to my sugarin.","index":667,"end_time":1760.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1759.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Seeing that image on the right of the print floor kind of reminds me of some of the images made for Avanti as well.","index":668,"end_time":1769.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1764.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":669,"end_time":1770.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1770.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And while I was doing some research across the site, I do still see mentions of the Avanti tool.","index":670,"end_time":1777.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1771.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is there a relationship between RICO and Avanti Slingshot still?","index":671,"end_time":1780.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1777.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, yes, but no.","index":672,"end_time":1785.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1782.13,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think that if someone were to come to us and say, hey, I need you guys to integrate with Avanti, we can obviously still do that because those, what do you call it?","index":673,"end_time":1796.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1785.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Those, those connections are still there, right?","index":674,"end_time":1799.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1796.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, you know, like.","index":675,"end_time":1800.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1799.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":676,"end_time":1802.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1800.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The software guys are not going to pull the integrations out if they''re there, they''re there.","index":677,"end_time":1805.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1802.35,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Right.","index":678,"end_time":1805.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1805.55,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So in that regard, yes.","index":679,"end_time":1807.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1806.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But as far as a company and us owning them or have anything to do with them in that way, know that ship has failed.","index":680,"end_time":1814.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1807.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"They are.","index":681,"end_time":1815.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1814.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know, they have another eps, and.","index":682,"end_time":1818.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1815.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Then whoever EPS merged with.","index":683,"end_time":1819.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1818.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":684,"end_time":1821.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1820.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Pick an acronym with those beds.","index":685,"end_time":1822.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1821.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I have.","index":686,"end_time":1823.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1822.8,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, yeah, it''s.","index":687,"end_time":1824.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1823.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It started out as efi, then it was EFI and eps, and now I don''t know what they are like.","index":688,"end_time":1828.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1824.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just.","index":689,"end_time":1829.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1828.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s a little bit murky to me as well.","index":690,"end_time":1832.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1829.44,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But, yeah, those.","index":691,"end_time":1833.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1832.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s funny you should mention that.","index":692,"end_time":1834.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1833.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I didn''t want to because I didn''t want them to be the same, but that''s what I was thinking of when I was thinking shop floor.","index":693,"end_time":1841.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1834.56,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because those images that you guys did for the Avanti thing were perfect.","index":694,"end_time":1846.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1841.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m like, yes, that, but not that.","index":695,"end_time":1848.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1846.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes.","index":696,"end_time":1849.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1849.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, totally hear you.","index":697,"end_time":1851.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1849.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":698,"end_time":1852.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1851.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I just want to check if we needed to make any changes to any documents or anything that mentioned Avanti.","index":699,"end_time":1856.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1852.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, it''s really up to the regions to pull it.","index":700,"end_time":1861.189,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1857.11,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If it''s on a website somewhere, it''s up to Avanti to do whatever changes they need to do on their end to, you know, to.","index":701,"end_time":1869.75,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1861.189,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"To disengage, if you will, from rico.","index":702,"end_time":1872.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1869.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you''re seeing it out in the world, it''s probably a holdover, and someone''s just not, you know.","index":703,"end_time":1878.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1873.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You know how it goes.","index":704,"end_time":1878.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1878.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s like rebranding, you know, the name of the product that.","index":705,"end_time":1881.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1878.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The old name, you know, resurfaces in a bunch of weird places, and you''re like, I didn''t even know about that.","index":706,"end_time":1887.49,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1881.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s a similar kind of thing.","index":707,"end_time":1889.089,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1887.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":708,"end_time":1889.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1889.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":709,"end_time":1890.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1889.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":710,"end_time":1890.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1890.09,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":711,"end_time":1892.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1890.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":712,"end_time":1893.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1892.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":713,"end_time":1894.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1894.29,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anything else, Natalie?","index":714,"end_time":1896.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1895.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Or are.","index":715,"end_time":1897.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1896.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Are we good?","index":716,"end_time":1898.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1897.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know I kind of, like, dropped the.","index":717,"end_time":1899.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1898.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The RPD stuff sort of in your lap after we talked last time, so my apologies, but we''re getting into that now to, you know, to, like, change up some stuff.","index":718,"end_time":1911.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1900.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Lou, once we''re done with the IPM and Optimizer sales guides, I''ll be sending the old RPD sales guide over as well, to shift over.","index":719,"end_time":1922.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1912.36,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But I was just waiting to get these images locked down for rpd, because obviously, I want to use those in the.","index":720,"end_time":1928.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1923.16,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"In the new sales guide, so.","index":721,"end_time":1931.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1929.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s coming.","index":722,"end_time":1932.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1932.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I.","index":723,"end_time":1933.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1933.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We just need to nail down these images first so that you can use them in the sales guide and wherever else we may need them, so.","index":724,"end_time":1940.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1933.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Great.","index":725,"end_time":1941.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1940.66,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":726,"end_time":1941.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1941.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The brochure has images too, right?","index":727,"end_time":1945.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1943.38,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Or, you know, this brochure weirdly doesn''t.","index":728,"end_time":1950.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1946.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Have like a ton of.","index":729,"end_time":1951.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1950.06,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I shouldn''t say like, it has images, obviously, but it''s not like people images because it''s quite a thick brochure, text wise.","index":730,"end_time":1960.48,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1951.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"If you take.","index":731,"end_time":1962.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1962.08,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yes, if you take a look, you''ll see what I mean.","index":732,"end_time":1966.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1962.88,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, the images are like, of the, like the icons and it''s the bubble and, you know, it''s those elements.","index":733,"end_time":1973.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1966.04,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s nothing like the lady we''re looking at here on the right.","index":734,"end_time":1976.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1973.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"There''s not a lot of it there because frankly, we have more than we know.","index":735,"end_time":1980.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1976.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What we have a lot to say about rpd, it''s a historical product that''s been around for many, many years.","index":736,"end_time":1987.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1980.2,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So, yeah, it''s just not quite as swishy as the other one.","index":737,"end_time":1992.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1988.12,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s really similar to Info Print Manager where it''s, you know, it''s a big piece of software.","index":738,"end_time":1999,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1992.92,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s very specific about what it does, or at least we''re trying to be specific about what it does.","index":739,"end_time":2003.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1999.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So the images that we''re working on, you know, we''ll use them in the sales guide.","index":740,"end_time":2008.6,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2004.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll use them in the PowerPoint more than the brochure, which is why I sent the brochure through is because it really.","index":741,"end_time":2013.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2008.6,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The, you know, the biggest image on it is the hero image, which is not changing.","index":742,"end_time":2017.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2014.17,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":743,"end_time":2018.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2018.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah.","index":744,"end_time":2020.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2018.45,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, perfect.","index":745,"end_time":2023.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2021.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":746,"end_time":2024.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2023.85,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So once, once we''ve made the updates we talked about today with the sales guide, we''ll send it over.","index":747,"end_time":2028.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2024.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I''ll send an animated right now.","index":748,"end_time":2032.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2030.17,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay, sorry.","index":749,"end_time":2033.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2032.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Working on it right now.","index":750,"end_time":2035.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2034.57,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":751,"end_time":2036.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2036.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, Very good.","index":752,"end_time":2038.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2036.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll send it.","index":753,"end_time":2039.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2038.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''ll send it for this video today once it''s done, and then we''ll get started on these image updates as well.","index":754,"end_time":2044.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2039.65,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":755,"end_time":2045.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2045.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right, Sounds good.","index":756,"end_time":2047.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2046.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":757,"end_time":2047.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2047.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So a lot''s going on as usual.","index":758,"end_time":2051.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2048.21,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then like I said, once we f. Finish up with these RPD images, I''ll send over the sales guide so that we can start morphing that over.","index":759,"end_time":2064.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2051.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I''ll have to take a look at the PowerPoint.","index":760,"end_time":2068.49,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2065.65,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t have the updated content yet from the PM.","index":761,"end_time":2072.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2068.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s.","index":762,"end_time":2072.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2072.61,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ve got a bit of time with RPD.","index":763,"end_time":2074.969,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2073.369,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s not set to go off, like, to launch until April, but I would like to try and get everything done towards the end of February for it, at least the PowerPoint and the brochure, those are the two elements that must go with every.","index":764,"end_time":2088.809,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2074.969,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Must go with every launch.","index":765,"end_time":2094.529,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2093.209,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And we try to get that out to the regions 30 days ahead of time.","index":766,"end_time":2097.609,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2094.529,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So the other stuff we can kind of, you know, like, that can come a little bit later, but the.","index":767,"end_time":2104.42,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2097.769,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The brochure and the PowerPoints are always the most important to the regions, and they want to get their hands on them earlier if they can.","index":768,"end_time":2110.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2104.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So that''s kind of my marketing line in the sand, so.","index":769,"end_time":2114.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2110.66,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":770,"end_time":2116.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2115.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":771,"end_time":2116.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2116.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think to probably what I can send over now, and I thought maybe I did already, but I guess I dreamed it was the RPD Battle card.","index":772,"end_time":2124.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2116.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That could probably go over to you guys right now as well to get put into the new template.","index":773,"end_time":2129.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2124.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Because I don''t think.","index":774,"end_time":2131.47,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2130.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t think much will change there, but we''ll see.","index":775,"end_time":2133.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2131.47,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":776,"end_time":2134.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2134.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And that one has no images again.","index":777,"end_time":2137.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2134.79,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, it just.","index":778,"end_time":2137.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2137.03,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It would just be the hero image.","index":779,"end_time":2138.95,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2137.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s just what you guys have done with the template.","index":780,"end_time":2141.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2138.95,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So it''s just the hero image stuff, you know, with the band down the side, and then everything else will be content.","index":781,"end_time":2146.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2141.19,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":782,"end_time":2146.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2146.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think we''re.","index":783,"end_time":2147.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2146.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''re good.","index":784,"end_time":2148.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2147.59,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The images are really used more in RPD land for the sales Guide and the PowerPoint.","index":785,"end_time":2154.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2148.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, we''ll work on that, too, once it''s.","index":786,"end_time":2158.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2155.18,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Once it''s in.","index":787,"end_time":2159.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2158.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":788,"end_time":2159.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2159.58,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":789,"end_time":2160.42,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2159.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I thought.","index":790,"end_time":2160.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2160.42,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like I said, I thought I did, but I. I guess I dreamed it because it''s all about you, Natalie.","index":791,"end_time":2166.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2160.78,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I dream about sending you briefs, Enrico.","index":792,"end_time":2170.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2166.22,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Red, All the grays.","index":793,"end_time":2175.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2170.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Oh, my God, the grays.","index":794,"end_time":2177.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2175.9,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I dream about the grays.","index":795,"end_time":2178.34,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2177.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"It''s so bad.","index":796,"end_time":2179.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2178.34,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I will send the battle card through either today or tomorrow.","index":797,"end_time":2184.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2181.25,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"We''ll see how that goes.","index":798,"end_time":2185.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2184.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay, so iou IPM product shots and.","index":799,"end_time":2191.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2186.93,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The RPD Battle Card.","index":800,"end_time":2193.49,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2191.77,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Natalie, I will send you a note.","index":801,"end_time":2195.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2193.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"When I''ve done all of that.","index":802,"end_time":2196.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2195.09,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Anything else from you guys, or are we good?","index":803,"end_time":2199.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2197.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think we''re good.","index":804,"end_time":2200.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2199.73,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re good.","index":805,"end_time":2202.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2201.25,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Only other thing, next week, Thursday, our meeting lands on Christmas.","index":806,"end_time":2206.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2202.45,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"So if you''d like, you can move it to Tuesday or Friday.","index":807,"end_time":2210.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2206.55,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s move it to.","index":808,"end_time":2212.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2211.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, why don''t we just move it to the following week?","index":809,"end_time":2215.27,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2212.99,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I think we''re in pretty good state.","index":810,"end_time":2218.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2216.31,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And if there''s anything, just send me a note, Natalie, like we''ve done in the past.","index":811,"end_time":2221.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2218.43,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"When it falls on a holiday, I''m.","index":812,"end_time":2223.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2221.67,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m heartbroken.","index":813,"end_time":2224.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2223.75,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You don''t want to talk to me on Christmas.","index":814,"end_time":2226.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2224.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I''m just heartbroken.","index":815,"end_time":2228.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2226.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"The week after.","index":816,"end_time":2233.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2232.48,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"I will actually be out that week.","index":817,"end_time":2235.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2233.6,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Will you.","index":818,"end_time":2235.76,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2235.24,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":819,"end_time":2236.32,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2235.76,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, I think if you''re free on Friday next week, we could do that.","index":820,"end_time":2240.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2236.56,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Just.","index":821,"end_time":2240.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2240.48,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah, just a sec.","index":822,"end_time":2242.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2241.52,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Let me see.","index":823,"end_time":2243.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2242.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That''s the 26th, so.","index":824,"end_time":2244.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2243.4,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No, the 26th for us happy Canadians is what we Call Boxing Day, and it''s a stat for us, so no Friday for me.","index":825,"end_time":2254.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2244.96,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then we''re into the following week, where our meeting would land on New Year''s Day, which is going to be a stat as well.","index":826,"end_time":2264.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2256.32,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So could we maybe move the meeting sometime other in that week?","index":827,"end_time":2271.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2264.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That would be the week of December 29th, or are you guys out that entire week as well?","index":828,"end_time":2275.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2271.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I am out that week.","index":829,"end_time":2278.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2276.22,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay.","index":830,"end_time":2279.1,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2278.46,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"No worries.","index":831,"end_time":2281.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2281.02,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Not the end of the world.","index":832,"end_time":2283.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2281.98,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I don''t think anything is going to be, like, going up in flames.","index":833,"end_time":2286.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2283.26,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So I think you can probably.","index":834,"end_time":2288.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2286.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"What do you call it, Cancel that meeting on January 1st, and then we can catch up the next week.","index":835,"end_time":2297.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2290.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And then just if there''s anything happening in the interim, just send me an email, like, hey, this is ready, or whatever.","index":836,"end_time":2303.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2297.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And I think we''ve done that in the past, and I think that works out just fine.","index":837,"end_time":2307.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2303.57,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So.","index":838,"end_time":2307.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2307.41,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":839,"end_time":2308.37,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2307.81,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":840,"end_time":2308.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2308.37,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And for.","index":841,"end_time":2309.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2308.73,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"For next week, I''ll be online as well, so I''ll just keep sending you updates as I get.","index":842,"end_time":2312.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2309.13,"speaker_name":"Nathalie Mintjens"},{"text":"Okay?","index":843,"end_time":2313.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2312.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":844,"end_time":2313.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2313.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":845,"end_time":2314.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2313.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Sure.","index":846,"end_time":2314.49,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2314.33,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And of course, if you do need to meet with me, if you''ve got questions or whatever, I''m in the 22nd, the 23rd, and the 24th.","index":847,"end_time":2320.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2314.49,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Pretty open.","index":848,"end_time":2322.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2322.07,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Like, this week is madness because everyone''s trying to get stuff done before they all run away that week, so it''s actually pretty open for me.","index":849,"end_time":2331.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2322.87,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"So if you do need me, just.","index":850,"end_time":2333.79,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2331.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just send me a little quick note and we can just pop on a call.","index":851,"end_time":2336.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2333.79,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay?","index":852,"end_time":2337.43,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2336.949,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":853,"end_time":2338.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2337.91,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":854,"end_time":2339.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2338.63,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Okay.","index":855,"end_time":2340.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2339.51,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"All right.","index":856,"end_time":2341.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2340.71,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, very good.","index":857,"end_time":2341.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2341.15,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Well, if I don''t talk to you all before a happy holiday season to.","index":858,"end_time":2346.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2341.83,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You all, I hope Santa is good to you.","index":859,"end_time":2349.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2346.39,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, yeah, we''ll pick up in a couple of weeks when.","index":860,"end_time":2353.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2349.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"When we''re into the new year.","index":861,"end_time":2355.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2353.69,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":862,"end_time":2356.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2355.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":863,"end_time":2357.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2356.97,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Just.","index":864,"end_time":2357.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2357.53,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Just remember remembering that Santa is red.","index":865,"end_time":2360.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2358.09,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"And I will think about reading it up.","index":866,"end_time":2364.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2360.09,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"I know every time you see a stop sign, Lou, I know you think of me.","index":867,"end_time":2367.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2364.89,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"I know you do.","index":868,"end_time":2368.89,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2368.01,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"But happy holidays to you on YouTube.","index":869,"end_time":2374.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2371.45,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":870,"end_time":2374.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2374.5,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":871,"end_time":2375.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2374.86,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"You guys have a good holiday.","index":872,"end_time":2377.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2375.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"And, yeah, like I said, we''ll pick up when, in January.","index":873,"end_time":2380.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2377.14,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"That sounds great.","index":874,"end_time":2380.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2380.1,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Great.","index":875,"end_time":2381.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2381.54,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"All right.","index":876,"end_time":2382.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2381.9,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Thank you, Vegas.","index":877,"end_time":2383.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2382.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Happy holidays.","index":878,"end_time":2383.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2383.14,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"},{"text":"Welcome.","index":879,"end_time":2384.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2383.94,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Take care, everyone.","index":880,"end_time":2385.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2384.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye.","index":881,"end_time":2385.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2385.38,"speaker_name":"Roz"},{"text":"Bye.","index":882,"end_time":2386.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2385.7,"speaker_name":"Lou Bogani"}],"dateString":"2025-12-18T17:30:00.000Z","host_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85828735088?pwd=b9W3cDKwBeJQyK00Qs0iP3vvCmTxIZ.1","participants":["nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,lou.bogani@marketersindemand.com,kiyan.klocker@marketersindemand.com,nina.belina@marketersindemand.com,rosalynne.regan@ricoh.ca,linnea.wolken@ricoh-usa.com","colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","lou.bogani@marketersindemand.com","kiyan.klocker@marketersindemand.com","nina.belina@marketersindemand.com","rosalynne.regan@ricoh.ca","linnea.wolken@ricoh-usa.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KC78YMG00WTGP1QT7DWACVPN","organizer_email":"nathalie.mintjens@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.91,"bullets":["Resolved display issues by standardizing design elements like gradients and gray tones.","Roz approved visual tweaks and requested lighter gray to align with brand direction.","Lou to upload revised files with updated colors and imagery for consistency across assets.","Animated video draft with alternate music versions to be delivered today for review.","RPD sales guide updates targeted for February ahead of planned April market release."],"highlights":[{"quote":"We''re getting into that now to, you know, to, like, change up some stuff.","speaker":"Roz"},{"quote":"This one is kind of wrapped up just for small details.","speaker":"Lou Bogani"},{"quote":"We''ll be delivering the first cut to you today.","speaker":"Nathalie Mintjens"}],"topics":["delivery","design","launch"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106-preview","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-19T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Sales Guide and Visual Asset Refinement**\n\nThe team is finalizing updates to the **IPM and Optimizer sales guides and related visuals** to improve clarity and brand consistency ahead of upcoming launches (04:07).\n\n- **Lou Bogani presented multiple refinements** including reducing logo size for better spacing and adjusting image placements to avoid awkward cropping (04:07).\n    - Roz emphasized the need to maintain distinct image libraries per product, preventing cross-use to strengthen product identity (10:24).\n    - Lou agreed to replace images that conflicted with these guidelines and remove certain icons for a cleaner look (11:04).\n    - Color adjustments were requested, with Roz directing a shift to lighter gray tones and gradient bubbles for a fresher look aligned with current branding preferences (06:04, 07:56).\n    - Lou committed to uploading updated files to the shared folder for testing and final review before distribution (16:15).\n\n- **The team is testing a new file export method limiting swatches** to five or six colors to solve prior color inconsistencies experienced when transferring files via Google software (02:07).\n    - Roz described persistent color distortion issues with Google Docs and suggested testing Adobe file transfer as a potential solution (02:27).\n    - Natalie Mintjens will coordinate updates and verify if Lou’s new method resolves the problem before sending files externally (16:18).\n\n- **Roz identified key image style directions for RPD marketing materials**, differentiating between RPD’s statement/bill printing focus and IPM’s distributed print use cases to maintain clear product narratives (24:00).\n    - She stressed the importance of subtle Ricoh red accents in images to strengthen brand recognition without overwhelming visuals (25:23).\n    - Roz requested imagery that suggests large print plants or shop floors without revealing competitor equipment to avoid legal issues (25:23).\n    - Lou and Roz agreed on creating horizontal and vertical versions of images to enhance flexibility in PowerPoints and sales guides (18:02).\n\n- **The RPD sales guide and PowerPoint must be ready by late February** to enable regional teams to receive materials at least 30 days before the April launch, highlighting the brochure and PowerPoint as the highest priorities (34:05).\n    - Roz plans to send the RPD battle card soon for template updates, noting it contains no new images, only hero shots and content formatting (35:37).\n    - Natalie will continue managing the rollout and updates across all assets post-finalization (35:55).\n\n## **Product Imagery Strategy and Brand Consistency**\n\nThe group focused on aligning product imagery with marketing goals and brand guidelines to enhance differentiation and customer recognition (20:24).\n\n- **Roz provided detailed guidance on image selection**, favoring subtle color use and avoiding overly bright or \"primary school\" looks for professional appeal (21:05).\n    - She recommended reducing red elements to a single highlight per image, improving visual balance and brand coherence (17:21).\n    - Roz noted some images needed texture adjustments to appear more natural, avoiding overly perfect skin tones (23:17).\n    - She requested adjustments on specific colors, such as shifting bottle colors to Ricoh red or making them clear to match brand standards (19:14).\n\n- **Product differentiation between RPD and IPM was clarified** to ensure marketing materials reflect the distinct use cases and customer needs for each product (27:30).\n    - RPD targets companies with one or two print locations focusing on bulk statement printing.\n    - IPM serves distributed print environments with multiple locations, often government or large enterprises.\n    - Roz plans to maintain clear visual and narrative separation to reduce customer confusion and support sales positioning (28:15).\n\n- **Competitive landscape considerations influenced image selection**, particularly avoiding visuals that reveal competitor equipment on print floors (25:23).\n    - Roz praised prior work on Avanti-related images but confirmed the Avanti relationship has ended from a company ownership perspective, affecting branding and integration references (29:30).\n    - Colin Costigan raised the need to review and potentially update documents mentioning Avanti to reflect current status, with Roz confirming this is a regional responsibility (30:52).\n\n## **Operational Workflow and Timeline Planning**\n\nThe team agreed on workflows and timelines critical to launching updated materials smoothly, incorporating feedback cycles and holiday scheduling (36:41).\n\n- **Roz requested final images and sales guides be ready for regional distribution by late February**, setting internal deadlines accordingly (34:05).\n    - Natalie Mintjens will coordinate updates and deliverables, ensuring Lou uploads revisions promptly for review (16:15).\n    - The team will test file transfers using Adobe methods to avoid color distortion and improve efficiency (02:07).\n\n- **Holiday scheduling conflicts were addressed**, with the team deciding to cancel the meeting landing on Christmas and New Year’s Day due to holidays in Canada and overlapping absences (36:41).\n    - Roz proposed no meetings during the week of December 29th since Natalie and others are out, recommending email updates instead (37:56).\n    - Natalie confirmed availability for quick calls during December 22-24 if needed to resolve last-minute issues (38:32).\n\n- **Continuous communication through email will cover interim updates**, minimizing disruption during the holiday season while maintaining project momentum (38:28).\n    - Roz emphasized availability for quick calls if questions arise despite the holiday period (38:32).\n\n## **Video Production and Multi-format Content Delivery**\n\nThe team is delivering an animated video with alternate music versions to provide choice and better align with refreshed brand energy (16:26).\n\n- **Natalie reported the first cut of the animated video will be delivered the same day**, with two music variants—one more upbeat—to match the updated animation style (16:26).\n    - Roz confirmed readiness to review and provide feedback promptly (16:44).\n    - This aligns with broader efforts to refresh content and keep marketing materials engaging and current.\n\n- **Multiple formats and orientations for images are planned** to increase flexibility across sales guides and PowerPoints (18:02).\n    - Roz suggested creating both vertical and horizontal versions of key images to enhance usability.\n    - This supports varied presentation needs and improves visual appeal across platforms.\n\n## **Stakeholder Collaboration and Responsibility Alignment**\n\nClear ownership and collaboration processes were established to ensure smooth execution and accountability (16:15).\n\n- **Lou Bogani is responsible for updating and uploading revised files** including sales guides, charts, and images to the shared folder for testing and review (16:15).\n    - Natalie Mintjens will manage coordination, task tracking, and final delivery to external recipients (16:18).\n    - Roz will provide detailed feedback on imagery and content to ensure alignment with branding and marketing goals (15:49).\n\n- **Roz will send product shots and image libraries to Natalie and Nina** to support ongoing creative work and maintain consistency across materials (18:41).\n    - This enables the team to work from a shared asset pool, reducing duplication and speeding revisions.\n    - Roz’s deep domain knowledge of commercial print and marketing nuances guides asset selection and messaging (29:04).\n\n- **The team agreed on iterative feedback cycles, emphasizing testing and refinement**, especially regarding color accuracy and image placement, to avoid delays and rework (02:07, 14:08).\n    - This process includes testing swatch-limited files and Adobe transfer methods to resolve technical issues impacting quality.\n    - Clear communication channels and prompt feedback loops are prioritized to meet tight deadlines.\n\n## **Brand and Product Positioning Philosophy**\n\nDiscussions revealed a deliberate approach to maintaining product clarity and competitive advantage through visual and messaging discipline (27:30).\n\n- **Roz highlighted the importance of distinct visual narratives for RPD versus IPM** to reduce customer confusion and reinforce product strengths (27:30).\n    - She emphasized the strategic use of imagery that reflects real-world use cases and customer environments.\n    - This visual clarity supports the sales process by helping prospects self-identify with the right solution.\n\n- **The team consciously avoids overusing red and dark grays**, opting instead for lighter grays and subtle red accents to modernize the brand while respecting legacy identity (06:04, 07:56).\n    - This shift responds to internal feedback and market trends favoring cleaner, lighter aesthetics.\n    - Roz explained this is part of a broader brand refresh philosophy to stay relevant without losing brand equity.\n\n- **Competitive integrations like Avanti remain possible but are de-emphasized** in marketing as company relationships have evolved, reflecting a shift in strategic partnerships (29:42).\n    - The team plans to phase out residual references and focus on Ricoh’s own product strengths and ecosystem.\n    - This approach clarifies market positioning and avoids confusion around partnerships.","outline":null,"keywords":["sales guide","color calibration","Ricoh Predictive Dynamics","image assets","branding guidelines","marketing collateral"],"overview":"- **Sales Guides & Visuals:** Finalizing updates for IPM and Optimizer sales guides to enhance clarity and brand consistency before launches.\n\n- **Image Adjustments:** Image libraries will be distinct per product, with reduced logos, lighter colors, and horizontal/vertical formats for flexibility.\n\n- **Color Consistency Issues:** Testing new file export methods to limit color swatches and resolve issues with Google Docs color distortions.\n\n- **RPD Launch Timeline:** RPD sales guide and PowerPoint must be ready by late February for regional teams before April launches.\n\n- **Holiday Meeting Changes:** Meetings on December 25 and January 1 are canceled; updates will be shared via email during the holiday.\n\n- **Differentiated Messaging:** Clear visual narratives for RPD and IPM to reduce customer confusion and support distinct marketing strategies.","action_items":"\n**Lou Bogani**\nShare updated sales guide files with reduced swatches for color testing (02:07)\nAdjust images to avoid cropping issues and replace conflicting images with product-specific imagery (08:39)\nChange gray boxes to lighter gradient per current branding refresh and finalize icon updates (06:10)\nRemove product overview text from current page, rearrange content to reduce whitespace, and add personas under target markets to save space (12:29)\nUpload amended files to shared drive folder to verify color export consistency (13:38)\nSwitch outline colors to charcoal on Optimizer materials for cleaner visuals (15:00)\nUpdate product shots and sales guide images following Roz’s feedback to reflect brand colors and styling (14:31)\nDeliver final sales guide package to Nathalie Mintjens after requested updates are completed (15:59)\n\n**Roz (Rosalynne Regan)**\nProvide product shots and GUI images for marketing materials to Nathalie and Lou (18:41)\nReview and confirm updated files for color accuracy and overall design after receiving from Lou (15:50)\nSend RPD Battle Card for template updating once RPD images are finalized (34:05)\nCoordinate timeline to finalize RPD sales guides and PowerPoint by end of February for April launch (32:23)\nAdvise on regional messaging surrounding Avanti references and integrations (29:42)\nNotify team regarding scheduling around holiday periods and handle any urgent needs via email or calls (36:51)\n\n**Nathalie Mintjens**\nConsolidate Lou’s completed tasks and upload new files for review (16:04)\nSend the first cut of animated video along with two music version options to Roz for approval (16:26)\nPrepare Process Director brochure for delivery by Monday (16:44)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nConfirm if any content needs updates regarding Avanti mentions and inform relevant parties (29:31)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"aad0b58d-94db-46f0-82ea-b81abc8b7f6c","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
