oz for approval (16:26)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare Process Director brochure for delivery by Monday (16:44)","completed":false},{"text":"Confirm if any content needs updates regarding Avanti mentions and inform relevant parties (29:31)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
