    '01KC9RJFZ6MJZMS39SZPGHMDKD',
    'AQI // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting',
    '{"Colin Costigan","bwillans","Guille Santana"}'::text[],
    2191,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/89786281993?pwd=li2lwrSFpmITXPKEdOBBgaXPwh8ONO.1',
    '{"id":"01KC9RJFZ6MJZMS39SZPGHMDKD","title":"AQI // MiD: Weekly Marketing Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Integration and Event Management**\n\nThe team finalized the setup of the **Eventbrite-HubSpot integration** to track customer attendance at regional user group meetings, aiming to streamline event registration and communication (04:04).\n\n- The integration now connects Eventbrite events with HubSpot, allowing toggling of event sync, though only one event, the **Manatee County, Florida**, currently exists.\n- **Barbara Willans** explained the goal is to track customers and prospects attending these events to tailor upgrades and campaigns for the upcoming year.\n- Communication will shift from **Marketo and Reg Fox** to HubSpot for invites, improving consistency and reducing complexity.\n- The integration will track both registrations and attendees through custom fields to enable targeted follow-up communications.\n\n## **Forms Consolidation and Optimization**\n\nThe team identified significant opportunities to consolidate and standardize marketing forms on the website, particularly moving away from complicated Marketo forms to HubSpot’s more flexible platform (06:04).\n\n- The **HAWK form**, a critical sales lead capture form, was unintentionally destroyed on **December 5th** and requires Adobe support to reset due to Marketo limitations.\n- **Barbara** emphasized the need to rebuild essential forms in HubSpot and retire outdated forms, some as old as **13 years**.\n- Phone number fields will be added as **optional** for consistency, as required fields have been shown to reduce registration rates.\n- The sales coordinator starting soon will manage lead form data entries, especially for dropdown selections linked to sales commissions, which will be rebuilt without reliance on Marketo’s complex dropdowns.\n\n## **Contact Data and Salesforce Integration**\n\nThe current contact and opportunity data totals **29,102** accounts under broad criteria but will narrow significantly when filtered by recent fiscal years, pending sales team input (14:43).\n\n- **Barbara** plans to gather feedback from sales leads on refining contact lists and parameters in a meeting on **December 29th**.\n- Salesforce integration setup will begin with syncing turned off to prepare the system until filtering rules are finalized.\n- Data sources for mailing lists currently span **Marketo, Salesforce, Upgrades Desk Pro, and Constant Contact**, causing reconciliation challenges.\n- HubSpot will become the central source of truth moving forward to consolidate fragmented data streams.\n\n## **Content and Campaign Planning**\n\nThree key content initiatives are scheduled for **January**, focusing on productivity, content refresh, and new product promotion (27:26).\n\n- The **pillars of productivity** campaign will launch with a simulive event and corresponding landing page, designed as a nurture program.\n- **Riverside** will be used for refreshed content creation, targeting field hydrologists, especially at **Aquarius** and **Whims** OPCOs.\n- A **digital twin** simulive event planned at January''s end will serve as a net-new lead generation effort.\n- **Barbara** will prepare campaign briefs next week to enable landing page and nurture workflow builds.\n\n## **Dashboard and Reporting Enhancements**\n\nA new **Databox dashboard** has been introduced and is under review by **Vivian, Jess, and Blake** with initial feedback expected by the end of the week to prepare for a presentation in mid-January (29:26).\n\n- The dashboard currently shows inflated lead numbers due to inclusion of the Christmas card campaign but will refine as filters are adjusted.\n- The goal is to socialize this dashboard as the **AQI Data Box** during the **Vivian Aqi socialization** with sales teams in mid-January.\n- Branding updates and customizations will follow feedback, including color scheme alignment and logo improvements.\n- Colin offered additional training and customization support to help Vivian confidently present the data to stakeholders.\n\n## **Technology and Operational Support**\n\nOperational readiness includes ongoing support for **Riverside** usage and form embedding, with cost and user access considerations addressed (22:58).\n\n- Riverside’s current setup allows desktop usage under the parent account email to avoid individual costs, but mobile app licensing and user experience require clarification.\n- Vivian aims to train the sales team on Riverside in mid-January, so resolving app access and cost issues is a priority.\n- The team will deliver the **newsletter subscribe form** embed code by next week for a planned mid-January launch aligned with nurture efforts.\n- Colin emphasized readiness to assist with ongoing form updates, code additions, and campaign support to keep projects on track through Q1 and beyond.","outline":null,"keywords":["Eventbrite Integration","HubSpot Forms","Salesforce Sync","Riverside Podcast","Databox Analytics","Marketing Campaign Planning"],"overview":"- **Eventbrite Integration Complete:** HubSpot now tracks attendance for events like the upcoming Manatee County meeting, streamlining communication.  \n- **Forms Optimization Needed:** Consolidate marketing forms, move to HubSpot; rebuild critical HAWK form after accidental deletion.  \n- **Contact Data Review Planned:** 29,102 accounts will be refined with sales input to improve data quality and filtering methods.  \n- **January Campaign Initiatives:** Key content campaigns will focus on productivity, content refresh, and new product promotion, starting mid-January.  \n- **New Databox Dashboard:** Under review for lead metrics; adjustments needed for Christmas campaign data before mid-January presentation.  \n- **Riverside Support Ongoing:** Training for sales team in January; resolving app access and cost issues is a priority.","action_items":"\n**Barb Willans**\nProvide the talk track for Vivian Aqi’s OPCO socialization presentation mid-January (02:20)\nRetrieve or recreate dropdown options for the HAWK form salespeople assignment to populate HubSpot (13:00)\nCoordinate with sales leads on refining contact data parameters for clean lists ahead of Jan 29 meeting (14:40)\nRemove Christmas card recipients from HubSpot due to DNS issues and monitor list data cleanup (15:40)\nPrepare campaign briefs for three January initiatives (Pillars of Productivity dashboards, Riverside content use, Digital Twin event) and share with marketing team (27:00)\nConsult Vivian on Databox branding preferences and compile feedback for dashboard adjustments (32:50)\nFollow up on Riverside app usage for field salespeople and relay any issues for technical resolution (24:35)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nBuild and consolidate forms in HubSpot from provided audit list; add phone number field as optional on all forms (09:10)\nSet up Salesforce integration ''ready but not syncing'' to allow configuration and future enablement (18:20)\nProvide embed code for newsletter subscription form for deployment by client or contractor (20:45)\nConfirm Riverside account setup under parent account and investigate app usage licenses for sales in the field (23:45)\nCustomize Databox dashboards with improved logo and potentially AQI branding once feedback received (33:10)\nCoordinate support for socialization materials and forms update for January OPCO presentation (36:15)\n\n**Guille Santana**\nClarify and assist with underlying form structure improvements and dropdown alternatives for sales lead allocation (10:00)\n"},"duration":36.52000045776367,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":1,"name":"bwillans"},{"id":2,"name":"Guille Santana"}],"sentences":[{"text":"I feel like everyone''s trying to cram everything in before the holiday.","index":0,"end_time":4.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The way that it goes, through partnerships and everything, everything lands at you.","index":1,"end_time":10.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":6.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yes.","index":2,"end_time":11.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":10.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know.","index":3,"end_time":14.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":13.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I did that to Gaye yesterday.","index":4,"end_time":15.959,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":14.16,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m like, oh, by the way, here''s what I''m thinking.","index":5,"end_time":18.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":15.959,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s like 10 miles long.","index":6,"end_time":21.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":19.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It was great, though.","index":7,"end_time":23.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":22.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was really good to go through all of that.","index":8,"end_time":26.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":25.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I know we have a packed agenda today.","index":9,"end_time":29.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":27.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Barb, I don''t know your availability, but if we do need to extend this meeting for any conversation, I''m available for an additional 30 minutes if needed.","index":10,"end_time":37.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":30.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Me too.","index":11,"end_time":37.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":37.42,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":12,"end_time":38.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":37.94,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":13,"end_time":38.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":38.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":14,"end_time":39.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":38.58,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":15,"end_time":40.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":39.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":16,"end_time":40.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then next week is definitely a little quieter.","index":17,"end_time":43.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":40.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s when I can actually.","index":18,"end_time":44.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":43.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can like, do so much development and catch up on, like, all the things that have been talked about, so no problem.","index":19,"end_time":50.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":44.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, I''ll pull up my screen.","index":20,"end_time":55.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":52.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Back over here.","index":21,"end_time":58.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":57.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"All right, so as you can see.","index":22,"end_time":62.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":60.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So definitely a packed agenda.","index":23,"end_time":64.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":62.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I wanted to start with the timeline slide that you sent over.","index":24,"end_time":67.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":64.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''ll get into a few of the integrations and forms, Zoom, webinar, the newsletter update, and Salesforce.","index":25,"end_time":75.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":68.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then making sure that you''re able to access Pulse.","index":26,"end_time":77.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":75.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sure.","index":27,"end_time":78.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":78.32,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"All right, we''ve got it.","index":28,"end_time":81.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":79.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We''re done.","index":29,"end_time":82.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":82.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Oh, you got pulse.","index":30,"end_time":83.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":82.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":31,"end_time":84.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":83.77,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":32,"end_time":84.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":84.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, quick.","index":33,"end_time":85.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":84.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"All right.","index":34,"end_time":87.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":86.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I was taking a look at this.","index":35,"end_time":88.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, I think this is pretty accurate.","index":36,"end_time":90.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":88.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t think it''s missing anything.","index":37,"end_time":91.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":90.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s really always a question of does the team any need any more detail or are they looking for more of just this high level overview?","index":38,"end_time":98.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":92.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s high level.","index":39,"end_time":99.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":99.21,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I''ll be quick because it''s.","index":40,"end_time":100.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":99.85,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"This is packed.","index":41,"end_time":101.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":100.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Basically what.","index":42,"end_time":103.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":102.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"What we care about is that green dot below that says Vivian Aqi socialization.","index":43,"end_time":109.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":103.37,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She mid January is.","index":44,"end_time":111.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":109.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Will be in front of all the sales teams and all the OPCOs and just has to give an update.","index":45,"end_time":115.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":111.53,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We had a.","index":46,"end_time":117.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":116.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"An OPCO meeting two weeks ago and not that people are getting nervous, but we have an umbrella company and so I think this is fine.","index":47,"end_time":124.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":117.41,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She will come back and give you the whole spiel or give me the spiel.","index":48,"end_time":129.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":125.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Not you guys, but I have a whole talk track for her.","index":49,"end_time":131.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":129.01,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"There are four OPCOs I think moving right now and one OPCO.","index":50,"end_time":136.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":131.57,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It just got raised.","index":51,"end_time":137.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":136.3,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And Vivian, she''s not a nervous person at all.","index":52,"end_time":139.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":137.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, not.","index":53,"end_time":140.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":139.66,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But she said I need this because the one OPCO is struggling because they didn''t.","index":54,"end_time":145.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":140.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t know why they didn''t hire an integration partner.","index":55,"end_time":149.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":146.18,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"How could you do this by yourself?","index":56,"end_time":150.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":149.22,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":57,"end_time":152.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":152.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s A lot of figuring out.","index":58,"end_time":155.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":154.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":59,"end_time":156.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":156.42,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So that''s.","index":60,"end_time":157.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":156.98,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s why.","index":61,"end_time":158.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":157.58,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I think this is enough.","index":62,"end_time":159.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.1,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"All I have to give her is a talk track to stand in front of them.","index":63,"end_time":162.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":159.78,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I think this is okay.","index":64,"end_time":164.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":163.07,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, perfect.","index":65,"end_time":165.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":164.11,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":66,"end_time":165.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":67,"end_time":165.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":165.67,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"If you need anything else here, let me know.","index":68,"end_time":167.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":165.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But yeah, this covered everything that was in our plan documents and everything like that.","index":69,"end_time":171.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":167.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":70,"end_time":173.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":172.11,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":71,"end_time":174.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":173.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right then with Eventbrite, I can even open up HubSpot.","index":72,"end_time":180.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":175.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we got the invite and connected to the account and I set up the integration.","index":73,"end_time":185.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":180.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I haven''t synced any of the data though.","index":74,"end_time":187.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":185.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But this is live and we can just toggle these.","index":75,"end_time":190.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":188.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":76,"end_time":192.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":191.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We can toggle any event that we want to sync over.","index":77,"end_time":196.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":194.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":78,"end_time":197.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":197.19,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t know that there''s any events there yet.","index":79,"end_time":201.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":197.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, there was like one.","index":80,"end_time":203.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":202.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it was just this.","index":81,"end_time":204.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":203.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Manatee County, Florida.","index":82,"end_time":205.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":204.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That was the only one that I saw.","index":83,"end_time":206.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":205.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":84,"end_time":209.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":208.47,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s new.","index":85,"end_time":209.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":209.15,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Cool.","index":86,"end_time":210.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":209.83,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Let me just pull that up, make sure I''m looking at the right thing.","index":87,"end_time":213.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":211.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":88,"end_time":227.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":226.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So this is what we''re seeing in Eventbrite.","index":89,"end_time":230.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":227.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s why that''s synced over.","index":90,"end_time":232.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":230.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":91,"end_time":233.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":232.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I could just let them know that it''s connected, but there''s, I mean, nothing to see yet.","index":92,"end_time":238.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":233.71,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":93,"end_time":239.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":238.87,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":94,"end_time":239.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":239.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what is next steps here for this integration?","index":95,"end_time":244.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, so what''s going to happen is we''re going to get a list of what''s called rugs, the regional user group meetings.","index":96,"end_time":251.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":244.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And we just wanted to track like the registration.","index":97,"end_time":256.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.07,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Everything will be an event in Eventbrite.","index":98,"end_time":259.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":256.79,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But what we wanted to do is track customers attending so that you know the strategy for next year.","index":99,"end_time":264.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":259.19,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We have a lot of upgrades and campaigns that we want to do.","index":100,"end_time":268.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":264.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So largely there are some prospects that, that go to these, but they''re largely customers.","index":101,"end_time":273.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":268.87,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So we just want to sync with Salesforce to make sure that, okay, we know who they are, where they came from, send them communications, make sure that anybody who attends is opted in so that we can just track.","index":102,"end_time":285.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":273.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And also they paid it.","index":103,"end_time":287.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":285.88,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Well, some pay, some don''t.","index":104,"end_time":289.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":287.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Depends on where you are in the world.","index":105,"end_time":290.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":289.28,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I don''t think we have to worry about that.","index":106,"end_time":292.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":290.76,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But we do want to see.","index":107,"end_time":294.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":292.96,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We are.","index":108,"end_time":295.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":109,"end_time":296.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":110,"end_time":296.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":296.48,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I need some more coffee.","index":111,"end_time":297.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":296.81,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Reset.","index":112,"end_time":298.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay, so we are going to send communications out of HubSpot like invites, because we used to send them out of Marketo and it was a bit of a pain in the butt.","index":113,"end_time":307.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":298.73,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So we used Reg Fox, Marketo and something else that I can''t remember, depending on where you are in the world.","index":114,"end_time":315.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":307.77,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And we just want to put it all In HubSpot.","index":115,"end_time":317.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":315.21,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":116,"end_time":317.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It sounds like a pain.","index":117,"end_time":319.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":317.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":118,"end_time":320.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":319.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So with this integration, you can even see like they have it all up top.","index":119,"end_time":323.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So HubSpot events has come a long way in the last year or so.","index":120,"end_time":327.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":323.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we''ll sync it in as an event and then do you want us to track registers or registrations and then attendees as well, like via custom field so we can send them different communications?","index":121,"end_time":337.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":327.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":122,"end_time":338.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":337.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":123,"end_time":338.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":338.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":124,"end_time":340.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":339.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s simple enough.","index":125,"end_time":341.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":340.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":126,"end_time":345.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t think we had anything else there.","index":127,"end_time":347.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":345.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then on the forms I know Guille sent over, like the audit that we ran of all of the forms, we do see a lot of opportunity for consolidation.","index":128,"end_time":356.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":349.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I know with Marketo you kind of just create a new form for every new need, which is not necessary in HubSpot.","index":129,"end_time":363.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":356.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":130,"end_time":364.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":364.08,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So what''s my action here?","index":131,"end_time":366.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":365.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"When I went through it, I saw like there''s forms on the website that some of them, like, they weren''t standardized.","index":132,"end_time":375.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":367.04,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":133,"end_time":375.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":375.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, they were pretty close, but not everybody had the same feel.","index":134,"end_time":377.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":375.32,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So we added the phone number and the opt in verbiage.","index":135,"end_time":381.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":377.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But then, you know, it''s.","index":136,"end_time":383.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":381.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Some of the assets are gated, all the on demand webinars are gated.","index":137,"end_time":387.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":384.33,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Contact us.","index":138,"end_time":388.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":387.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then there''s some OPCO forms.","index":139,"end_time":391.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":388.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like there''s the.","index":140,"end_time":392.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":391.81,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The HAWK form is the most important form probably out of all of this.","index":141,"end_time":396.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":392.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And December 5th, I destroyed the form that I don''t know what happened, but it''s.","index":142,"end_time":401.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":397.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It was so complicated in Marketo to get anybody added.","index":143,"end_time":405.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":401.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It was really hard.","index":144,"end_time":407.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":406.41,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, Marketo is frustrating.","index":145,"end_time":409.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":408.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It was really frustrating.","index":146,"end_time":410.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":409.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I finally just saved everything and it got rid of the dropdown.","index":147,"end_time":413.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":410.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So now I have to call Adobe to get it reset to December 5th.","index":148,"end_time":417.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":414.28,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So gay.","index":149,"end_time":418.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":417.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s.","index":150,"end_time":418.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":418.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s what I was talking about.","index":151,"end_time":420.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":418.88,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, I still.","index":152,"end_time":420.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.08,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ve been so busy, I couldn''t call them yet.","index":153,"end_time":422.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":420.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I just have to get it reinstated.","index":154,"end_time":425.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":423.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But we have to manually add and get rid of people as they come and go.","index":155,"end_time":431.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":425.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s.","index":156,"end_time":433,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":432.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s insane.","index":157,"end_time":434.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":434.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":158,"end_time":436.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":436.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I guess next steps out of these, we just.","index":159,"end_time":438.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":436.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we have the list of all of them.","index":160,"end_time":439.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":438.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":161,"end_time":440.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":440.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the HAWK form and everything.","index":162,"end_time":442.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":440.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Obviously resource forms similar to Avanti will have that dedicated to the specific resource so that it leads to a different external page and things like that.","index":163,"end_time":450.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":442.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But basically in the documents we sent over, we just saw a lot of opportunity for consolidation or even just old, really old forms, like 13 years old that may not need migration.","index":164,"end_time":461.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":450.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So what we''ll do.","index":165,"end_time":462.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And correct me if I''m wrong on the stage that we''re at but I think that we can go ahead and build the forms that we know need to be carried over and then we just have, if there''s anything else out of that massive list that we sent that we need to build, just let us know.","index":166,"end_time":477.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sorry, go ahead.","index":167,"end_time":482.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":482.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nope, I just am agreeing with you.","index":168,"end_time":485.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":483.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":169,"end_time":485.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":485.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I think I sent over the embed code for this and this would change to match colors on the website and things like that.","index":170,"end_time":491.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":485.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And did you need phone number added to this one.","index":171,"end_time":495.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":494.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As a non optional.","index":172,"end_time":504.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":502.83,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s up to you.","index":173,"end_time":506.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can make it.","index":174,"end_time":506.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I tend to make them not required.","index":175,"end_time":510.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":506.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I, this is where I look to your, your guidance.","index":176,"end_time":516.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":510.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"All the salespeople, if you remember at Ricoh, I mean they wanted a kidney.","index":177,"end_time":522.299,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":518.139,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I mean they didn''t want to do any work and sorry, but that''s true.","index":178,"end_time":526.339,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":522.379,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And Avanti is different.","index":179,"end_time":527.659,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":526.339,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"They were hunters, but these guys are kind of in the middle.","index":180,"end_time":531.139,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":527.659,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"They''re like, hey, can you add this and this and this?","index":181,"end_time":533.059,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":531.139,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I remember you telling me pretty sure it was you.","index":182,"end_time":535.739,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":533.059,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Every time you add a required field, your registration is going to drop by a certain percentage.","index":183,"end_time":541.339,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":535.979,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean I don''t know the exact math on that, but it''s, you''re basically raising the barrier of entry and phone number has become, I mean people just hate random phone calls.","index":184,"end_time":553.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.579,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That has become a large barrier of a required field.","index":185,"end_time":558.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":555.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I, I always recommend making that optional.","index":186,"end_time":560.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":558.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s make it optional, but add it for consistency.","index":187,"end_time":563.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":561.28,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":188,"end_time":564.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And you can always, I mean you guys have zoom info as well.","index":189,"end_time":566.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":564.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You could always enrich them.","index":190,"end_time":568.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":566.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or we can enrich them for you.","index":191,"end_time":570.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":568.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean we really just need their email address and their opt in.","index":192,"end_time":572.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":570.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Absolutely.","index":193,"end_time":574.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":573.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":194,"end_time":574.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":574.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And that''s, yeah, it became so long at Recode nobody used it anyway.","index":195,"end_time":579.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":574.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So.","index":196,"end_time":579.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":579.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":197,"end_time":580.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":580.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll add the phone to form as optional and then we have the list of the ones that we, the forms that we just need to create based on your analysis.","index":198,"end_time":592.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":581.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I think that we''re good to go there.","index":199,"end_time":594.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":592.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":200,"end_time":595,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":594.52,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":201,"end_time":596.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":595.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I just have a question on the dropdown, Barb that was inside the form but like invisible or did you have it somewhere else?","index":202,"end_time":607.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":597.24,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"It was inside the form and right at the top and visible.","index":203,"end_time":612,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":608.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So what happens is that Hawk is a sister.","index":204,"end_time":615.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":612.16,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like it''s another OpCo, but it''s a close cousin.","index":205,"end_time":618.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":615.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So these salespeople get a spiff of X amount of dollars every time they provide a lead.","index":206,"end_time":625.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":618.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So they go in, select their name and then put in the lead.","index":207,"end_time":628.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":625.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It says right at the top of the form, if you don''t see your name, just put name in the comments but nobody.","index":208,"end_time":635.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":629.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So that''s not it.","index":209,"end_time":639.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s.","index":210,"end_time":639.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.1,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s the.","index":211,"end_time":640.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":639.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s Aquatic Informatics, slash lead hyphen, something.","index":212,"end_time":647.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":640.94,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And where did you use that for events or.","index":213,"end_time":652.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":649.5,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"No, it was, it was for salespeople and it''s in Marketo.","index":214,"end_time":656.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":653.18,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I can put it in the chat so you can see it.","index":215,"end_time":659.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":657.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":216,"end_time":660.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":659.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know, I know.","index":217,"end_time":661.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":660.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, you had it in your document as well.","index":218,"end_time":662.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":661.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it was somewhere, somewhere in there.","index":219,"end_time":665.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":663.67,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"I always think it''s so funny also just having a URL that says like lead or landing page or.","index":220,"end_time":675.909,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":670.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, like what is happening here?","index":221,"end_time":681.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":677.75,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But it''s good, you know, like they try to.","index":222,"end_time":684.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":682.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"For such a tiny little team which is getting bigger by the day.","index":223,"end_time":687.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":684.15,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, here it is.","index":224,"end_time":690.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":689.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Aquaticinformatics.com lead input.","index":225,"end_time":694.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":690.27,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I love it.","index":226,"end_time":698.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":697.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"There it is.","index":227,"end_time":699.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":699.03,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So in number three it says if you don''t see her name in the drop down, which was right under lead information there was a drop down.","index":228,"end_time":708.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":699.75,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Now there''s two companies, right?","index":229,"end_time":710.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":708.47,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Hawk.","index":230,"end_time":711.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":710.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like it was like dozens and dozens of people and I could not figure out how to get them into Marketo and Salesforce at the same time.","index":231,"end_time":719.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":711.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And it just, it became a hassle.","index":232,"end_time":722.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":719.5,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We have a coordinator starting in a couple of weeks and this will be her responsibility because I, I don''t know what happened, but when I saved it got rid of everybody.","index":233,"end_time":731.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":722.86,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s the, the beauty of Marketo.","index":234,"end_time":736.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can''t go back.","index":235,"end_time":738.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":737.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You can''t, you can''t just go in and say, hey, I want to revert to this.","index":236,"end_time":742.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":738.78,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I have to call Adobe to revert it.","index":237,"end_time":744.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":742.38,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yep, insane.","index":238,"end_time":746.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":744.67,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But what were we about to say?","index":239,"end_time":748.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":747.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, we can totally do this in HubSpot and maybe later when we''re maybe in January or something, we can just assign them with workflows without the need of a drop down.","index":240,"end_time":762.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":750.19,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we''ll see how we can optimize the journey.","index":241,"end_time":768.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":765.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I also don''t want to, like, I don''t want to change too much too quick for the team.","index":242,"end_time":773.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":768.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If this is something that they''re used to and like the flow of.","index":243,"end_time":775.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":773.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We would just need the, the list of options that go into that drop down and then we can build that out.","index":244,"end_time":780.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":776,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I can.","index":245,"end_time":782.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":781.84,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"As soon as I find the list that I deleted, I can like, you know, even if it''s there, I know how to go into HubSpot and add people.","index":246,"end_time":789.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":783.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s fine.","index":247,"end_time":791.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":790.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I can do that.","index":248,"end_time":792.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":791.84,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The hassle is I don''t know these people.","index":249,"end_time":795.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":792.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":250,"end_time":797.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":796.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Know who they are, where they live, how to get that information that who I. I don''t know.","index":251,"end_time":802.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":797.49,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So we''re going to have to.","index":252,"end_time":803.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":802.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m going to have to figure that out.","index":253,"end_time":805.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":803.81,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"This lead is not widely populated, but it''s enough that we rely on it.","index":254,"end_time":811.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":805.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yep.","index":255,"end_time":811.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":811.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":256,"end_time":811.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":811.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, well, we''ll build it for everything that we have so far and then we can just update it when we have more information on the drop down.","index":257,"end_time":817.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":811.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sounds good.","index":258,"end_time":818.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.81,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":259,"end_time":819.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":818.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":260,"end_time":821.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":821.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then, yep, we got the forms also listed in that document that are needed for the direct flip.","index":261,"end_time":827.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":822.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I feel like we''re pretty good there.","index":262,"end_time":829.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":827.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, there''s.","index":263,"end_time":833.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":832.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s the link lead input, so we already had that in there.","index":264,"end_time":835.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":833.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":265,"end_time":836.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":835.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we already talked through this.","index":266,"end_time":839.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":837.729,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"One thing that I wanted to check also was we''re going through the contacts and opportunities and I know we wanted to dedicate some time to just chatting through this.","index":267,"end_time":847.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":839.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So the number that we had given you was 29,102.","index":268,"end_time":851.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":848.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And the parameters that were used to build that was just all accounts with create date of any and greater than zero opportunities.","index":269,"end_time":860.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":851.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we, you had mentioned doing the previous two fiscal years.","index":270,"end_time":865.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":860.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if we have this end in 2025 and start in January 2023, this number changes.","index":271,"end_time":874.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":865.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if I run this report that drops drastically.","index":272,"end_time":882.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":877.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I''ll go in and I just was so busy this week.","index":273,"end_time":886.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":883.71,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ll go and thank you guy for the Excel spreadsheets as well.","index":274,"end_time":889.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":886.55,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So yeah, I''ve got some questions on how we do this, but I can play with this.","index":275,"end_time":895.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":889.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We have a meeting on the 29th with, with the sales leads for Whims and Aquarius and they''re going to have some input on this.","index":276,"end_time":905.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":896.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We want them to.","index":277,"end_time":906.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":905.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But when you look at the Google sheet and you look at keep noise, et cetera, like that''s just way too much for sale like that.","index":278,"end_time":918.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":907.83,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m never going to do that.","index":279,"end_time":919.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":918.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But I want to be able to show them what the options are.","index":280,"end_time":922.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":919.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then in, for example, do you want me to just.","index":281,"end_time":926.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":922.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Are we diving into contacts right now or do you want to go back to the other stuff?","index":282,"end_time":929.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":926.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay, so then my other question is once I get their feedback.","index":283,"end_time":933.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":929.63,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Feedback.","index":284,"end_time":933.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":933.17,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You know, I didn''t use HubSpot for the Christmas card because the DNS issue.","index":285,"end_time":937.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":934.53,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Totally fine, it''s a one off.","index":286,"end_time":939.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":937.89,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I have to go into HubSpot, just remove them all.","index":287,"end_time":941.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":939.33,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But I did put it into constant contact because whatever, it''s a one off and it''s skewing our data box right now because it looks like I have 11,000 leads, which is not true.","index":288,"end_time":953.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":942.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But when I look into constant contact, which is drop dead simple.","index":289,"end_time":957.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":954.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"There''s 11,000 whims, recipients of the.","index":290,"end_time":961.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":958.61,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The card based on everybody''s input, including Kyle out of Salesforce.","index":291,"end_time":965.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":961.69,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"3,000 of them bounced and so now we have a list of 8,000.","index":292,"end_time":972.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":966.25,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Well, where did that list come from?","index":293,"end_time":973.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":972.17,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You know.","index":294,"end_time":974.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":973.69,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Well, it came from Marketo Sales, Salesforce Upgrades Desk Pro.","index":295,"end_time":979.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":974.17,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So when I look at all of that, I don''t know how to reconcile it with giving you that information.","index":296,"end_time":986.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":979.53,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":297,"end_time":987.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":987.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":298,"end_time":988.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we were basing things also off this type field to tell us which customers were active or expired customers as well.","index":299,"end_time":996.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":988.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if we filter out active, then we see this number drop even further.","index":300,"end_time":1000.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":996.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":301,"end_time":1002.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1001.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we just need whatever that source of truth is that they were using to build that list.","index":302,"end_time":1005.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1002.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":303,"end_time":1007.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1006.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It came from different places, but at least I sent it out of constant contact.","index":304,"end_time":1010.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1007.3,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s pretty good little program.","index":305,"end_time":1012.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1011.14,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t know.","index":306,"end_time":1014.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1013.78,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s decent.","index":307,"end_time":1014.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1014.22,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s nice and simple.","index":308,"end_time":1016.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1014.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s like.","index":309,"end_time":1016.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1016.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It is what it is, right?","index":310,"end_time":1017.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1016.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s.","index":311,"end_time":1017.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1017.66,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"They''re like.","index":312,"end_time":1018.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1017.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We do email and SMS.","index":313,"end_time":1020.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1018.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":314,"end_time":1021.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1020.98,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"For 200 Canadian a month.","index":315,"end_time":1023.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1021.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":316,"end_time":1024.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1023.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not too bad.","index":317,"end_time":1025.14,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1024.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, leave that with me and I''ll.","index":318,"end_time":1028.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1026.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ll figure something out this weekend.","index":319,"end_time":1030.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1028.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I just.","index":320,"end_time":1030.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.14,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Again, I just.","index":321,"end_time":1031.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1030.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Too busy this week, but I''ll.","index":322,"end_time":1032.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1031.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":323,"end_time":1032.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And as you know, I''m happy.","index":324,"end_time":1034.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1032.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Happy to hop on a call and go through anything with you.","index":325,"end_time":1036.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1034.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you remember our.","index":326,"end_time":1038.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1037.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What was that?","index":327,"end_time":1039.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1038.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"March and April.","index":328,"end_time":1039.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1039.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You and I spent just hours and hours in HubSpot cleaning up Rico and Avanti.","index":329,"end_time":1044,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1039.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we still got in trouble.","index":330,"end_time":1047.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1046.08,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You know, I never know what Rico brains are thinking.","index":331,"end_time":1054.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1049.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I''m sure you know all the.","index":332,"end_time":1056.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1054.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know if you followed all the eps stuff as well, but.","index":333,"end_time":1059.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1056.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Not really.","index":334,"end_time":1061.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1060.4,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I. Enrico, Roz and I, we don''t even talk about it.","index":335,"end_time":1064.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1061.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t even know if you''re still working with them.","index":336,"end_time":1065.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1064.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We don''t talk about it.","index":337,"end_time":1066.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1065.88,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I just met with Roz yesterday actually.","index":338,"end_time":1067.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1066.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Did you?","index":339,"end_time":1068.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1068.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Oh, she''s great.","index":340,"end_time":1069.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1068.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I''m spending Christmas Day with her and her family.","index":341,"end_time":1071.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1069.66,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Oh, that''s awesome.","index":342,"end_time":1072.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1071.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, tell her I said hi.","index":343,"end_time":1074.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1072.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I will.","index":344,"end_time":1074.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1074.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":345,"end_time":1075.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1074.9,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She really likes you.","index":346,"end_time":1076.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1075.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I''m glad you''re still with her because.","index":347,"end_time":1078.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.14,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, of course.","index":348,"end_time":1079.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1078.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Cool.","index":349,"end_time":1082.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1082.02,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":350,"end_time":1083.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1082.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":351,"end_time":1083.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1083.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So yeah, just keep us posted on the contacts and then that kind of brings me to.","index":352,"end_time":1087.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1083.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was going to set up the integration with Salesforce but not sync anything and I just wanted to run that by you just so we have the setup.","index":353,"end_time":1095.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1088.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then when we figure out like these are the parameters of contacts we want to bring over, then we can.","index":354,"end_time":1100,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1095.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just turn that on, you know what?","index":355,"end_time":1102.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1100,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Let''s.","index":356,"end_time":1102.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1102.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Let''s do that for.","index":357,"end_time":1104.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1102.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I hate the check in a box thing, but I think we should just say, let''s just check the box.","index":358,"end_time":1111.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1104.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":359,"end_time":1112.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know what?","index":360,"end_time":1113,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1112.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Here''s what we got.","index":361,"end_time":1113.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1113,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We did it.","index":362,"end_time":1114.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1113.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Nothing is sinking, so don''t worry about it.","index":363,"end_time":1116.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1114.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Everybody gets an input.","index":364,"end_time":1117.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1116.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, I just.","index":365,"end_time":1118.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1117.84,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Vivian just sent me a note and said, and she''s amazing, by the way.","index":366,"end_time":1122.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1118.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, she''s absolutely the best boss ever.","index":367,"end_time":1124.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1122.04,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She''s awesome.","index":368,"end_time":1124.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1124.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And she goes, where are we at?","index":369,"end_time":1126.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1125.4,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Because I know people are asking her.","index":370,"end_time":1128,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1126.76,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I said, well, I''m just talking to them now.","index":371,"end_time":1129.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1128,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And Eventbrite is all set up.","index":372,"end_time":1131.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1129.96,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She goes, okay, what about zoom?","index":373,"end_time":1134.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1131.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Done.","index":374,"end_time":1135.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1134.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"What about.","index":375,"end_time":1136.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1135.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m like, just.","index":376,"end_time":1137.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1136.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s.","index":377,"end_time":1138.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1138.52,"speaker_name":"Guille Santana"},{"text":"We''re good.","index":378,"end_time":1139.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1138.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":379,"end_time":1140.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1139.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it takes.","index":380,"end_time":1141.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1140.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, Barbara, I think I''m using your exact words.","index":381,"end_time":1144.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1141.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re a little bit different than most agencies.","index":382,"end_time":1146.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1144.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like, we actually just own things holistically, and if we say we''re going to do something, it''s getting done.","index":383,"end_time":1150.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1146.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":384,"end_time":1152.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1152.18,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And she''s.","index":385,"end_time":1153.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1152.42,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She''s getting there.","index":386,"end_time":1153.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1153.06,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, don''t get me wrong, she just doesn''t really know you guys.","index":387,"end_time":1156.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1153.9,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, I do.","index":388,"end_time":1158.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1157.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I should have maybe invited her to the call, but I don''t want to waste your time either.","index":389,"end_time":1161.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1158.22,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":390,"end_time":1161.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1161.5,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And.","index":391,"end_time":1162.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1161.7,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, and if we ever want to bring her on, just let us know we can.","index":392,"end_time":1164.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1162.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":393,"end_time":1166.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1165.86,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But when that OPCO said they''re.","index":394,"end_time":1167.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1166.22,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"They''re way, way, way behind.","index":395,"end_time":1169.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1167.94,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Months behind, and we''re getting this done in three months and then testing, they didn''t believe it.","index":396,"end_time":1176.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1170.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, well, how is that possible?","index":397,"end_time":1178.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1176.9,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I said, well, who are you using?","index":398,"end_time":1180.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1178.78,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"They said, well, nobody.","index":399,"end_time":1181.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1180.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, that''s.","index":400,"end_time":1182.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1182.1,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s why they answered their own question.","index":401,"end_time":1186.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1182.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s suicide.","index":402,"end_time":1188.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1187.38,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And the other partner, just for you guys, because I''ll do a testimonial whenever you guys want.","index":403,"end_time":1192.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1188.26,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The other.","index":404,"end_time":1193.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1192.42,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"One of the other ones came on and said, everything''s going fantastic and we have an integration partner, but we''re going into our tenth month.","index":405,"end_time":1201.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1193.06,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Wow.","index":406,"end_time":1202.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1201.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":407,"end_time":1203.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1202.98,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Fantastic''s a generous word.","index":408,"end_time":1206.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1204.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":409,"end_time":1207.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1206.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yes.","index":410,"end_time":1212.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1211.54,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":411,"end_time":1212.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1212.18,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I finally got this done yesterday and I did upgrade it, and we''re all good.","index":412,"end_time":1217.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1213.62,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":413,"end_time":1218.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1217.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ll just add in the phone number field and that''ll automatically update on the form then.","index":414,"end_time":1222.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1218.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you guys don''t need to change anything there.","index":415,"end_time":1224.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1222.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":416,"end_time":1224.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1224.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":417,"end_time":1225.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1224.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And moving forward, if you ever need us to hop in and add any codes or anything like that, just let us know.","index":418,"end_time":1230.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1225.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Will do.","index":419,"end_time":1231.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1230.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Thanks.","index":420,"end_time":1231.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1231.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Of course.","index":421,"end_time":1232.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1231.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, then it was.","index":422,"end_time":1235.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1234.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How do we add a section for registration to the website?","index":423,"end_time":1237.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1235.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we''ll build a newsletter subscribe form and give you the embed code for that.","index":424,"end_time":1242.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1239.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then again, if you want us to add it or James to add it, either way is fine.","index":425,"end_time":1247.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1243.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":426,"end_time":1248.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1248.41,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So any date we had in mind, Vivian signed up for a quarterly newsletter I''d like to add this to as a part of our strategy.","index":427,"end_time":1257.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1248.85,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You know, just part of our nurture series saying, you know, make sure you sign up, etc, So I don''t know, mid, mid January.","index":428,"end_time":1264.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1258.73,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Is that possible?","index":429,"end_time":1265.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1265.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we can have this built like next week, and then we can embed it whenever you''re ready to start.","index":430,"end_time":1270.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1266.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, yeah, whatever makes sense.","index":431,"end_time":1273.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1271.45,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I mean, you guys need a vacation as well.","index":432,"end_time":1275.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1273.69,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Barb, when have you known me to do that?","index":433,"end_time":1278.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1276.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Never.","index":434,"end_time":1279.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1279.37,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But you have Marley.","index":435,"end_time":1280.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1279.77,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I know.","index":436,"end_time":1282.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1281.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m so excited for her first Christmas.","index":437,"end_time":1284.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1282.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is she okay?","index":438,"end_time":1285.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1284.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"As an aside, is she.","index":439,"end_time":1286.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1285.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"What is she.","index":440,"end_time":1287.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1286.76,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"What''s her age now?","index":441,"end_time":1288.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1287.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"18.","index":442,"end_time":1288.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1288.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She''s.","index":443,"end_time":1289.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1288.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She''ll be 11 months in a week.","index":444,"end_time":1291.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1289.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, I''m fast forwarding her, but is she.","index":445,"end_time":1295.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1291.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She''s a little young.","index":446,"end_time":1297.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1296.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right, but it''s for the parents.","index":447,"end_time":1299.48,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1297.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we''re getting.","index":448,"end_time":1302.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1300.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think she''s getting excited.","index":449,"end_time":1303.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1302.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We don''t let her watch, like too much tv, but we show her some Christmas cartoons.","index":450,"end_time":1307.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1304.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Had to watch like Charlie Brown, of course.","index":451,"end_time":1310.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1308.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But my wife and I kind of like, she got some gifts and then I got some gifts and we''re just super excited.","index":452,"end_time":1316.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1310.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, fun.","index":453,"end_time":1318.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1317.53,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And my mom is just losing her mind.","index":454,"end_time":1320.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is her first grandchild, so.","index":455,"end_time":1322.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1320.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, my God.","index":456,"end_time":1323.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1322.49,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":457,"end_time":1326.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1326.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we''ve already talked through this, so.","index":458,"end_time":1329.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1326.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, just let us know in your conversations with the team because it definitely gets a little hairy if Marketo has this.","index":459,"end_time":1337.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1329.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Salesforce has this.","index":460,"end_time":1338.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1337.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We just need to know, like, what is the source of truth?","index":461,"end_time":1340.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1338.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then obviously HubSpot becomes that source of truth moving forward.","index":462,"end_time":1343.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1340.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":463,"end_time":1344.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1343.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":464,"end_time":1346.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1344.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then you have pulse.","index":465,"end_time":1347.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1346.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So.","index":466,"end_time":1347.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1347.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I feel like we were missing things on your list or did we just, like, we were on the same page about everything and got through that quickly?","index":467,"end_time":1353.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1348.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think we''re on the same page about everything.","index":468,"end_time":1355.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1353.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We just.","index":469,"end_time":1356.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1355.63,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We got through it.","index":470,"end_time":1357.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1356.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Everything''s a fire drill, so I don''t want to waste anybody''s time.","index":471,"end_time":1361.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1357.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, not wasting our time.","index":472,"end_time":1363.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1361.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we''re.","index":473,"end_time":1365.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1364.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re moving on this stuff.","index":474,"end_time":1366.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1365.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll build out these forms and then.","index":475,"end_time":1370.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1366.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, we''re moving and grooving.","index":476,"end_time":1371.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1370.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What''s your guys plan with Riverside?","index":477,"end_time":1375.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1373,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know that that''s been set up.","index":478,"end_time":1376.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1375.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you been able to log in?","index":479,"end_time":1378.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1376.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So question.","index":480,"end_time":1380.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1378.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I logged in last night.","index":481,"end_time":1382.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1380.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, I. I have the apps.","index":482,"end_time":1383.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1382.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":483,"end_time":1383.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1383.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s what I was.","index":484,"end_time":1384.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1383.96,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Oh, that was a very good question.","index":485,"end_time":1386.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1384.76,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I''m not sure, like I, I logged in.","index":486,"end_time":1388.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1386.24,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay, that was fine.","index":487,"end_time":1389.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1388.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But then it said you have three days.","index":488,"end_time":1391.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1389.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I just want to set the remote expectation.","index":489,"end_time":1393.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1391.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You have three days of free whatever and then it''s going to cost you like $90.","index":490,"end_time":1398.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1393.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":491,"end_time":1399.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1398.89,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I''m like, okay.","index":492,"end_time":1400.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1399.29,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And that''s fine for me, but if we add 100 people, then it''s cost prohibitive.","index":493,"end_time":1406.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1401.29,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":494,"end_time":1406.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1406.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I don''t know how that works.","index":495,"end_time":1408.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1406.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"If, like when I logged in, I used.","index":496,"end_time":1410.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1408.33,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"When I, I put my name in.","index":497,"end_time":1412.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1410.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t know if that was right, if I should have put Aquatic Informatics or something.","index":498,"end_time":1416.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1413.45,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, so we set it up with your.","index":499,"end_time":1420.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1417.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let me just log back up.","index":500,"end_time":1425.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1423.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, so it was accounts plus aquatic informatics@marketers in demand.com.","index":501,"end_time":1430.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1426.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"and that''s how we have to set it up so that you fit under our parent account and then you''re not paying separately for it.","index":502,"end_time":1434.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1430.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, but that was the email.","index":503,"end_time":1437.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1435.61,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But it needed a name.","index":504,"end_time":1438.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1437.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Or is that the name and the email?","index":505,"end_time":1440.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1438.25,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So here, let me just share my screen.","index":506,"end_time":1444.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1442.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, thanks.","index":507,"end_time":1445.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1444.57,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It was late, so I''m just on riverside.com login and then.","index":508,"end_time":1450.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1446.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s the accounts + aquatic informatics marketers in Demand.","index":509,"end_time":1453.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1450.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, okay.","index":510,"end_time":1455.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1454.41,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s the desktop.","index":511,"end_time":1456.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1455.17,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":512,"end_time":1456.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1456.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then it should take you here and, and then, you know, Riverside, you can just create a studio for any conversation or anything that you wanted to host.","index":513,"end_time":1463.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1456.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh, so I have the app and if salespeople.","index":514,"end_time":1467.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1464.01,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Is that possible, they can use the app in the field because they have to put in their name.","index":515,"end_time":1470.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1467.17,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I will have to check on that and get back to you.","index":516,"end_time":1474.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1472.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''d be great.","index":517,"end_time":1475,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1474.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"This makes perfect sense.","index":518,"end_time":1476.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1475,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So this is the Riverside.","index":519,"end_time":1477.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1476.76,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I know, but I never used the app before.","index":520,"end_time":1479.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1477.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I haven''t either.","index":521,"end_time":1481.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1479.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, so it says it works perfectly, but because it said Barb Willens.","index":522,"end_time":1486.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1481.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It says, Barb, you only have three days left.","index":523,"end_time":1488.16,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1486.28,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I''m like, for what?","index":524,"end_time":1489.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1488.16,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":525,"end_time":1490.119,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1489.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not doing it.","index":526,"end_time":1491.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1490.119,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, interesting.","index":527,"end_time":1493.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1491.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":528,"end_time":1493.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1493.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll check in on that.","index":529,"end_time":1494.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1493.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that''d be great.","index":530,"end_time":1497.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1495.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then what''s just, what''s going to happen with this?","index":531,"end_time":1500.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1497.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And, and just so you know, the reason I explained, probably way too much.","index":532,"end_time":1504.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1500.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Vivian again is so impressed.","index":533,"end_time":1506.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1504.04,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And she''s always like, oh, can I, can I call them?","index":534,"end_time":1509.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1506.67,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m like, you can call my mother.","index":535,"end_time":1510.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1509.71,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t care.","index":536,"end_time":1511.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1510.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, you can call anybody you want.","index":537,"end_time":1513.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1511.47,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You can call Tristan, Colin, Gay.","index":538,"end_time":1515.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1513.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like they will answer you and you don''t need to be invited.","index":539,"end_time":1518.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1515.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And she''s not one to wait for an invite, but she''s just, she''s excited.","index":540,"end_time":1523.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1518.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":541,"end_time":1523.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1523.31,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And Riverside, she wants to train the salespeople mid January.","index":542,"end_time":1527.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1523.55,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I started with a standard work document and how you do that.","index":543,"end_time":1531.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1527.39,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But the app is what they want and I, I hit a snag last night, so.","index":544,"end_time":1535.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1531.31,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Desktop.","index":545,"end_time":1535.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1535.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yes, I''ll.","index":546,"end_time":1536.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1535.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll check.","index":547,"end_time":1536.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1536.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''d be great.","index":548,"end_time":1538.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1537.66,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":549,"end_time":1538.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1538.38,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So she''s, she''s excited.","index":550,"end_time":1540.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1538.74,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"No problem at all.","index":551,"end_time":1541.42,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1540.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":552,"end_time":1543.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1542.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":553,"end_time":1543.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1543.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anything.","index":554,"end_time":1544.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1543.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know, anything on the other contract that also.","index":555,"end_time":1548.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1544.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That we can help out with that''s more like less hubs or.","index":556,"end_time":1550.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1548.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean it could be HubSpot Focus, but just anything that you need additional support with.","index":557,"end_time":1554.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1550.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":558,"end_time":1556.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1555.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So what I''m doing, maybe this afternoon, definitely next week, is setting up.","index":559,"end_time":1561.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1556.38,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We talked about the pillars of productivity, starting with dashboards.","index":560,"end_time":1566.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1561.86,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I do have a date for the dashboards.","index":561,"end_time":1568.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1566.87,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''ll be a simulive event, but I want to put like, I want to put it as a campaign in the HubSpot.","index":562,"end_time":1575.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1568.83,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ve got the lists and constant contacts.","index":563,"end_time":1578.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1576.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So just putting together a campaign brief on that saying this is what I want to do.","index":564,"end_time":1582.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1578.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You know, like we, we had it all set to go at the very end of November and it just, the.","index":565,"end_time":1593.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1582.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The lady couldn''t get me the recording.","index":566,"end_time":1595.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1593.77,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She had a tragedy happen.","index":567,"end_time":1597.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1595.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And we''re not monsters, you know, but we canceled it like 15 minutes prior.","index":568,"end_time":1602.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1597.41,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And for a 20 minute recording we have like 150 people.","index":569,"end_time":1607.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1602.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And so we kind of.","index":570,"end_time":1608.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1607.45,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We want to keep that because 20 minutes everybody''s in.","index":571,"end_time":1612.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1608.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So we just want to make sure that we still have that.","index":572,"end_time":1615.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1613.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But, but so I need to put together the brief is the short answer.","index":573,"end_time":1619.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1615.77,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then we have.","index":574,"end_time":1621.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1620.64,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So we''ve got three things, key things for January.","index":575,"end_time":1624.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1621.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"One is starting the pillars of productivity.","index":576,"end_time":1627.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1625.28,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We wanted that landing page that they can go to afterwards.","index":577,"end_time":1631.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1627.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That is not a webinar.","index":578,"end_time":1632.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1631.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s starting building out that program.","index":579,"end_time":1634.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1632.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The second thing is using Riverside for content.","index":580,"end_time":1640.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1635.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"People are going to be refreshed and hitting the ground and we want to like they were excited.","index":581,"end_time":1646.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1641.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Aquarius more than whims, but they''re all feel like they''re all hydrologists.","index":582,"end_time":1651.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1646.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So they''re in the field.","index":583,"end_time":1652.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1651.85,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Right.","index":584,"end_time":1652.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.45,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So they, they want that program.","index":585,"end_time":1654.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1652.73,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Haven''t thought it through what I want to do with it yet, but we need somewhere to put that stuff.","index":586,"end_time":1659.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1654.61,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":587,"end_time":1660.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1659.25,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"With.","index":588,"end_time":1660.969,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1660.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"With some guidelines.","index":589,"end_time":1662.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1660.969,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then the third is we have a digital twin again.","index":590,"end_time":1669.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1663.65,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''ll be simulive at the end of January.","index":591,"end_time":1672.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1669.73,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So those are the three big things that I just.","index":592,"end_time":1676.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1673.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Whether it''s like nurture is the first one, the second one, I''m not sure.","index":593,"end_time":1682.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1676.96,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The third is net new.","index":594,"end_time":1684.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1682.72,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So just let me put the campaign briefs together next week, you guys, and I''ll.","index":595,"end_time":1690.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1685.04,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ll share it with you and then.","index":596,"end_time":1691.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1690.4,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Then you can help me.","index":597,"end_time":1692.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1691.52,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":598,"end_time":1693.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1692.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Then we can build landing pages, whatever you need.","index":599,"end_time":1695.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1693.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it sounds like we''ll need, like, a content syndication.","index":600,"end_time":1697.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1695.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Landing page.","index":601,"end_time":1698.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1697.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":602,"end_time":1699,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1698.68,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":603,"end_time":1699.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1699.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":604,"end_time":1700.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1699.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, we can definitely do that.","index":605,"end_time":1701.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1700.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":606,"end_time":1702.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1701.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So that was a question Vivian had said, well, does New north build out the landing pages microsite, you know, or is it James?","index":607,"end_time":1711.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1704.12,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I said, well, like, we''re keeping James for sure.","index":608,"end_time":1714.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1711.88,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like he.","index":609,"end_time":1714.759,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1714.2,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, but we did speak with him, he''s wonderful.","index":610,"end_time":1717.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1715.48,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The other day, and said, you know, your role, like, we''re going to give them more of a role for, you know, for consistency.","index":611,"end_time":1725.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1717.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And.","index":612,"end_time":1726.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1725.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And he understood that, you know, but we still need him, you know.","index":613,"end_time":1729.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1726.41,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Well, he hosts the website on his own server, too.","index":614,"end_time":1731.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1729.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know.","index":615,"end_time":1732.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1731.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Don''t want to upset that guy, seriously, but he''s.","index":616,"end_time":1736.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1732.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"He''s wonderful.","index":617,"end_time":1737.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1736.89,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So, anyway, we''re.","index":618,"end_time":1738.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1737.57,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re just trying to skinny down, I think the.","index":619,"end_time":1742.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1739.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The number of.","index":620,"end_time":1744.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1743.69,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Not the number of contractors, but the number of orphans we got out there.","index":621,"end_time":1750.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1745.69,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s a good word for it.","index":622,"end_time":1752.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1750.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":623,"end_time":1752.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1752.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s like disparate systems.","index":624,"end_time":1754,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1752.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":625,"end_time":1755.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1754.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, for sure.","index":626,"end_time":1756.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1755.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So, yeah.","index":627,"end_time":1757.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1756.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And then.","index":628,"end_time":1758.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1757.84,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, my last question was just on Databox.","index":629,"end_time":1761.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1758.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''m not sure if you''ve shown that to anybody or if you wanted anything else added in the meantime.","index":630,"end_time":1765.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1761.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, obviously we''re going to build.","index":631,"end_time":1766.559,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1765.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That out, but, yeah.","index":632,"end_time":1768.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1766.559,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Did I show it?","index":633,"end_time":1769.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1768.4,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I didn''t mean to show it, but I did.","index":634,"end_time":1773.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1770.56,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I was on a BDR call, and I know we''re at time, so this will just take one minute.","index":635,"end_time":1779.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1773.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But you''re fine.","index":636,"end_time":1780.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1779.63,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":637,"end_time":1781.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1781.11,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So when I was going through it, Vivian had to drop, so she recorded the last 15 minutes.","index":638,"end_time":1785.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1781.55,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But I went through it with Jess, her boss, and the bdr, which is Blake.","index":639,"end_time":1789.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1785.79,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I was going through all of this.","index":640,"end_time":1791.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1790.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I''ve gone through.","index":641,"end_time":1792.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1791.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ve already put up all of my requests.","index":642,"end_time":1797.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1793.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I said, look, they kept asking, what can they do?","index":643,"end_time":1800.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1797.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"What can they do?","index":644,"end_time":1801.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1800.75,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I said, look, all you can do is ask.","index":645,"end_time":1803.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1801.27,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And they can say no, but just ask.","index":646,"end_time":1805.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1803.47,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like you can ask them anything.","index":647,"end_time":1807.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1806.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And that 11,000 just makes me laugh.","index":648,"end_time":1810.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1808.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That was the Christmas card, which I will.","index":649,"end_time":1811.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1810.05,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You crushed it, barb.","index":650,"end_time":1812.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1811.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You''re up 580,000% on leads.","index":651,"end_time":1814.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1812.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can retire.","index":652,"end_time":1816.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1815.57,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yes.","index":653,"end_time":1817.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1816.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Finally.","index":654,"end_time":1817.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1817.25,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s fantastic.","index":655,"end_time":1819.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1818.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"No, so I''ve done my part.","index":656,"end_time":1822.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1819.49,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Vivian and Jess and Blake will all be done today.","index":657,"end_time":1825.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1822.45,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I Gave them until the end of today to give their initial feedback.","index":658,"end_time":1829.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1825.49,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I said, it''s not finite.","index":659,"end_time":1831.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1829.93,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We just need something for January that we can start to build off of.","index":660,"end_time":1835.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1832.13,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I don''t think it''s anything I''m asking for.","index":661,"end_time":1840.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1836.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I think you''ve already done in the past for me, but for them, they''d never seen the filters or like the, the charts and that type of thing.","index":662,"end_time":1852.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1840.39,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":663,"end_time":1852.669,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1852.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can change how these are visually represented.","index":664,"end_time":1854.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1852.669,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can set up filters.","index":665,"end_time":1856.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1854.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, you guys can do that too also just from looking at it any way you want.","index":666,"end_time":1860.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1856.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So for sure.","index":667,"end_time":1862.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1860.99,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And so I guess the goal is for this mid January, when Vivian is in front of all of goes.","index":668,"end_time":1869.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1862.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I think this, this will be like, I love this.","index":669,"end_time":1874.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1870.33,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"This is.","index":670,"end_time":1874.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1874.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I always told you, Colin, this is the best tool I''ve ever had in my hundred years of marketing, ever.","index":671,"end_time":1879.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1874.49,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I don''t know why everyone doesn''t come to you guys for this.","index":672,"end_time":1882.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1880.09,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, you should this or something.","index":673,"end_time":1884.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1882.97,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I, when I showed it and I said, look at draft, draft, draft, look at this.","index":674,"end_time":1889.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1885.21,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And they were just like, everybody should have like every as a marketer.","index":675,"end_time":1896.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1889.77,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And so she really wants to be confident that she can stand up in front of them in January is the goal.","index":676,"end_time":1903.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1896.8,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, well, we''re not going to have a lot of data yet, but you''re going to have enough to be dangerous that you can show them.","index":677,"end_time":1911.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1903.44,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And, and we can have, if she wants to join one of these and go through any questions or anything or even like a training of how to change some of the views and everything, we can do that.","index":678,"end_time":1919.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1911.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If you wanted us to brand it like AQI colors, we could do that as well.","index":679,"end_time":1924.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1920.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know if that will help with her.","index":680,"end_time":1927.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1925.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What was it?","index":681,"end_time":1928.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1927.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The AQI socialization call.","index":682,"end_time":1930.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1928.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, yeah, I mean, we can do anything.","index":683,"end_time":1932.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1931.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, so I talked to her about that.","index":684,"end_time":1935.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1933.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So the purple is the Veralto color.","index":685,"end_time":1937.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1935.15,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So that''s our parent company.","index":686,"end_time":1938.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1937.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And so everybody''s calling this something different.","index":687,"end_time":1942.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1940.15,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I said, I suggested we just call it the aqua box and change it to our brand colors.","index":688,"end_time":1950.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1943.03,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And I thought Viv would love that.","index":689,"end_time":1952.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1950.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"No, not love that.","index":690,"end_time":1954.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1953.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"She goes, this is my data box.","index":691,"end_time":1960.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1958.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, I don''t care.","index":692,"end_time":1961.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1960.83,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So she''s the boss.","index":693,"end_time":1963.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1962.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And.","index":694,"end_time":1963.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1963.39,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But everybody, they''re calling it the black box.","index":695,"end_time":1967.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1964.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The.","index":696,"end_time":1967.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1967.15,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"They''re calling it, Everybody''s calling it something the purple box.","index":697,"end_time":1972.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1968.19,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Just the box.","index":698,"end_time":1974.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1973.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m like, can we get some consistency?","index":699,"end_time":1976.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1974.39,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Because Viv has to socialize this.","index":700,"end_time":1978.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1976.55,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So I think it''s going to be the AQI data box.","index":701,"end_time":1981.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1978.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But our, our colors wouldn''t Be bad.","index":702,"end_time":1983.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1981.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But before you do anything, I''ll talk to her first.","index":703,"end_time":1987.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1983.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But.","index":704,"end_time":1987.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1987.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Okay.","index":705,"end_time":1987.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1987.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, just in.","index":706,"end_time":1988.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1987.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In their feedback, if that''s something they want, just let us know.","index":707,"end_time":1991.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1988.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For sure.","index":708,"end_time":1992.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1991.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ll get them to put it in the document.","index":709,"end_time":1993.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1992.39,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''ll get a. I''ll get a better version of your logo added in here, too.","index":710,"end_time":1996.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1993.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"This is just.","index":711,"end_time":1997.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1996.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was building it Friday night, so.","index":712,"end_time":1999.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1997.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"For sure.","index":713,"end_time":2001.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2001.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":714,"end_time":2002.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2001.82,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"There''s some sections that we wanted added and things that we haven''t talked about yet for next year.","index":715,"end_time":2007.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2002.06,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And just to leave you on this note, we''ve budgeted.","index":716,"end_time":2010.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2008.3,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You guys don''t know how much yet past Q1, but we want to make sure that, you know, we keep this train moving, you know, and.","index":717,"end_time":2020.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2010.9,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And so she has this big budget call today.","index":718,"end_time":2024.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2020.3,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But just know that it''s not.","index":719,"end_time":2025.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2024.3,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"The goal is not just to cut you off after Q1.","index":720,"end_time":2028.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2026.14,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, we, you know, we kind of not kind of.","index":721,"end_time":2032.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2028.62,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We do need you.","index":722,"end_time":2033.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2032.58,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"After that whole OPCO call that we had, it was apparent.","index":723,"end_time":2039.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2033.34,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It was like, how are you guys doing this in three months?","index":724,"end_time":2042.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2039.74,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Just have the right partner.","index":725,"end_time":2046.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2045.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":726,"end_time":2046.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2046.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I mean, to be completely transparent, we see so much opportunity for your guys, marketing campaigns and everything like that too, so.","index":727,"end_time":2054.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2046.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Would definitely love to be a part of that journey.","index":728,"end_time":2056.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2054.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":729,"end_time":2057.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2057.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, you''re.","index":730,"end_time":2058.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2057.79,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You''re in the plan.","index":731,"end_time":2059.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2058.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So let''s.","index":732,"end_time":2059.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2059.27,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Let''s see if she can get it over the.","index":733,"end_time":2061.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2060.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Over the line today.","index":734,"end_time":2063.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2062.47,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But that''s the plan.","index":735,"end_time":2065.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2063.47,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And, And I just.","index":736,"end_time":2066.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2065.11,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I know we''re over time, but I want to wish you guys such a happy holiday.","index":737,"end_time":2070.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2067.19,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"When I moved over here, it''s only been four months, but I can''t even believe what we''ve done in four months.","index":738,"end_time":2075.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2070.95,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And we hit our goal in four months.","index":739,"end_time":2078.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2075.87,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s crazy.","index":740,"end_time":2080.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2079.06,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Next year it''s gonna be.","index":741,"end_time":2082.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2081.7,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"That''s the Barb effect.","index":742,"end_time":2083.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2082.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, well, I don''t know about that, but I think next year with you guys, we''re just gonna.","index":743,"end_time":2089.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2084.1,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We''re gonna hit this out of the park.","index":744,"end_time":2092.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2090.9,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Like, I know it.","index":745,"end_time":2093.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2092.38,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s such a great company.","index":746,"end_time":2095.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2094.1,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And yeah, we were.","index":747,"end_time":2097.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2095.3,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We were named one of Forbes top 25 companies for 2026.","index":748,"end_time":2102.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2097.86,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Love it.","index":749,"end_time":2102.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2102.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s awesome.","index":750,"end_time":2104.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2103.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yep.","index":751,"end_time":2105.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2104.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And so everybody''s kind of riding the high into the.","index":752,"end_time":2108.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2105.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Into the holidays.","index":753,"end_time":2109.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2108.27,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":754,"end_time":2110.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2109.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":755,"end_time":2111.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2110.83,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And the top 250 for the Wall Street Journal.","index":756,"end_time":2113.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2111.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"So everyone''s like, that''s awesome.","index":757,"end_time":2115.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2113.87,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"We''re doing okay.","index":758,"end_time":2117.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2116.27,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, definitely.","index":759,"end_time":2119.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2117.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And you guys are superstars, and you guys always make me look good.","index":760,"end_time":2123.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2119.79,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Colin, Gaye, you''re wonderful.","index":761,"end_time":2125.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2123.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"But Colin is like my, My, my marketing brother here.","index":762,"end_time":2130.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2125.75,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"He makes me look good all the time.","index":763,"end_time":2132.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2130.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":764,"end_time":2132.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2132.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"DA was surprised how long we''ve been working together.","index":765,"end_time":2134.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2132.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I was like, I''ve been working with Barb since like 2021.","index":766,"end_time":2137.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2134.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know.","index":767,"end_time":2138.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2137.55,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s.","index":768,"end_time":2138.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2138.07,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"It''s been like almost five years.","index":769,"end_time":2139.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2138.43,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I''m like, anytime I need something, I just.","index":770,"end_time":2142.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2139.75,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You always have that, that, that thing in your back pocket.","index":771,"end_time":2146.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2142.51,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Not think this, this, you know, whatever.","index":772,"end_time":2149.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2146.23,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Some sort of solution.","index":773,"end_time":2150.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2149.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":774,"end_time":2151.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2150.91,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"In your back pocket.","index":775,"end_time":2152.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2151.35,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"And it''s.","index":776,"end_time":2152.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2152.19,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You guys, it''s like, I just don''t.","index":777,"end_time":2154.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2152.59,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I wouldn''t call anybody else.","index":778,"end_time":2157.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2155.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I wouldn''t.","index":779,"end_time":2157.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2157.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":780,"end_time":2158.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2157.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"I appreciate that.","index":781,"end_time":2159.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2158.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":782,"end_time":2160.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2159.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":783,"end_time":2161.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2160.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Wishing you the best holidays as well.","index":784,"end_time":2162.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2161.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Tell Roz that I said hi.","index":785,"end_time":2164.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2162.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then.","index":786,"end_time":2165.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2164.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, anything we need to do to help out with the.","index":787,"end_time":2168.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2165.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The socialization in mid January, we''ll get those forms updated and we''ll create a newsletter sign up option as well.","index":788,"end_time":2174.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2168.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll check in on the Riverside mobile stuff also.","index":789,"end_time":2177.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2174.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''d be great.","index":790,"end_time":2178.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2178.16,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":791,"end_time":2179.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2178.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":792,"end_time":2180.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2179.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":793,"end_time":2180.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2180.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Happy holidays, everybody.","index":794,"end_time":2181.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2180.6,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"Yeah, have a great weekend.","index":795,"end_time":2183.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2181.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Take care.","index":796,"end_time":2183.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2183.36,"speaker_name":"bwillans"},{"text":"You guys too.","index":797,"end_time":2184.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2183.92,"speaker_name":"bwillans"}],"dateString":"2025-12-19T16:00:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/89786281993?pwd=li2lwrSFpmITXPKEdOBBgaXPwh8ONO.1","participants":["guille.santana@marketersindemand.com,tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com,colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,barb.willans@aquaticinformatics.com","guille.santana@marketersindemand.com","tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com","barb.willans@aquaticinformatics.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KC9RJFZ6MJZMS39SZPGHMDKD","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.94,"bullets":["Confirmed Eventbrite integration is live; syncing to track customer registration and Salesforce alignment underway.","Agreed to consolidate outdated forms and standardize opt-in fields across HubSpot assets.","Scheduled Salesforce sync setup with syncing paused; future contact rules to follow team input.","Planned January rollout of dashboards, Riverside video content, and digital twin campaign.","Barb confirmed goal met in four months; team targeting expanded collaboration beyond Q1."],"highlights":[{"quote":"We hit our goal in four months.","speaker":"bwillans"},{"quote":"We''re moving and grooving.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"Vivian again is so impressed.","speaker":"bwillans"}],"topics":["integration","forms","salesforce","delivery","reporting"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-turbo","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-12-19T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Integration and Event Management**\n\nThe team finalized the setup of the **Eventbrite-HubSpot integration** to track customer attendance at regional user group meetings, aiming to streamline event registration and communication (04:04).\n\n- The integration now connects Eventbrite events with HubSpot, allowing toggling of event sync, though only one event, the **Manatee County, Florida**, currently exists.\n- **Barbara Willans** explained the goal is to track customers and prospects attending these events to tailor upgrades and campaigns for the upcoming year.\n- Communication will shift from **Marketo and Reg Fox** to HubSpot for invites, improving consistency and reducing complexity.\n- The integration will track both registrations and attendees through custom fields to enable targeted follow-up communications.\n\n## **Forms Consolidation and Optimization**\n\nThe team identified significant opportunities to consolidate and standardize marketing forms on the website, particularly moving away from complicated Marketo forms to HubSpot’s more flexible platform (06:04).\n\n- The **HAWK form**, a critical sales lead capture form, was unintentionally destroyed on **December 5th** and requires Adobe support to reset due to Marketo limitations.\n- **Barbara** emphasized the need to rebuild essential forms in HubSpot and retire outdated forms, some as old as **13 years**.\n- Phone number fields will be added as **optional** for consistency, as required fields have been shown to reduce registration rates.\n- The sales coordinator starting soon will manage lead form data entries, especially for dropdown selections linked to sales commissions, which will be rebuilt without reliance on Marketo’s complex dropdowns.\n\n## **Contact Data and Salesforce Integration**\n\nThe current contact and opportunity data totals **29,102** accounts under broad criteria but will narrow significantly when filtered by recent fiscal years, pending sales team input (14:43).\n\n- **Barbara** plans to gather feedback from sales leads on refining contact lists and parameters in a meeting on **December 29th**.\n- Salesforce integration setup will begin with syncing turned off to prepare the system until filtering rules are finalized.\n- Data sources for mailing lists currently span **Marketo, Salesforce, Upgrades Desk Pro, and Constant Contact**, causing reconciliation challenges.\n- HubSpot will become the central source of truth moving forward to consolidate fragmented data streams.\n\n## **Content and Campaign Planning**\n\nThree key content initiatives are scheduled for **January**, focusing on productivity, content refresh, and new product promotion (27:26).\n\n- The **pillars of productivity** campaign will launch with a simulive event and corresponding landing page, designed as a nurture program.\n- **Riverside** will be used for refreshed content creation, targeting field hydrologists, especially at **Aquarius** and **Whims** OPCOs.\n- A **digital twin** simulive event planned at January''s end will serve as a net-new lead generation effort.\n- **Barbara** will prepare campaign briefs next week to enable landing page and nurture workflow builds.\n\n## **Dashboard and Reporting Enhancements**\n\nA new **Databox dashboard** has been introduced and is under review by **Vivian, Jess, and Blake** with initial feedback expected by the end of the week to prepare for a presentation in mid-January (29:26).\n\n- The dashboard currently shows inflated lead numbers due to inclusion of the Christmas card campaign but will refine as filters are adjusted.\n- The goal is to socialize this dashboard as the **AQI Data Box** during the **Vivian Aqi socialization** with sales teams in mid-January.\n- Branding updates and customizations will follow feedback, including color scheme alignment and logo improvements.\n- Colin offered additional training and customization support to help Vivian confidently present the data to stakeholders.\n\n## **Technology and Operational Support**\n\nOperational readiness includes ongoing support for **Riverside** usage and form embedding, with cost and user access considerations addressed (22:58).\n\n- Riverside’s current setup allows desktop usage under the parent account email to avoid individual costs, but mobile app licensing and user experience require clarification.\n- Vivian aims to train the sales team on Riverside in mid-January, so resolving app access and cost issues is a priority.\n- The team will deliver the **newsletter subscribe form** embed code by next week for a planned mid-January launch aligned with nurture efforts.\n- Colin emphasized readiness to assist with ongoing form updates, code additions, and campaign support to keep projects on track through Q1 and beyond.","outline":null,"keywords":["Eventbrite Integration","HubSpot Forms","Salesforce Sync","Riverside Podcast","Databox Analytics","Marketing Campaign Planning"],"overview":"- **Eventbrite Integration Complete:** HubSpot now tracks attendance for events like the upcoming Manatee County meeting, streamlining communication.  \n- **Forms Optimization Needed:** Consolidate marketing forms, move to HubSpot; rebuild critical HAWK form after accidental deletion.  \n- **Contact Data Review Planned:** 29,102 accounts will be refined with sales input to improve data quality and filtering methods.  \n- **January Campaign Initiatives:** Key content campaigns will focus on productivity, content refresh, and new product promotion, starting mid-January.  \n- **New Databox Dashboard:** Under review for lead metrics; adjustments needed for Christmas campaign data before mid-January presentation.  \n- **Riverside Support Ongoing:** Training for sales team in January; resolving app access and cost issues is a priority.","action_items":"\n**Barb Willans**\nProvide the talk track for Vivian Aqi’s OPCO socialization presentation mid-January (02:20)\nRetrieve or recreate dropdown options for the HAWK form salespeople assignment to populate HubSpot (13:00)\nCoordinate with sales leads on refining contact data parameters for clean lists ahead of Jan 29 meeting (14:40)\nRemove Christmas card recipients from HubSpot due to DNS issues and monitor list data cleanup (15:40)\nPrepare campaign briefs for three January initiatives (Pillars of Productivity dashboards, Riverside content use, Digital Twin event) and share with marketing team (27:00)\nConsult Vivian on Databox branding preferences and compile feedback for dashboard adjustments (32:50)\nFollow up on Riverside app usage for field salespeople and relay any issues for technical resolution (24:35)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nBuild and consolidate forms in HubSpot from provided audit list; add phone number field as optional on all forms (09:10)\nSet up Salesforce integration ''ready but not syncing'' to allow configuration and future enablement (18:20)\nProvide embed code for newsletter subscription form for deployment by client or contractor (20:45)\nConfirm Riverside account setup under parent account and investigate app usage licenses for sales in the field (23:45)\nCustomize Databox dashboards with improved logo and potentially AQI branding once feedback received (33:10)\nCoordinate support for socialization materials and forms update for January OPCO presentation (36:15)\n\n**Guille Santana**\nClarify and assist with underlying form structure improvements and dropdown alternatives for sales lead allocation (10:00)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"e74ae283-1b0e-4f79-8913-bec0666689bc","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
