,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"There are good weeks, there are bad weeks, but like from the new registrations, unfortunately there are a lot of really small companies, like I think what we call companies size 1 and 2.","index":422,"end_time":1636.27,"speaker_id":7,"start_time":1627.15,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"So lower than 20.","index":423,"end_time":1637.43,"speaker_id":7,"start_time":1636.27,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"So less than 20 employees is like half of it or even more from the valid ones.","index":424,"end_time":1643.76,"speaker_id":7,"start_time":1638.79,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"And then if we count them out, it''s even less than one per week, which is a valid new registration with like a company says that would even pay for it.","index":425,"end_time":1655.36,"speaker_id":7,"start_time":1645.2,"speaker_name":"MaximilianRabeler"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":426,"end_time":1658.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1657.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":427,"end_time":1658.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1658.36,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, but it''s.","index":428,"end_time":1662,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1661.04,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"They without.","index":429,"end_time":1662.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1662,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Basically, without any marketing, they somehow find us.","index":430,"end_time":1665.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1662.88,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We don''t really know how.","index":431,"end_time":1668,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1665.44,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":432,"end_time":1671.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1670.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I think with a more targeted approach, where we''re already identifying them based.","index":433,"end_time":1675.81,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1671.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"On company size and pushing them towards free registration, obviously that''s a much tighter fit.","index":434,"end_time":1679.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1675.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":435,"end_time":1681.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1680.89,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":436,"end_time":1684.09,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1683.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Just being cognizant of time.","index":437,"end_time":1686.61,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1685.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''ve already explained the marketing infrastructure.","index":438,"end_time":1689.53,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1686.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And again, we''ll send over this slide.","index":439,"end_time":1691.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1690.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But this is just all the different technology that comes into this campaign.","index":440,"end_time":1694.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1691.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then we''ve also identified all of the activities that we will be going through.","index":441,"end_time":1699.97,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1695.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And this is also already built into to your portal in Pulse, so you.","index":442,"end_time":1704.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1699.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can go in here and see the.","index":443,"end_time":1706.71,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1704.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Items that we''re working on.","index":444,"end_time":1707.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1706.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re delivering this updated roadmap document today.","index":445,"end_time":1709.75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1707.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re also working on the video plan.","index":446,"end_time":1712.07,"speaker_