with obviously.","index":485,"end_time":1834.07,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1832.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In one email sending people to the.","index":486,"end_time":1835.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1834.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Registration so that they can do a self guided.","index":487,"end_time":1837.59,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1835.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The new landing page is likely going to be geared around this story lane demo optimization and explaining the different features.","index":488,"end_time":1845.59,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1837.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Of Desi Dollo''s offering.","index":489,"end_time":1847.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1845.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":490,"end_time":1850.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1850.19,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"All right, any questions?","index":491,"end_time":1855.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1852.59,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Max, Bettina, did we already think about something like a recommendation feature?","index":492,"end_time":1861.07,"speaker_id":8,"start_time":1855.51,"speaker_name":"HendrikPollex"},{"text":"So like in that was just coming to my mind.","index":493,"end_time":1864.71,"speaker_id":8,"start_time":1861.31,"speaker_name":"HendrikPollex"},{"text":"So some of my most used apps maybe have something like you recommend your app to a friend and get the next license month off.","index":494,"end_time":1875.24,"speaker_id":8,"start_time":1864.71,"speaker_name":"HendrikPollex"},{"text":"So like a referral almost.","index":495,"end_time":1877.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1875.32,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, referral.","index":496,"end_time":1878.84,"speaker_id":8,"start_time":1877.88,"speaker_name":"HendrikPollex"},{"text":"Yeah, I think you mentioned that Colin.","index":497,"end_time":1881,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1878.84,"