    1841,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/85039954260?pwd=7GrXTMosQASbwQapyiVncGn3aAbQCz.1',
    '{"id":"01KC4WAEMBHQY49MHWB0RVE843","title":"MiD//Noetic: Weekly Set Meeting  5/8 - Onwards","summary":{"notes":"## **Podcast Production and Release Schedule**\n\nThe team is accelerating podcast releases to clear backlog by end of March and improve audience engagement.\n\n- **Podcast episodes recorded on January 21 and February 4** have been scheduled for release to speed up backlog clearance (08:25)\n    - Rachel Curtis confirmed the team reordered episodes based on recording dates to prioritize older content\n    - The goal is to release summer episodes faster after holiday compilations to maintain momentum\n    - This tighter schedule addresses previous delays and aims to increase audience retention through consistent posting\n    - Rachel and Julia will keep updating release dates as progress continues\n\n- **Compilation video will be completed by January 18 and reviewed on January 19** to prep for a teaser launch next week (11:01)\n    - Rachel suggested teasing a clip the week before full launch for two weeks during early January\n    - The teaser and full video rollout plan aligns with holiday timing to maximize visibility\n    - Friday’s 30-minute review meeting is set to finalize marketing details and asset preparation\n    - This approach supports continuous engagement during a typically slow season\n\n- **Increasing podcast guest promotional support to boost reach** was recommended (21:29)\n    - Rachel proposed providing guests with clear promotional assets and instructions for sharing\n    - Colin agreed that setting expectations for tagging and sharing could amplify audience growth\n    - This formalizes guest involvement as part of the podcast marketing framework\n    - The team plans to implement this to maximize each episode’s impact\n\n## **AI Campaign Launch and Management**\n\nThe AI marketing campaign will launch immediately with a 10-day managed run and ongoing asset use planned.\n\n- **Decision to launch the AI campaign now with a cutoff on December 31** to test early engagement during the holiday period (16:38)\n    - Nancy requested the campaign start immediately with the ability to pause at year-end\n    - Colin confirmed the campaign tools (Smart Lead for email and Heyreach for LinkedIn) are ready for handoff\n    - The initial run will serve as a test to gather early performance data during a slower week\n    - Follow-up discussions on campaign management and tool subscriptions are scheduled for Friday\n\n- **Landing page for AI campaign is live but hidden from site navigation and accessible via direct link** (17:25)\n    - Colin confirmed the page is on the WordPress site and ready for use in outreach\n    - Nancy requested the direct URL for easy insertion into email templates and LinkedIn messages\n    - This setup allows controlled traffic flow while keeping the page ready for future navigation inclusion\n    - The team is monitoring user engagement as a leading indicator for AI campaign interest\n\n- **Account transfers and tool subscriptions for campaign management are under review** (19:40)\n    - Colin noted Riverside cannot be transferred due to account linking, but Bussprout and Adroll transfers are in progress\n    - Nancy emphasized the need to list tools with their functions to decide on subscriptions versus pausing\n    - Riverside is confirmed at Business Premium level with all features and discounted pricing due to volume\n    - Final decisions on tool ownership and outsourcing will be made after further internal discussions with Tiffany\n\n## **Platform and Tool Management**\n\nThe team is aligning on platform ownership and feature retention to ensure continuity and cost efficiency.\n\n- **Riverside access will end on January 31, requiring downloads of final assets before then** (22:50)\n    - Rachel confirmed downloading episodes from Pulse while Riverside remains active\n    - Colin will send detailed shutdown timelines and last request deadlines via email\n    - This ensures no loss of content and smooth transition as accounts transfer or close\n    - The team is preparing for this transition to avoid operational disruptions\n\n- **Riverside’s Business Premium tier provides early access to features including AI tools** (24:34)\n    - Nancy sought confirmation on feature levels and discounts for annual payment\n    - Colin clarified all client accounts are Business Premium with ongoing feature updates and discounts\n    - This ensures the team retains full functionality without feature gaps post-transfer\n    - Understanding subscription terms helps inform budgeting and renewal strategies\n\n## **Meeting Scheduling and Coordination**\n\nUpcoming meetings are being adjusted around holidays to maintain focus on deliverables without overloading the team.\n\n- **The team agreed to hold the next meeting on Friday and reconsider meetings during holiday weeks** (29:01)\n    - Colin noted closures on December 25 and January 1; team members have partial availability\n    - Nancy suggested canceling the December 22 meeting and possibly moving the December 31 meeting earlier if needed\n    - The focus will be on reviewing AI campaign metrics and finalizing outstanding items\n    - Flexibility in scheduling supports workload balance during a busy season\n\n## **Strategic Client Engagement: Waymo Opportunity**\n\nThere is promising client interest from Waymo, signaling potential for significant future work.\n\n- **Nancy has a third call scheduled with Waymo on Friday indicating serious engagement** (25:49)\n    - Colin shared enthusiasm, noting Waymo’s strong growth potential and market impact\n    - Nancy highlighted the need for proactive brand reputation management due to mixed public sentiment and competitive pressure from Elon Musk\n    - The team recognizes the sensitivity and complexity of this client’s public image\n    - Decisions on featuring Waymo as a client logo will be made cautiously based on progress\n\n- **Waymo’s tech-driven, rapid expansion requires specialized communication strategies** (26:24)\n    - The client’s aggressive market testing and regulatory challenges present unique messaging needs\n    - Nancy and Colin agreed that thoughtful brand management will be critical to long-term success\n    - This opportunity aligns with the team''s expertise in managing complex tech client reputations\n    - The team is preparing to support Waymo’s evolving priorities as engagement deepens","outline":null,"keywords":["Podcast scheduling","Compilation video","AI campaign","Marketing tools transfer","Riverside subscription","Waymo client engagement"],"overview":"- **Accelerated Podcast Schedule:** Team aims to clear podcast backlog by end of March; older content prioritized for engagement.  \n- **Teaser Video Completion:** Compilation video ready by January 18; teaser clips to enhance visibility pre-launch.  \n- **AI Campaign Launch:** Immediate AI campaign launch planned to gather early data; runs until December 31 with management discussions scheduled.  \n- **Riverside Access Deadline:** Riverside access ends January 31; team coordinating downloads to ensure no content loss before shutdown.  \n- **Waymo Client Engagement:** Positive client interest from Waymo; strategic communication is vital due to their rapid expansion and public sentiment.  \n- **Meeting Adjustments:** Upcoming meetings to be rescheduled around holidays; focus on workload balance and reviewing campaign metrics.","action_items":"\n**Rachel Curtis**\nContinue sending podcast episode feedback and updates on asset packages (07:31)\nPrepare for real-time review of compilation video during Friday''s Cred Stack meeting (14:02)\nCoordinate posts and asset preparation during compilation video run post-New Year (14:49)\n\n**Nancieruder**\nCoordinate with Tiffany on financial and logistical closeout to ensure alignment and oversight (06:53)\nApprove compilation video teaser release early next week and full release following week of New Year’s (13:59)\nConfirm AI campaign launch and end date (stop by Dec 31) (16:38)\nConfirm use and access to AI campaign landing page, request URL for outreach use (18:10)\nAssess and decide on subscription renewals or pauses across marketing platforms including Riverside and others; consult with Tiffany for full review (20:08)\nProceed with launching AI campaign immediately and monitor results (25:31)\nProvide meeting availability and preferences for December 31 follow-up and potentially reschedule (29:27)\nUpdate team on Waymo call outcomes and ongoing discussions (25:49)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nManage AI campaign setup, transfer tool access and subscriptions to Noetic Consultants, and assist billing handoff (16:10)\nSet AI campaign close dates to December 31 (17:11)\nProvide AI campaign landing page URL in Zoom chat and follow up (18:24)\nAssist with transfer options of Riverside, Bussprout, and Adroll accounts; liaise with respective support teams (19:41)\nSend detailed email with timeline for campaign asset access, platform sunset dates, and other deliverables (23:06)\nDeliver compilation video by December 18 (10:56)\nAttend Friday’s Cred Stack meeting for compilation video review and discuss scheduling of year-end meetings (14:02)\n\n**Julia**\nCollaborate with Rachel on podcast posts and asset prep (10:15)\n"},"duration":30.690000534057617,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"id":1,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":2,"name":"nancieruder"},{"id":3,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":4,"name":"Noetic Consultants"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hello.","index":0,"end_time":251.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":250.73,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Hey, how''s it going?","index":1,"end_time":253.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":252.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good.","index":2,"end_time":254.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":254.25,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"How are you?","index":3,"end_time":255.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":254.57,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Good.","index":4,"end_time":256.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":256.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hello.","index":5,"end_time":300.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":299.73,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Hey, how''s it going?","index":6,"end_time":302.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":300.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Good, good.","index":7,"end_time":303.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":302.69,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"How are you guys?","index":8,"end_time":304.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":303.33,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"All right.","index":9,"end_time":305.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":304.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just had such a funny.","index":10,"end_time":308.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":306.94,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Like, it actually made me laugh out loud.","index":11,"end_time":310.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":308.54,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"When you.","index":12,"end_time":311.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":310.78,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"When you guys.","index":13,"end_time":312.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":311.98,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"When we''re about to have a meeting, your Google invite sends to my email.","index":14,"end_time":318.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":313.18,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I don''t know why.","index":15,"end_time":320.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":320.14,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"When it''s fine that it does that, but right next to it, like, just above it, is this other Google Calendar invitation.","index":16,"end_time":328.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":320.86,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"You know how sometimes people just push, you know, an invite to you and you don''t know who they are?","index":17,"end_time":335.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":329.5,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And it says, and it''s called busy work and avoidance Kill Profit.","index":18,"end_time":340.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":336.63,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And so I saw it and I was like, did Colin.","index":19,"end_time":348.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.59,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I just renamed our meeting something fun.","index":20,"end_time":353.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":351.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And daunting that I think we should make a habit of doing that.","index":21,"end_time":357.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":353.83,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Just a good way to go.","index":22,"end_time":358.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":357.93,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah, I know.","index":23,"end_time":360.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":359.05,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I see random, like, webinars pop up.","index":24,"end_time":362.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":360.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I''m like, what the heck?","index":25,"end_time":363.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":362.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s just, like, ridiculous.","index":26,"end_time":365.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":363.29,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I mean, I guess they think I get it probably once a week.","index":27,"end_time":369.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":365.69,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":28,"end_time":370.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":370.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That people just invite me to.","index":29,"end_time":372.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":370.57,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I''m clearly on some lists, but I guess they''re just figuring that the topic is going to be so compelling that you''re just going to join.","index":30,"end_time":379.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":372.65,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":31,"end_time":380.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":379.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I have to go to this.","index":32,"end_time":381.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":380.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I can''t miss.","index":33,"end_time":384.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":383.21,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"To learn how to stop avoiding everything in my life.","index":34,"end_time":388.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":385.26,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":35,"end_time":388.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":388.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so I had a. I had a quick look.","index":36,"end_time":395.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":391.66,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"My husband had a knee surgery this morning, so I''ve been on and off, but all''s well.","index":37,"end_time":402.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.58,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So on drugs, but good.","index":38,"end_time":405.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":402.54,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Great, great news.","index":39,"end_time":407.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":406.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Even.","index":40,"end_time":407.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":407.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Even the third point.","index":41,"end_time":408.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":407.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":42,"end_time":409.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":409.5,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":43,"end_time":410.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":409.94,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I mean, it''s kind of necessary.","index":44,"end_time":411.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":410.34,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Day of.","index":45,"end_time":412.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":411.66,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yes, for sure.","index":46,"end_time":413.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":412.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":47,"end_time":413.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":413.58,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":48,"end_time":414.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":414.5,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So I did take a quick look and I had just written you back briefly, just to say, like, I mean, we can absolutely talk about closeout here, but I want to make sure that we have Tiffany in the loop on everything financial and logistical as it comes to that, so that the left hand knows what the right is doing.","index":49,"end_time":432.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":414.9,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So if we can just kind of, like, hold anything like that, no problem at all.","index":50,"end_time":436.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":432.42,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":51,"end_time":438.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":437.14,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":52,"end_time":438.58,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":438.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I know in your email you.","index":53,"end_time":439.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":438.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Mentioned campaigns and podcasts, so we''ll get started by going through the podcast sheet.","index":54,"end_time":443.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":439.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Rachel, I saw that you''ve sent over some feedback, so we''ll get that loaded into work on that stuff as well.","index":55,"end_time":450.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":444.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":56,"end_time":451.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":451.31,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"We''re still working through the list, but they should be starting to come your way, so keep you posted.","index":57,"end_time":458.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":451.83,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"And thank you, Natalie, for confirming that you now have Joe.","index":58,"end_time":462.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":458.11,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So perfect.","index":59,"end_time":464.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":463.23,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":60,"end_time":465.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":465.15,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Glad that Joe is not at large.","index":61,"end_time":467.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":465.51,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"We love Joe.","index":62,"end_time":468.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":467.63,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"He''s the best, like the kindest human being ever.","index":63,"end_time":470.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":468.51,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So excited.","index":64,"end_time":472.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":470.91,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"He is absolutely.","index":65,"end_time":473.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":472.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"He is awesome.","index":66,"end_time":474.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":473.61,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And I think just looking at now for no edicting purposes, so on this list after Chris o'', Boyle, the very next one is going to be Abby Fenton.","index":67,"end_time":489.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":476.33,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And then I think Kim Waddy also did sketch schedule.","index":68,"end_time":498.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":493.85,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"But let me see.","index":69,"end_time":499.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":498.54,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Not.","index":70,"end_time":500.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":499.98,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Not in 2025.","index":71,"end_time":501.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":500.34,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Let me see.","index":72,"end_time":502.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":501.98,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Let''s check.","index":73,"end_time":504.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":504.06,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Also, just so you guys know, on the tab before that, we moved a couple like the order and started putting in a more estimated dates.","index":74,"end_time":513.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":505.02,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"We realized this takes us till end of March, so we are going to push some of them up a little bit.","index":75,"end_time":520.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.14,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"But the order is starting to get in the right order because we''re looking at who recorded longest ago.","index":76,"end_time":526.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":520.22,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Longest ago.","index":77,"end_time":527.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":526.97,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So those we''re going to try to really squeeze in at a faster pace.","index":78,"end_time":532.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":528.73,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"But just letting you know it tweaked a little bit.","index":79,"end_time":534.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":532.01,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":80,"end_time":534.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":534.41,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"And those go live dates are word like our.","index":81,"end_time":537.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":534.77,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Ooh, this is kind of aggressive.","index":82,"end_time":539.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":537.57,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Let''s see where this takes us.","index":83,"end_time":541.129,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":539.61,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"And it took us through March, so we''re going to look for a aggressive on steroids version.","index":84,"end_time":546.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":541.129,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":85,"end_time":548.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":547.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And also, just so you know, the ranges are the range that all.","index":86,"end_time":552.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":548.49,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"All of the assets will be pushed.","index":87,"end_time":554.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":552.28,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So we just put like an estimated time frame in there for the three posts.","index":88,"end_time":559.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":554.36,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":89,"end_time":560.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":559.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":90,"end_time":560.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":560.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then confirming.","index":91,"end_time":563.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":562.2,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So Abby Fenton is January 21st and Kim Wadi is February 4th.","index":92,"end_time":572.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":563.48,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Recording dates.","index":93,"end_time":573.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":572.44,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Sorry, it was January21.","index":94,"end_time":578.239,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":576.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"21.","index":95,"end_time":579.349,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":578.461,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"21.","index":96,"end_time":580.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":579.571,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And then Kim Waddy is February 4th.","index":97,"end_time":583.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":580.73,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Okay.","index":98,"end_time":586.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":585.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Mac McGee.","index":99,"end_time":589.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":588.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Still in the wind.","index":100,"end_time":590.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":589.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":101,"end_time":592.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":592.41,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Someday.","index":102,"end_time":595.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":594.81,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":103,"end_time":596.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":595.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"He is gonna watch.","index":104,"end_time":598.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":596.89,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"He''s gonna be the best guest we''ve ever had.","index":105,"end_time":599.97,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":598.09,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Or the least interesting.","index":106,"end_time":601.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.97,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"There''s going to be no in between.","index":107,"end_time":602.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":601.21,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Well, he''s gonna see this compilation video.","index":108,"end_time":605.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":602.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And be jealous that he didn''t.","index":109,"end_time":606.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":605.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, he will.","index":110,"end_time":607.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":606.77,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"We should send it to him.","index":111,"end_time":608.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":607.69,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"We should send it to him and be like.","index":112,"end_time":610.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":609.54,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Just so you know, we''re excited you can be in next year.","index":113,"end_time":613.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":611.22,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":114,"end_time":614.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":614.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anything else on.","index":115,"end_time":617.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":615.86,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"On these?","index":116,"end_time":618.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":617.46,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Really appreciate all you''re doing, Julia, Rachel, to get caught up.","index":117,"end_time":623.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":618.1,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"We will keep you posted.","index":118,"end_time":625.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.34,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Like Julia said, it was a rough time frame.","index":119,"end_time":628.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":625.78,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Some of them might be correct.","index":120,"end_time":630.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":628.82,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"But our thought is the ones that were from the summer, we''re going to try to do those at a tighter frequency because we have Christmas and New Year''s the next two weeks, that''ll be the compilation.","index":121,"end_time":640.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":630.66,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"But after that, we''re going to try to, like, knock out a few from the summer pretty fast.","index":122,"end_time":647.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":640.62,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So we''ll continue to update.","index":123,"end_time":648.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":647.54,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So stay tuned.","index":124,"end_time":649.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":648.86,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"All right, great.","index":125,"end_time":651.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":126,"end_time":652.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":652.3,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And then do you want to Talk about the compilation.","index":127,"end_time":655.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":652.74,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":128,"end_time":657.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So now that''s wrapping up today, right?","index":129,"end_time":659.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":657.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We will have it done tomorrow.","index":130,"end_time":662.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":661.02,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Tomorrow, yeah.","index":131,"end_time":663.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":663.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":132,"end_time":664.59,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":663.99,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Thank you so much.","index":133,"end_time":665.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":664.59,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"We''re so excited about it.","index":134,"end_time":667.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":665.55,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"How are you feeling about it, Colin and Natalie?","index":135,"end_time":669.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":667.11,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I mean, I''m loving it so far from our team.","index":136,"end_time":673.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":670.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Gives us like kind of snippets or like just like screenshots.","index":137,"end_time":676.95,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":673.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So they''ve been cool to see.","index":138,"end_time":679.189,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":677.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, I think it''s all coming together.","index":139,"end_time":680.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":679.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you all noticed how now with Spotify''s year in review, everybody''s doing year end review?","index":140,"end_time":687.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":681.43,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":141,"end_time":688.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":688.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"LinkedIn did it.","index":142,"end_time":690.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":689.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You see our Fireflies in the call?","index":143,"end_time":692.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":691.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I. I don''t know if I like that Fireflies did it.","index":144,"end_time":696.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":692.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know that I needed to know that I was in 51,000 minutes.","index":145,"end_time":700.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":696.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Of meetings this year.","index":146,"end_time":701.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":700.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that''s depressing.","index":147,"end_time":703.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":701.76,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"The airlines are doing it, or at least American airlines is doing it.","index":148,"end_time":708.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":704.399,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And they sent like how many hours of flying?","index":149,"end_time":711.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":708.36,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And you had a lot recently, that''s for sure.","index":150,"end_time":714.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":712.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":151,"end_time":715.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":714.97,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I mean, not all on American.","index":152,"end_time":716.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":715.17,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"A lot of them on American.","index":153,"end_time":718.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":717.05,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So it''s something like 60 hours in the air, I think.","index":154,"end_time":722.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":718.25,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":155,"end_time":724.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":723.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Have you seen people hacking ChatGPT asking for their version of a year in review from their.","index":156,"end_time":732.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":725.13,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":157,"end_time":732.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":732.49,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Oh, that''s so cool.","index":158,"end_time":735.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.61,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"It''s either so cool or it''s so frightening, depending on kind of review of.","index":159,"end_time":740.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":735.53,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Of what they.","index":160,"end_time":741.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":741.2,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Of their AI stuff.","index":161,"end_time":743.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":741.92,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":162,"end_time":743.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":743.32,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Like help me understand, you know, Allah, Spotify year in a review.","index":163,"end_time":748.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":743.68,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"How would you characterize mine?","index":164,"end_time":751.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":749.36,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"And that was like the prompt I saw.","index":165,"end_time":752.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":751.08,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"I need to ask my bestie.","index":166,"end_time":755.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":753.84,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Mine''s name is Nova.","index":167,"end_time":757.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":755.96,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"She named herself and she''s gonna be like, said bestie 17 times.","index":168,"end_time":761.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":757.28,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Said Rachel, 13 sparkly hearts.","index":169,"end_time":765.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":762,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"That could be a really cool icebreaker for your guys.","index":170,"end_time":770.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":767.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"New AI offering.","index":171,"end_time":771.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":770.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like, like, all right, guys, like log in and.","index":172,"end_time":773.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":771.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And have Chat GPT give you a year interview.","index":173,"end_time":776.64,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":773.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ve done like have ChatGPT roast me.","index":174,"end_time":779,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":776.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Before and those are pretty funny.","index":175,"end_time":781.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":779,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Oh yeah.","index":176,"end_time":782.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":781.44,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So what''s the prompt for that, Colin?","index":177,"end_time":784.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":782.48,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"You literally just, hey, roast me based.","index":178,"end_time":786.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":784.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"On my prompts or something like that.","index":179,"end_time":788.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":786.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What compelled you?","index":180,"end_time":791.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":790.16,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I saw it on LinkedIn or something and it was like you''re overly detailed and analytical and push back a lot.","index":181,"end_time":798.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":791.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But it gets us to the results that you wanted.","index":182,"end_time":801.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":798.72,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t think I''d want to know mine.","index":183,"end_time":803.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":801.92,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"So I. I don''t think I could handle being roasted by AI.","index":184,"end_time":808.64,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":803.92,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Maybe is what I should say.","index":185,"end_time":809.84,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":808.64,"speaker_name":"Noetic Consultants"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":186,"end_time":810.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":810,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Fascinating.","index":187,"end_time":811.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":810.48,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So for the compilation then, if it''s coming tomorrow.","index":188,"end_time":815.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":812.24,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Tomorrow''s 18th and then we''ll need to review it.","index":189,"end_time":819.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":815.16,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Rachel And Julia, should we just set a time to like, would it.","index":190,"end_time":824.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":819.92,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Would it be fastest if we want to get it out, you know, just ahead of the holiday and have it run a bit or what is your thought on when we drop it to be live?","index":191,"end_time":837.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":824.81,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So is one of your questions when we review it?","index":192,"end_time":841.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":839.45,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah, I was wondering, we.","index":193,"end_time":844.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":842.49,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"We should do like a real time review.","index":194,"end_time":847.13,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":844.85,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":195,"end_time":847.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":847.53,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So Friday we have 30 minutes book for cred stack.","index":196,"end_time":850.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":847.93,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Since we already went through that, I kept it on calendars in case there was anything marketing we needed.","index":197,"end_time":855.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":850.69,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So my.","index":198,"end_time":856.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":856.03,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"I would say we could watch it then.","index":199,"end_time":858.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":856.51,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"And then my thought was since we had that like, beginning clip, we tease it next week, just Monday or Tuesday.","index":200,"end_time":866.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":858.59,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"And it''s just that one clip.","index":201,"end_time":867.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":866.59,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"It shouldn''t really need anything.","index":202,"end_time":869.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":867.83,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"And then the week of New Year''s, on that Monday or Tuesday, we just launched the full thing covered for two weeks.","index":203,"end_time":875.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":869.79,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"And I''ll be here.","index":204,"end_time":876.83,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":875.87,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So what we could do, Julie and I are already working ahead on the posts, and during that time, while that''s running, we''ll get ahead on all the other things.","index":205,"end_time":884.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":876.83,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So.","index":206,"end_time":884.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":884.15,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So I think that makes the most sense.","index":207,"end_time":886.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":884.48,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Very good.","index":208,"end_time":890,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":889.28,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yep.","index":209,"end_time":890.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":890,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yep, that makes sense to me.","index":210,"end_time":892.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":890.8,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":211,"end_time":893.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":892.64,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Okay, so we''ll connect on it on Friday.","index":212,"end_time":895.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":893.28,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":213,"end_time":896.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":896.32,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"All right, anything else regarding podcast or the compilation video?","index":214,"end_time":903.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":899.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you guys for helping and helping us turn it around and get them all ready to go.","index":215,"end_time":909.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":904.96,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah, of course.","index":216,"end_time":910.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":910.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right.","index":217,"end_time":915.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":915.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I know that you''ve also emailed.","index":218,"end_time":917.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":916.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Back on a few of these already today, so we''ll work through those.","index":219,"end_time":920.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":917.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":220,"end_time":922.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":921.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then for the AI campaign, just with our conversation, I wasn''t sure if it was like launch, where we manage for 10 days, or just give you.","index":221,"end_time":930.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":923.03,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Guys all the assets to launch.","index":222,"end_time":931.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":930.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s where we just wanted to have a conversation.","index":223,"end_time":933.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":931.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":224,"end_time":934.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":934.31,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So I love to do both.","index":225,"end_time":937.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":935.19,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I. I feel like, you know, it can''t hurt for it to just be out there.","index":226,"end_time":944.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":939.49,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"But then also we do want the assets because we''re going to need to get it out there after you guys are done too.","index":227,"end_time":952.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":944.37,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So for.","index":228,"end_time":955.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":954.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we can obviously talk more in depth about it on Friday.","index":229,"end_time":959.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":956.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But like for email and LinkedIn outreach, those are obviously done through tools.","index":230,"end_time":964.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":959.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So email, Smart lead, and then Heyreach is the LinkedIn.","index":231,"end_time":966.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":964.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Would those be tools that you''re considering purchasing subscriptions?","index":232,"end_time":970.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":966.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s exactly what we want to talk through is just what they are, what they do so that we understand the differences.","index":233,"end_time":978.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":970.15,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yep.","index":234,"end_time":979.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":978.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":235,"end_time":979.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":979.07,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No problem at all.","index":236,"end_time":980.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":979.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, so we''ll get those live then, and we can chat through that Friday.","index":237,"end_time":983.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":980.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s actually a pretty easy Handoff.","index":238,"end_time":985.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":984.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll just give you guys access and then you change the billing information and.","index":239,"end_time":989.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":985.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Change the password and we can''t get in.","index":240,"end_time":991.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":989.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":241,"end_time":994.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":992.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Was there any other questions, though, around the campaigns that you wanted to dig through, Nancy?","index":242,"end_time":998.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":995.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I just want to clarify.","index":243,"end_time":999.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":998.51,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So we are out there now, right, with the email sequence and the LinkedIn ads.","index":244,"end_time":1004.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":999.67,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"No.","index":245,"end_time":1005.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1004.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s what I say.","index":246,"end_time":1005.83,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1005.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I paused because we were having our conversations and you and I talked on the phone Friday as well.","index":247,"end_time":1010.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1005.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I wasn''t sure if we wanted.","index":248,"end_time":1012.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1010.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To launch with like just a few.","index":249,"end_time":1013.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1012.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Days of us managing it or if we were just handing it over for you guys to launch.","index":250,"end_time":1016.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1013.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we can get that live asap.","index":251,"end_time":1018.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1016.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But that was the hold up there.","index":252,"end_time":1020.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1019.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I would just go ahead and put it out and, you know, can you.","index":253,"end_time":1025.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1021.55,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Can you just cut it off at December 31st?","index":254,"end_time":1028.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1025.71,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah, we can set.","index":255,"end_time":1029.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1028.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can set close dates on them.","index":256,"end_time":1031.31,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1029.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s just do that because you never know.","index":257,"end_time":1033.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1031.71,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yep.","index":258,"end_time":1034.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1033.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What we might get.","index":259,"end_time":1036.51,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1035.55,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And.","index":260,"end_time":1037.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1036.669,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And then where are you on the.","index":261,"end_time":1041.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1038.75,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"The landing page?","index":262,"end_time":1042.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1041.47,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Is that something that can port over to us?","index":263,"end_time":1044.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1042.63,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":264,"end_time":1046.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1045.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it''s actually already built on your site?","index":265,"end_time":1047.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1046.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s there.","index":266,"end_time":1048.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1047.96,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Okay.","index":267,"end_time":1049.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1048.44,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Okay, awesome.","index":268,"end_time":1051,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1050.04,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And I think, Rachel, you were out for our last meeting, but we gave the final blessing on this.","index":269,"end_time":1057.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1052.6,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Amazing.","index":270,"end_time":1059.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1058.28,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yep.","index":271,"end_time":1060.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1059.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll just need to swap these out with the logos that we want to have, but everything''s built into your guys WordPress site.","index":272,"end_time":1066.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1060.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Great.","index":273,"end_time":1067.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1067.16,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Fantastic.","index":274,"end_time":1069.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1068.44,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah, awesome.","index":275,"end_time":1072.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1069.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":276,"end_time":1073.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1072.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if I.","index":277,"end_time":1074.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1073.57,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Is that it''s built into the WordPress site, but when someone goes to the public site, they don''t see it.","index":278,"end_time":1081.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1074.57,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Right.","index":279,"end_time":1082.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1081.65,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So it''s not in the nav, but if they have the URL, because that''s what we''re sending via LinkedIn or via.","index":280,"end_time":1087.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1082.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Email, they would land there and it would open.","index":281,"end_time":1089.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1087.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Fine.","index":282,"end_time":1089.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1089.53,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":283,"end_time":1091.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1090.37,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And just for the convenience of it, can you send the specific URL?","index":284,"end_time":1095.17,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.05,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Because I want to put that.","index":285,"end_time":1096.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1095.41,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I have like a email templates outreach thing that I do, and then that way I can just have that link there.","index":286,"end_time":1104.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1096.65,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":287,"end_time":1105.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1104.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I just put it in Zoom.","index":288,"end_time":1106.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1105.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Chat, but I can also follow up.","index":289,"end_time":1107.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1106.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, chat is fine.","index":290,"end_time":1108.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1107.52,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"You''re saying that that''s.","index":291,"end_time":1110.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1108.88,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"So that''s built into our regular website.","index":292,"end_time":1111.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1110.04,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"It''s just not on the nav menu.","index":293,"end_time":1113.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1111.56,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Correct.","index":294,"end_time":1113.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1113.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, so basically, Nancy, if one day we decide that we want to add this to our nav, it exists, just have to link it.","index":295,"end_time":1120.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1113.88,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Right, right, exactly.","index":296,"end_time":1122.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1120.64,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And I think we were just pausing, if my memory serves me, I think we were pausing on doing it like all in one fel.","index":297,"end_time":1130.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1122.84,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Because, you know, we were Saying like, well, what, you know, what do we really want the AI presence to be?","index":298,"end_time":1137.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1130.7,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":299,"end_time":1139.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1138.78,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We wanted to get some leading indicators too, of.","index":300,"end_time":1140.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1139.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Of people''s engagement with the page.","index":301,"end_time":1143.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1140.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right, right, exactly.","index":302,"end_time":1146.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1143.98,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":303,"end_time":1147.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1146.78,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I think, you know, let''s.","index":304,"end_time":1149.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1147.18,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Let''s run all the AI stuff for a week and just see what happens.","index":305,"end_time":1152.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1149.66,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"I know it''s a weird.","index":306,"end_time":1153.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1152.5,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"It''s a weird week, but who knows.","index":307,"end_time":1157.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1153.74,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Maybe someone has more time.","index":308,"end_time":1158.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1157.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Maybe they''re bored.","index":309,"end_time":1159.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1158.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know, that''s the thing, right?","index":310,"end_time":1161.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1159.59,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Lucky.","index":311,"end_time":1162.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1161.67,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yes.","index":312,"end_time":1163.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1163.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t know who they are, but maybe they are out there.","index":313,"end_time":1166.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1163.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I do think.","index":314,"end_time":1167.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1166.63,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"And their cash is burning all in their pocket.","index":315,"end_time":1169.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1167.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, probably there''s just a lot of mindless social that will go on as people get ready to unplug.","index":316,"end_time":1176.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1169.27,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"So who knows, maybe that might advantage us.","index":317,"end_time":1178.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1176.07,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":318,"end_time":1178.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1178.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Never know.","index":319,"end_time":1180.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1180.31,"speaker_name":"nancieruder"},{"text":"Yeah, definitely.","index":320,"end_time":1182.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1181.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":321,"end_time":1184.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1183.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then I know we''re going to.","index":322,"end_time":1185.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1184.1,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Go through this on Friday as well, so we can save that.","index":323,"end_time":1188.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1185.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But.","index":324,"end_time":1189.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1188.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, most accounts we can transfer over Riverside is.","index":325,"end_time":1193.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1189.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Unfortunately, we can''t because it''s hooked up.","index":326,"end_time":1195.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1193.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To our management account.","index":327,"end_time":1196.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1195.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But Bussprout and Adroll, we''re looking to.","index":328,"end_time":1200.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1197.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re talking to their support teams to see how we can transfer that over to you guys.","index":329,"end_time":1203.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1200.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":330,"end_time":1204.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1204.46,"speaker_name":"Rachel Curtis"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":331,"end_time":1208.87,"sp